#: result.py:3857
msgid "Beryl: Did you remember your dice? * she asks with a smile on her face. I pat myself down in a panic, knowing full well that I lost it..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:3858
msgid "Well, you see. I... * Just as I'm about to come clean, she reaches into her pocket and pulls out my fancy little dice bag, the one she gifted me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:3860
msgid "Beryl: J-just leavin' my gifts wherever you want... * I try and form some sort of apology but she breaks into giggles. * Nah, you're all good. I kept it nice and safe for you!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:3861 result.py:3998
msgid "* Magdalena gets our attention. * Hope you all remember where we were!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:3862
msgid "Yeah, yeah. I remember! Walked right into a portal."
