#: result.py:3870
msgid "So I'm being eaten alive, aren't I?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:3871
msgid "* Magdalena smiles, but ignores me * Also, you are down 10 health points and you feel yourself losing more strength as you're squeezed by this small... space."
