#: result.py:3892
msgid "* Cadence purses her lips and turns her attention dramatically towards Decima * Shit is right! You are a destructo!!! * She growls and tackles Decima and they collapse into a puddle of laughter."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:3893
msgid "* Magdalena clears her throat loudly, and they both freeze."
