#: result.py:4125
msgid "* Cadence holds intense eye contact with her for a few seconds, then sighs. * FINE!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4126
msgid "Magdalena: Ok, so you decide to enter the Devlin Headquarters. It's a five-or-so minute walk, and the path is fairly clear of debris, most likely maintained by Devlin's employees."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4127
msgid "Magdalena: You remember that she told you to meet her in the office on the very top floor, like 90 floors up or something ridiculous like that."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4128
msgid "Magdalena: The air-evator shoots you up to the top floor in under ten seconds, and places you gently on the smooth metallic floor of her office."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4129
msgid "Magdalena: She's at the far side of this giant office room, staring out the massive windows out into the city. She's dressed in her black cloak, which makes her look like a shadow."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4130
msgid "Magdalena: She swings around when she hears you enter, and smiles. ' My... I mean, the heart. You have it. MMMM I can almost feel it from here!'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4131
msgid "Magdalena: She floats across the floor to you like a ghost, arms outstretched. 'Hand it to me, my lovelies.'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4132
msgid "Sorry, Decima. We gotta destroy this thing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4133
msgid "Decima: But..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4134
msgid "Decima: Coins?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4135
msgid "Cadence: Shhh, babe. It's gonna be ok."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4136
msgid "Decima: Fine! Let's stomp the heart. Stomp it all the way to hell."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4137
msgid "Magdalena: Do you want to actually stomp it?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4138
msgid "Stomp it to hell."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4139
msgid "Let's burn it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4140
msgid "Eat it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4141
msgid "Decima said it! Let's stomp it!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4142
msgid "* Magdalena laughs, * Wow, you are... so creative. Ok, so you stomp it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4143
msgid "Magdalena: As your substantial foot smashes down on the squishy heart, you hear the loudest, most disturbing screech you've ever experienced."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4144
msgid "Beryl: Ahhh! Stop stomping!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4145
msgid "Decima: I drop to my knees and pray for a pair of earplugs from Horsehat!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4146
msgid "Magdalena: You notice that the noise is affecting people walking by. Some of them cover their ears and run away, while others gather around."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4147
msgid "Shit. Uh, ok I stop stomping it!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4148
msgid "Aren't you supposed to burn these types of things? Get rid of the curse?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4149
msgid "Cadence: Yes! That's what I'm saying! Fire is always the best solution."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4150
msgid "Cadence: Well, most of the time... Some of the time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4151
msgid "Magdalena: Burning it, hmm? All right. Who has fire?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4152
msgid "Beryl: I d-do! I take out a lighter... It's not much, but..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4153
msgid "Cadence: It will have to do. Ok, I take the lighter and... How do you light meat on fire?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4154
msgid "* Beryl giggles, * Shouldn't you know how to burn, like, everything??"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4155
msgid "Cadence: I should, shouldn't I? Well, I guess I just hold it on up to this lil' heart, see if it burns up?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4156
msgid "* Magdalena smiles, * Ok, so... you hold the flame to the spiraling meaty heart, and it begins to singe the edges of it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4157
msgid "Magdalena: When you do this, however, the heart lets out an ear shattering sound. A high pitched scream bursts through the quiet city."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4158
msgid "Beryl: Oh no! Cadence, B-burn it faster!!!!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4159
msgid "Cadence: I jab it with the lighter?!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4160
msgid "Magdalena: Interesting move... It keeps screaming! And now a crowd is forming of onlookers wondering what's happening."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4161
msgid "Cadence: Beryl! Take it! I put the lighter away."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4162
msgid "Honestly, the best bet is to make a meal of it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4163
msgid "Beryl: Uh, HC... Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4164
msgid "Decima: No this is a genius idea! HC, you know what's up! I'm ready to dig in!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4165
msgid "Decima: Also, maybe I'm just hungry in real life...."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4166
msgid "* Magdalena laughs, * What! Ok, despite that being a really, really weird idea, go for it..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4167
msgid "Ok, Uh, well... I guess I'll borrow a dagger, and..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4168
msgid "Cadence: Not even gonna cook it?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4169
msgid "Decima: No time! Hand me a chunk of that meat!!!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4170
msgid "Magdalena: Oh my god... Ok, you take a chunk of 'that meat'. It's hard to pull a piece out, also..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4171
msgid "Magdalena: It screams when you manage to rip out a bit. In fact, it screams so loud that the few people walking around you take notice, and start to gather."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4172
msgid "Magdalena: But you are able to throw it in your mouth and chew it. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4173
msgid "Magdalena: Of course, it tastes like raw meat, and you can feel the spirals squirming down your throat."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4174
msgid "Magdalena: Actually, make a constitution save."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4175
msgid "Decima: No problem! * She shakes the d20 in her hands for a few seconds, then throws them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4176
msgid "Decima: Why does my luck always fail me!!! * She rolled a six."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4177
msgid "Magdalena: Yeah, so this piece of heart grabs at the inside of your throat and forces its way back up and out your mouth."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4178
msgid "Magdalena: You lose two health for that... It feels just awful."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4179
msgid "Decima: Wow! Ok, sorry HC. I tried. I failed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4180
msgid "Magdalena: The heart is still screaming. You seem to have triggered a defense mechanism within."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4181
msgid "Magdalena: What's worse, the crowd gathering around you begins to part, and you see the doctor."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4182
msgid "Beryl: Uh oh... I, uh, hide the heart! in my pack!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4183
msgid "Magdalena: You tuck the heart in your pack, concealing it from view, however the noise is so loud you can hardly tell the difference."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4184
msgid "Magdalena: Doctor Devlin reaches the group. She is wearing her usual dark sunglasses, and massive hood that conceals most of her features."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4185
msgid "Magdalena: She says, 'The heart. You have it.'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4186
msgid "Beryl: N-nooooope..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4187
msgid "Magdalena: 'Unconvincing! Besides, I'd know that scream anywhere. Now, why don't you give me my lovely little heart, yes?'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4188
msgid "Decima: Where's the cash, then?!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4189
msgid "Magdalena: 'The coins are back in my office. Once you hand the heart over, I will give you all the coins.'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4190
msgid "Magdalena: ' Why don't you come with me? We can get away from this crowd, do this somewhere more private?'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4191
msgid "Decima: Let's follow her. She's right, we'll have more privacy."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4192
msgid "Beryl: Uhhh.... Ok? I don't really t-trust you, Decima! But... Ok, yeah, let's g-go."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4193
msgid "Magdalena: Ok, so you follow Devlin back to her skyscraper. She has a weird ability to part the crowds of onlookers, making it a short walk."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4194
msgid "Magdalena: Her office is on the top floor, like 90 floors up! Something like that. It's a tall one."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4195
msgid "Magdalena: The heart seems gets quieter the closer Devlin is, like they have a bond already."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4196
msgid "Magdalena: Her office overlooks the devastated city. It looks tiny from here, only a few city blocks wide, and slowly being overtaken by a wave of green."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4197
msgid "Magdalena: 'Well, here we are. Now, where is my darling...'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4198
msgid "Decima: Why are you talking about this like it's your freaking baby!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4199
msgid "Magdalena: 'The heart is special to me. I will use it to rebuild this city, to turn it into something worthy.'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4200
msgid "Magdalena: She reaches her hand out to you, Beryl."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4201
msgid "Beryl: Should I?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4202
msgid "Decima: Just go for it. I mean, she wants to rebuild the city, what could possibly be wrong about that?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4203
msgid "Beryl: F-famous last words, but... Ok. I hand over t-the heart."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4204
msgid "Magdalena: She smiles, showing off her sharpened teeth. 'You've done the right thing.' She cackles as she takes the heart from your hands, and she holds it for a long moment, staring into the spiraling tendrils."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4205
msgid "Magdalena: Then she rips her coat off... and reveals a giant hole in her fleshy chest. It's gruesome, bloody. She shoves it inside."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4206
msgid "Magdalena: She's still laughing as she adjusts the heart, and the spiral begins to light up and you feel the familiar tingly good sensation.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4207
msgid "Magdalena: You want to walk towards the heart. Devlin's voice begins to sound soft and gentle."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4208
msgid "Magdalena: Constitution saves, everyone!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4209
msgid "Roll"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4210
msgid "Fifteen! Am I safe?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4211
msgid "Magdalena: Yes! Anybody else?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4212 result.py:4261
msgid "Beryl: Not close... Un-unless three counts? * Magdalena just shakes her head."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4213
msgid "Cadence: And what about five? Nope..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4214
msgid "Decima: Well I rolled twelve and if that doesn't save me I don't know what will!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4215
msgid "Magdalena: Literally anything above that would have... Well, shit. HC, you're the only one that passed!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4216 result.py:4265
msgid "Magdalena: For the rest of you, Devlin gestures for you to walk towards her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4217
msgid "Magdalena: 'Yessss, that's right. You are under my care now. Do not worry, Devlin is here to save the day."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4218
msgid "Decima: All right, Devlin, sounds good to me! Suck me into your gorgeously gooey chest hole."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4219
msgid "Well... I'm not buying it! Right?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4220
msgid "Magdalena: Right. You know this trick, and you're able to avert your eyes in time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4221
msgid "Can I... Hmmm. Can I take a weapon from one of you?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4222 result.py:4271
msgid "Magdalena: They can't hear you, but yeah."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4223
msgid "I'll take Beryl's sword!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4224
msgid "I swipe Beryl's sword and plunge it into Devlin's heart in one swift motion."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4225 result.py:4274
msgid "Magdalena: Hmmm... roll for it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4226
msgid "* I toss the die in my hand and let it clatter on the floor. * twenty..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4227
msgid "Magdalena: Well shit, HC. You've gone and done it!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4228 result.py:4277
msgid "Magdalena: You plunge the sword straight into Devlin's spinning heart, and it lets out a scream so loud that the windows in her office shatter."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4229
msgid "Magdalena: The wind rushes in, knocking Beryl, Cadence and Decima to the floor."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4230
msgid "Magdalena: HC, you fall over on top of Devlin but you don't even care, because all you're focused on is stabbing the freaking life out of her heart."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4231 result.py:4288
msgid "Magdalena: The screaming, spiraling, glowing heart slowly fades, as does the life in Devlin's eyes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4232 result.py:4289
msgid "Magdalena: You've defeated Devlin. You can feel the power of her flow straight into your veins. You've never felt so powerful, so invincible."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4233
msgid "Do I feel... Evil?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4234
msgid "Magdalena: That, $, is for you to decide. * She smiles."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4235 result.py:4292
msgid "Magdalena: The rest of you can stand up now. It's still kind of hard to walk with the wind, but---"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4236 result.py:4293
msgid "Decima: COINS?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4237 result.py:4294
msgid "Magdalena: Oh my god, Decima! Ok, yes, coins! So, you notice the door to Devlin's office safe has been blown off, and guess what's inside..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4238 result.py:4295
msgid "Decima: ...coins?... * She whispers."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4239 result.py:4296
msgid "* Magdalena leans in to Decima, whispers, * 500 gold coins."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4240 result.py:4297
msgid "* Decima falls over dramatically, * TOO MANY COINS!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4241 result.py:4298
msgid "Cadence: We can build so many mansions with this money!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4242
msgid "Decima: Start our own empire... The possibilities."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4243 result.py:4300
msgid "Beryl: Uhhh, or m-maybe something less... evil?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4244 result.py:4301
msgid "* Decima nods, contemplates for a moment, * Maybe."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4245 result.py:4302
msgid "Magdalena: So, that's kind of as far as I've written... So I'll stop there!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4246 result.py:4303
msgid "Beryl: It w-was amazing, Mags! * She wraps her arms around Mags, snuggles into her chest."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4247 result.py:4304
msgid "Cadence: It was epic!!!! Hey, so... * She reaches into a bag, * Since you got us all little miniatures last game, I scavenged around for some tiny treats."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4248 result.py:4305
msgid "Cadence: I painted this mug for you, Mags... It says * She twists it around to Mags."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4249 result.py:4306
msgid "* Magdalena reads it out loud, * Magdalena: Pira's premiere Dungeon Master."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4250
msgid "Magdalena: That's... That's pretty dope. Thanks, Cads."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4251 result.py:4308
msgid "Cadence: Anything for the PDM! * She keeps rummaging, then turns to me and Beryl."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4252 result.py:4309
msgid "Cadence: Decima helped me pick out a couple of things for you and Beryl, but I don't know what you'd prefer, so..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4253 result.py:4310
msgid "Cadence: A bag of 'gold' coins or this lil' berry plush I got from the Rust Pups..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4254 result.py:4311
msgid "Decima: It's supposed to be a Bloodberry but, like, they only had a generic berry. At least it's cute."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4255
msgid "Beryl: Awww, well... I p-personally t-think HC should get both f-for saving us all from the literal devil!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4256
msgid "Cadence: That is very true. You are a DnD hero. * She passes me the coins and berry."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4257
msgid "You sure? * I try to hold them up to her at least, to let her choose one, but she just pushes them back."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4258
msgid "Beryl: Positive. A-all I want is... * She leans in and kisses me on the cheek. * One kiss! T-there. I am satisfied!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4259
msgid "Ten! Am I safe?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4260
msgid "Magdalena: No, sorry. What's everyone else have?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4262
msgid "Cadence: And what about five? Nope."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4263
msgid "Decima: Well I rolled fifteen and if that doesn't save me I don't know what will!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4264
msgid "Magdalena: It certainly saves you... Well, shit. Decima, you're the only one that passed!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4266
msgid "Magdalena: 'Yessss, that's right. You are under my care now. Do not worry, Devlin is here to save the day.'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4267
msgid "Cadence: I'll do whatever you want, even though your name is Devlin!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4268
msgid "Decima: Yet again, Decima has to save the world. Horsehat, help me out here."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4269
msgid "Magdalena: That's right. You know this trick, and you're able to avert your eyes in time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4270
msgid "Decima: And I know exactly what to do! Do not fear! I will stab the heart!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4272
msgid "Decima: Hmmm... I am lacking a long sword... I'll take Beryl's sword!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4273
msgid "Decima: I swipe Beryl's sword and plunge it into Devlin's heart in one swift motion! I yell out to Horsehat as I plunge it in that gross swirly thing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4275
msgid "* Decima tosses the die dramatically in her hands then closes her eyes and lets it clatter on the floor."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4276
msgid "Magdalena: 20! Well shit, Decima. You've gone and done it!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4278
msgid "Magdalena: The wind rushes in, knocking Beryl, Cadence and HC to the floor."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4279
msgid "Magdalena: Decima, you fall over on top of Devlin but you don't even care, because all you're focused on is stabbing the freaking life out of her heart."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4280
msgid "Decima: 'Devlin! I feel kinda bad for killing you! But don't worry, I'll totally keep your skyscraper safe! Your legacy will live on through me!'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4281
msgid "Decima: 'Also I'll keep your coins safe too and cherish them forever and also your sunglasses are epic so I'll probably take those...'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4282
msgid "Decima: 'Also your name is dope so I'm gonna be the new Devlin! Call me Doctor Pigly Devlin-Girkin.' That's what I yell as I kill Devlin."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4283
msgid "Magdalena: Really?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4284
msgid "Decima: Really."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4285
msgid "Magdalena:..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4286
msgid "Decima:...."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4287
msgid "Magdalena: Ok, you scream that long ass speech in like five seconds even though she can't hear you, then..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4290
msgid "Decima: MUAHAHAHAHA! I am the NEW DEVLIN! COWER BEFORE ME! * She clears her throat. * Or, you know, I'll use my powers for good, too..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4291
msgid "Magdalena: That, Pigly, is for you to decide. * She smiles."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4299
msgid "Decima: Start our own empire... Doctor Pigly Devlin-Girkin and Jam. Unlimited power..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4307
msgid "Magdalena: That's... That's pretty dope. Thanks, Cadence."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4312
msgid "* Bag of coins."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4313
msgid "* Berry Plush."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4314
msgid "Decima: Pigly approves!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4315
msgid "Cadence: Awww, great choice! That little berry is the cutest."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4316
msgid "* We hang out for a bit longer, until Cadence stretches, stands up, * I gotta get back to my lil' Peep. Make sure she hasn't poked her eye on anything too sharp!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4317
msgid "* Decima hops up, * And I shall escort you home."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4318
msgid "Cadence: So kind! Even though you are literally right next door..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4319
msgid "* They head out together, leaving Beryl and Mags and me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4320
msgid "Beryl: I'm gonna go turn down the heat a bit before we leave, Mags. I'll be right back! * She skips off towards the back room."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4321
msgid "* Magdalena and I sit awkwardly for a minute, which is starting to feel more normal than talking with her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4322
msgid "You were an awesome... game leader? * I finally manage."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4323
msgid "* She sighs, * DM? * She's trying to act annoyed, but she's still smiling."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4324
msgid "Mags: I'm actually super glad you liked it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4325
msgid "* She pauses for a moment, her eyes darting from the ground to my eyes nervously. She looks around the library, which is empty now that Beryl has gone to the back."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4326
msgid "* Then she wraps her arms around me, embracing me cautiously, her hands not quite gripping me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4327
msgid "* I can tell that she isn't used to this, and that she's waiting for me to reciprocate, to pull her into me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4328
msgid "* Pull her closer."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4329
msgid "* Let her pull away."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4330
msgid "* So I do. I pull her body closer to mine, until I feel her relax and sink further into me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4331
msgid "* I wait until she wants to pull back."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4332
msgid "* When she does, she looks into my eyes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4333
msgid "* She and I are about the same height, so she doesn't need to strain to place her lips against mine."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4334
msgid "* She's nervous still. I can feel her lips trembling as she kisses me, but I can also sense her growing smile."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4335
msgid "* Again, I follow her lead, let her release her smooth, warm lips from mine when she's ready, but when she does I immediately want to pull her back in."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4336
msgid "* She's blushing now and fiddling with her hair, but she's still smiling."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4337
msgid "Magdalena: Sorry, I'm bad at this."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4338
msgid "You aren't! Really. You could be, like, a pro kisser... or something."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4339
msgid "* She laughs, * A pro kisser? You dork."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4340
msgid "* She regains her composure, stands up straighter, * Anyway, we should do some more hanging out..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4341
msgid "Magdalena: I want to be an actual good friend to you, you know?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4342
msgid "Magdalena: I fucked it up really bad at first, so I totally get if you don't want to."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4343
msgid "Magdalena: But I like you a lot. I just have, like, massive walls up all the time. And I'm an asshole a lot of the time..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4344
msgid "No, you... Well, yeah that's kind of true. Thanks for trying, though. New people are overwhelming, I get it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4345
msgid "* We both turn as Beryl hurries back to us. * Ok, it's about to get very, very cold. So we should head out ASAP!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4346
msgid "* Magdalena nods. She turns to me, * I'll, uh, see you soon, k?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4347
msgid "* I nod, * Yeah, of course! Anytime. * I think I actually mean it, too."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4348
msgid "*  I want to have a better friendship with Magdalena. Hopefully she really wants to be better."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4349
msgid "* I wander back to the city, taking my time through Skipnoise Avenue, breathing in semi-fresh air as I skirt the void on the path towards my apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4350
msgid "* Mags meets me at the door, dressed in her typical ectoplasmic green. A touch more makeup than usual, though. And much stompier boots."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4351
msgid "* She scans my outfit. * That's what you're wearing? Interesting choice..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4352
msgid "* Already with the bullshit. * Mags, you're wearing the same thing you wear literally every day."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4353
msgid "* She smiles in a way that makes me almost believe she's self aware. * Yeah, cause I look good."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4354
msgid "So, are you ready?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4355
msgid "Mags: Yeah, if we're sure this isn't gonna be totally lame. Let's go."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4356 result.py:4443
msgid "* We head inside and find a much larger crowd than usual. Someone distinctly unmasked is on stage going absolutely ham on a beat-up keyboard. The crowd seems to like it, but they're certainly not the Headliner."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4357 result.py:4444
msgid "* At the end of a ruthlessly high-speed piece, they stand, breathing hard. The crowd cheers. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4358 result.py:4445
msgid "* The keyboard players yells at everyone. * You ready for ESPER99?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4359 result.py:4446
msgid "* The cheering quadruples in enthusiasm. We sink into the back of the crowd and clap along with them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4360
msgid "* Mags leans close, talks into my ear. * Sit tight, HC. I'm gonna be right back."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4361 result.py:4448
msgid "* I nod, and they head off towards the bar. When I return my attention to the stage, the keyboardist has been replaced by a masked figure in a pale dress."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4362 result.py:4449
msgid "* Bright blood stains their chin and neck. Cupped in both hands, like some kinda sacred object, is a circular metal tray filled with grey dirt. They aren't moving, and it's kinda freaking me out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4363 result.py:4450
msgid "* It's quiet for a moment as the crowd acclimatizes to the sudden vibe change. Lights fade out, then reignite in brilliant, hellish crimson."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4364 result.py:4451
msgid "* The figure slowly raises the tray of dirt to shoulder height, offering it up to some unseen giant. The lights brighten."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4365 result.py:4452
msgid "* There's a glint of teeth from under the perimeter of the mask as they spit blood into the tray, place it on the edge of the stage, take a step back. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4366 result.py:4453
msgid "* A growly bass vibrates up from beneath the floor, churning the blood and dirt into symmetrical patterns. The figure raises a hand above the dish and waits."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4367
msgid "* Mags appears beside me, drink in each hand. * Did I miss anything?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4368 result.py:4455
msgid "Nah, I'm guessing you're just in time. * I take one of the glasses and give it a sniff. Pearl Mana, but with a boozy smell and an oily rainbow on its surface."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4369
msgid "* I beat Mags to the first sip just as the bass cuts. All attention turns to the stage. The ring of my ice sounds weird in the sudden silence. I lift the drink to my lips, but Mags elbows me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4370 result.py:4457
msgid "* She points at the tray. * What the fuck."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4371 result.py:4458
msgid "* Waxy fronds have broken through the surface of the ashy dirt and are heading skyward at an unnatural pace, only slowing when they get in proximity of the figure's hand."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4372 result.py:4459
msgid "* The stem splits and a fleshy, red flower blooms in high speed, petals unsticking from each other and fanning out, strings of crimson sap wilting between them. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4373 result.py:4460
msgid "* Red fluid continues to run from the crooks of the petals, up their length, and, in opposition to gravity, upwards into the air. Holograms, maybe? Or am I looking at some kinda buoyancy-juice."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4374 result.py:4461
msgid "* I don't have much time to consider the technology behind a legit reverse-o gravity situation before the droplets join in orbit around the figures hand. As the blood drips, wet notes sound from all around us."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4375 result.py:4462
msgid "* They pull back their fist and the fluid rushes in parallel. I can almost feel the gravity shift in the room, pulling us towards the stage. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4376 result.py:4463
msgid "* Speakers around the room hammer patterns into their slime coating, sending flecks into the audience. The sound hits like a particle beam, into the sternum, out from under the shoulder blades."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4377 result.py:4464
msgid "* I shape my mouth around the notes as they pass through me, really get a feel for them. Back here though, the sound has already filtered through the meaty cores of everyone in front of me. I wanna get close."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4378
msgid "* I take Mags by the sleeve, give her a little tug, nod my head toward the stage. She rolls her eyes and takes the lead, liberally applying her elbows to everyone in our path."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4379 result.py:4466
msgid "* The chaos is more concentrated before the stage. No gaps between dancers to water it down. Just bodies churning, jumping, and yelling in the encompassing aura of the spotlights. And a metallic taste in the air."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4380 result.py:4467
msgid "* After circumnavigating a particularly tall attendee, the increased vividness up front hits us. The gleam of the lights is sharp, even in the smoggy room, and the shadows when it strobes off are deep. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4381 result.py:4468
msgid "* Can't tell if those are hologram artifacts around the figures edges, or just the shimmer of spotlights through the gore haze. I consider how much of this could reasonably be real."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4382
msgid "* I catch a glimpse of Mags every once in a while, drenched in red light, bouncing like crazy. It isn't till the fourth song in the set that she needs a breather."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4383 result.py:4470
msgid "* I follow her to the bar, where the music is no longer bumping against the upper limits of my auditory range. She takes a seat and orders another Pearl Mana cocktail."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4384
msgid "* The waiter droid crackles a response that I don't attempt to parse. My ears are ringing and it takes focus to pick Mags' voice out of the din."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4385
msgid "* Mags grabs the drink from the droid, takes a sip. * Pay the man, HC."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4386
msgid "* The droid turn to me, clawed hand outstretched. * TEN COUPONS -- PLEASE"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4387
msgid "* Pay for the drink"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4389
msgid "* I slide some coupons across the countertop. * My pleasure."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4390
msgid "* Mags rolls her eyes, unimpressed. * Woah there, big spender. Don't gotta flex."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4391
msgid "* I raise my hands. * Sorry Mags. You're on your own."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4392
msgid "* She smirks and slides some coupons across the countertop. * You really know how to show a girl a good time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4393
msgid "* Amidst so many people fully letting loose, her sarcasm seems more hollow than usual. Less cutting. I fail to stifle a laugh."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4394
msgid "* She laughs with me, as if her cold words have always been in jest. Or is this just another tactic to keep me off guard? I push the thoughts from my head. Maybe I'll drop to her level for a bit."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4395
msgid "* I change the subject. * You know, I'd have assumed you were too cool to dance. Proud of you for letting yourself look like such a dork out there."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4396
msgid "Mags: Please, nothing is worse than that. * She cocks her head towards the stragglers frozen at the back of the crowd, whose anxious head bobbing is imperceptible to anyone outside a small radius."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4397
msgid "* I grin. * I can respect it. It takes a lot of skill to do a dance that subtle."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4398
msgid "* Mags doesn't respond, just takes a deep swig from her drink."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4399
msgid "* I gesture at a pair of the immobile attendees. * That could be us..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4400
msgid "* Mags turns, tries to hide a smile. * Let's get back in there. A guy bumped me earlier and I wanna see if I can knock his ass down."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4401
msgid "* We return to the crowd hand in hand, to a scene bizarre enough that our short break resets whatever comfort with it we had developed before."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4402 result.py:4485
msgid "* The bleached figure is still using hand gestures to puppeteer the blood swarm, still pulling music up through the earth, through the stem of their flower, and into the wet air."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4403 result.py:4486
msgid "* It's all very unnerving. Occasionally their mouth opens for a choral stab and their tongue writhes behind their bloodstained teeth. They aren't droid, but I'd never guess human."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4404 result.py:4487
msgid "* Hologram almost makes sense, till I taste the ferric tang in the air or catch them remaining fully opaque when they step in front of a light."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4405 result.py:4488
msgid "* Maybe the real ESPER99 is backstage, and what we're seeing now is a glitch. Or a ghost bloodthirsty enough to manifest a whole tooth-filled meat suit."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4406
msgid "* Irrelevant, if so. The glitch is the show worth catching. Mags and I dance and get sore and sweaty, get insight into the layer of hell that the figure escaped from."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4407 result.py:4490
msgid "* When they start their final song, we can tell. The blood cloud spasms, explodes outward into a larger, more chaotic radius. ESPER99 is milking that flower for all it's worth."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4408 result.py:4491
msgid "* Geometric shapes emerge from the storm at their command. Pointillized spheres and rhomboids last for milliseconds before returning to the rhythmic, pulsing mist. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4409 result.py:4492
msgid "* Part of me wants to bite my lip, let my own conduction fluid drizzle across the void to join the cloud. Fucking gross. Instead, I let the hissing vocals erase my mind."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4410
msgid "* Mags' dancing slows to a halt, and she just stares at the stage, entranced by the shapes. I stop too, but it's to look at the crimson glint in Mags' eyes, the way the spotlights gleam on her damp shoulders."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4411
msgid "* Dunno how Mags manages to look elegant in this cauldron of meat and blood, but she does. I put an arm around her shoulder and we watch ESPER99 play out their last song."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4412 result.py:4495
msgid "* The lights shut off and the final drone cuts out. There's a moment of gentle raindrop sounds as gravity reclaims the blood. Then, the crowd erupts."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4413
msgid "* We join in the clapping. Mags remains silent, but I muster a yell. Gradually, the standard yellow lights flick back on, and the area beyond the stage become visible again."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4414
msgid "* I start to flow towards the door with the bulk of the crowd, but Mags takes my arm, guides me towards a newly-illuminated merch booth."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4415 result.py:4498
msgid "* The line is already long, which wouldn't be an issue, but a bottleneck has formed at the door and the backed up crowd will soon overwhelm the little table."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4416
msgid "* I hold fast as the crowd thickens, starts bumping into me. Mags hops, tries to get a feel for the situation."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4417
msgid "Mags: Yo, this is only gonna take a sec. Meet me outside, will you?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4418
msgid "* With the music gone, the throng has lost its appeal. I nod, and make my way for the exit."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4419 result.py:4502
msgid "* I pour out into the street with the rest of them. The desolation I usually associate with Skipnoise Ave is completely absent. Pods of friends precipitate along the sidewalk. I try and find somewhere visible to stand."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4420
msgid "* In a bit, Mags emerges from the Lemon, a white shirt rolled and tucked under her arm. I wave and she sees me, heads over."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4421
msgid "Mags: Yeah, so. They gave me the wrong size, so I guess you can have this. * She tosses me the shirt."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4422
msgid "* I unroll it. Big ESPER99 logo on the front. Some weird squiggles on the back. Neat. And the fabric is super soft."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4423
msgid "* It's an unsubtle lie. I'm a bit taller than her, but no way I to go up a full shirt size. Plus, if they had really given her the wrong shirt, she'd have slain them where they stood."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4424
msgid "Thank, Mags. * I wring the shirt in my hands. * So, did you have fun?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4425
msgid "Mags: Yeah, it was a dope show. You were smart to invite me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4426
msgid "* I snort. * Most people would just say thanks."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4427
msgid "* She rolls her eyes. * Yeah, and I suppose you want a kiss, too? Fine, if it'll get you out of here. * She leans in, hovers her lips above mine."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4428
msgid "* The disparate gesture catches me off guard, but only for a second."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4429
msgid "* Let her kiss me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4430 result.py:4510 result.py:17739
msgid "* Turn away."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4431
msgid "When she sees I'm not withdrawing, she smooches me on the mouth. Just a quick one."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4432
msgid "* Then backs off, wipes her lips, even cracks a smile. * Ok, you good? Cause I think I see someone I know over there."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4433
msgid "Mags: Self control. I can respect that."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4434
msgid "* She breaks eye contact, resumes scanning the crowd. * I'll see you later, HC. * She doesn't pause, just walks off. No looks back."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4435 result.py:4520
msgid "* I take a long draw on the cold air, mitigate some of my high battery temperature, then head home."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4436
msgid "* Beryl meets me at the door, dolled down as ever. Despite her lack of makeup, I can tell tonight is a big deal for her. She springs to my side, clings to my arm."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4437
msgid "* She looks relieved to no longer be alone out here. * HC! Hi!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4438
msgid "Hey, Beryl. How's it going?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4439
msgid "* She hugs me. * Good! I'm shy and a little nervous, but I'm t-tryna channel it into hype."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4440
msgid "* I giggle. * Is it working?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4441
msgid "Beryl: I think so! Half is t-turning to hype, half is turning to anxiety. You know how it goes. Much better now that you're here, though!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4442
msgid "Good. * I give her a squeeze. * I got you. Let's go."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4447
msgid "* Beryl leans close, talks into my ear. * Sit tight, HC. I'm gonna be right back."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4454
msgid "* Beryl appears beside me, drink in each hand. * Did I miss anything?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4456
msgid "* I beat Beryl to the first sip just as the bass cuts. All attention turns to the stage. The ring of my ice sounds weird in the sudden silence. I lift the drink to my lips, but Beryl elbows me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4465
msgid "* I take Beryl by the arm, give her a little tug, nod my head toward the stage. She nods vigorously and falls in line behind me. It takes some elbowing, but we make it through."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4469
msgid "* I catch a glimpse of Beryl every once in a while, drenched in red light, bouncing like crazy. It isn't till the fourth song in the set that she needs a breather."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4471
msgid "* The waiter droid crackles a response that I don't attempt to parse. My ears are ringing and it takes focus to pick Beryl's voice out of the din."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4472
msgid "* Beryl takes a long drink from her water, then gasps for air. Her eyes are wild and she's smiling wide. * THIS IS NUTS!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4473
msgid "Damn, Beryl. You ok?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4474
msgid "Beryl: I'm more than ok! I st-stepped on a guys toe and didn't even say sorry!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4475
msgid "Really letting loose, huh. * I pluck the glass of water from her hands, take a swig."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4476
msgid "* She giggles. * Doing my best! How are you doing out there?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4477
msgid "I'm great! Although all this blood is making me thirsty. * I take another big swig of water. * Might have to slorp you at some point."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4478
msgid "Beryl: Oh no! Vampire HC! T-too bad you're drinking... * She does a dorky evil laugh. * Holy Water!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4479
msgid "No! * I slide the glass back to her. * Fuck! Foiled by a god damn cutie pie!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4480
msgid "* Beryl giggles some more. * There's a joke about you sucking my neck here somewhere... But I don't know what it is..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4481
msgid "Don't worry, you'll have an eternity to think about it... After I suck your neck!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4482
msgid "* She groans through her smile, then finishes her water. * Gosh, that was rough, even by my standards. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4483
msgid "Beryl: C'mon, let's go back! I wanna step on more toes! * She gets up and starts to walk, then  pauses. * I'm just kidding, it was an accident. I'd never hurt a t-toe on purpose..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4484
msgid "* We return to the crowd hand in hand, to a scene bizarre enough that our short break reset whatever comfort with it we had developed before.  "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4489
msgid "* Irrelevant, if so. The glitch is the show worth catching. Beryl and I dance and get sore and sweaty, get insight into the layer of hell that the figure escaped from."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4493
msgid "* Beryl's dancing slows to a halt, and she just stares at the stage, entranced by the shapes. I stop too, but it's to look at the crimson glint in Beryl's eyes, the way the spotlights gleam on her damp shoulders."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4494
msgid "* Dunno how Beryl manages to look elegant in this cauldron of meat and blood, but she does. I put an arm around her shoulder and we watch ESPER99 play out their last song."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4496
msgid "* We join in the clapping. Beryl remains silent, but I muster a yell. Gradually, the standard yellow light flick back on, and the area beyond the stage become visible again."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4497
msgid "* I start to flow towards the door with the bulk of the crowd, but Beryl takes my arm, guides me towards a newly-illuminated merch booth."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4499
msgid "* I hold fast as the crowd thickens, starts bumping into me. Beryl hops, tries to get a feel for the situation."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4500
msgid "Beryl: I feel like this might go s-smoother if we split up. Would you meet me outside? I'll only be a sec."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4501
msgid "* With the music gone, the throng has lost its appeal. I nod, and make my way for the exit. Behind me, Beryl shouts her thanks."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4503
msgid "* In a bit, Beryl emerges from the Lemon, a white shirt rolled and tucked under her arm. I wave and she sees me, heads over."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4504
msgid "Beryl: Look! I got you a p-present! * She unrolls the shirt, displays the ESPER99 logo."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4505
msgid "* She tosses it  to me. It's super soft. * Beryl... You're so sweet, thank you so much!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4506
msgid "* Beryl giggles. * Of course! Thanks for b-bringing me to this. Shows are rare in P-Pira and I'm really happy I got to see one with you! This was... Super special... * She hugs me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4507
msgid "Beryl: You know... Right now would be a really cute time for you to kiss me..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4508
msgid "Aww, Beryl..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4509 result.py:5712 result.py:6523 result.py:7356 result.py:9846
#: result.py:16556 result.py:18599
msgid "* Kiss her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4511
msgid "* I take her shoulders, pull her in, and we kiss. Warm, but her arms prickle in the cool night air. Time to head home."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4512
msgid "* We walk south-west together, around the rim, till the voices fade and the post-show energy is subdued. The beat now is our footsteps and the distant night calls of the pit slugs."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4513
msgid "* When it comes time for our paths to part, we wait for a bit, holding hands. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4514
msgid "* She looks at the cold purple sky. * This was fun."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4515
msgid "Yeah, it really was. * I notice some flecks of red on her shirt, point at them. * You got some..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4516
msgid "* She laughs. * Oh, yeah. Maybe I'll d-do laundry tomorrow. Or something. I'll see you later, HC."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4517
msgid "Bye, Beryl."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4518
msgid "* She laughs, soft and sad, then perks back up a little. * No worries! This was a really good night. And... Yeah. I'll see you around, HC..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4519
msgid "* A quick touch, her fingers on the back of my hand, then she walks back into the crowd. East. The long way home."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4521
msgid "* Forcier didn't give me much to go on in terms of their location. Guess I'll look around Root Street a bit. Maybe I'll follow that noise..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4522
msgid "* I see Forcier crouched down in a gap in alleyway asphalt behind Decima's workshop, digging around in a pile of dirt and gravel."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4523
msgid "* Curiosity gets the best of me and I call out their name as I get closer. * Forcier! Everything all right?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4524
msgid "* Forcier tips their head up and shields their eyes from the sun with one hand. They give a warm smile when they see it's me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4525
msgid "* Forcier shakes their hands free of dirt and stands. * Ah, HC. How is the day treating you so far?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4526
msgid "Great!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4527
msgid "Could be better..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4528
msgid "Forcier: Yeah? * They set aside their shovel and stand up and I feel like they're studying my eyes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4529
msgid "Forcier: Anything in particular bothering you? * They lean forward, offering their full attention to my response."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4530
msgid "Just feeling low."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4531
msgid "Bored."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4532
msgid "I'm not sure."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4533
msgid "Forcier: Ah. * They pause. * Introspection can be a difficult task, especially amidst emotional turmoil."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4534
msgid "Forcier: Sometimes I find myself pacing through my garden for hours just trying to parse my emotions and find words to describe what I'm experiencing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4535
msgid "Forcier: I'm sorry to hear that. You know, I'm here to chat with you about anything, anytime..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4536
msgid "Forcier: Or somewhere near here, anyway... I enjoy listening. Working things out, or just finding a distraction. Whatever you'd prefer."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4537
msgid "* I belong here in the city, among new friends... I feel warmth swell in my chest. * That's really sweet, Forcier. First, though, you gotta tell me what's happening with this dirt pile!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4538
msgid "Forcier: I'm attempting to clear the ground of a particularly aggressive and robust root, but unfortunately, my abundance of effort is meeting little success."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4539
msgid "Forcier: The large root has recently begun to overwhelm the west corner of my garden. For the sake of my experiments, I'll need to exorcize it. You could help, if you wish."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4540
msgid "You have a garden?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4541
msgid "Forcier: Oh, yes I can certainly understand that. Pira seems so empty sometimes... It's easy to lose oneself in these endless ruins. * The gesture to the maze of dead concrete behind us."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4542
msgid "Yeah, exactly. I owe so much to this place, and I love it here...."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4543
msgid "It's just boring me today, I guess..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4544
msgid "Forcier: Perhaps assisting me would occupy your mind. Not a particularly challenging task for the mind, but I could use the help."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4545
msgid "Forcier: A large root has recently begun to overwhelm the west corner of my garden. For the sake of my experiments, I'll need to exorcize it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4546
msgid "Wait.. What garden?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4547
msgid "* Forcier smiles. * Really?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4548
msgid "Uh, yeah? * They study my face with their eyes which makes me feel a bit insecure. * Do I look bad?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4549
msgid "Forcier: Not at all. That's just a vague answer and I wanted to double check."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4550
msgid "Well then, yeah, I'm great! I'm just wondering aimlessly around Pira trying to find something exciting. I feel like I've found it! What's going on here?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4551
msgid "* Forcier chuckles. * This may be more frustrating than exciting. I was just fighting with this weed that has dug itself deep into my garden."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4552
msgid "This is your garden? * I look past them into what I thought was an empty space in between Decima's workshop and the Root Street Theater."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4553
msgid "How... have I never noticed this? * About thirty feet back I can see a quaint stone path leading to a clearing behind the buildings."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4554
msgid "* Forcier looks surprised. * I haven't shown you? Well, prepare for a hearty dose of botanical amazement! * They pause. * Actually, in the interest of not overselling it... Get ready for a small fun surprise."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4555
msgid "Forcier: I need an excuse to take a break from this root, anyway. * They lead me to their garden; an overgrown mess of green sprouting out of an abandoned building."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4556
msgid "* It's filled with a dark soil that seems far more fertile than the windswept concrete and micro plastic ash found elsewhere in the city. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4557
msgid "* After a moment of scrutinizing, I notice a few small green-yellow sprouts spread about the mounds of dirt and grass."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4558
msgid "* Forcier takes a deep breath beside me and exhales slowly. * My sanctuary."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4559
msgid "* At this point, I can't differentiate the sprouts from the scrubby yellow shrub grass that can be found in the more moist areas of Pira. All the equipment must have a purpose though."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4560
msgid "Oh. Cool. * I pause, unsure what to say. * Whatcha growing?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4561
msgid "Forcier: I'm testing several species during this experimental cycle. The most promising of which is a type of mountain bean recovered from deep in the wasteland beyond the edges of Pira City."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4562
msgid "* They gesture to the tiny plants. * If all goes well, it could become one of the first edible crops to grow within the city. I hold a cautious optimism that these will yield fruit."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4563
msgid "Forcier: Despite the failures of the last two cycles. * Their expression maintains its collected pride. No hint of disappointment. I can tell they love their work."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4564
msgid "Forcier: It's difficult to acquire diverse species of plants here. Especially edible ones."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4565
msgid "* They finally look towards me. * I have to get creative. Make a few deals..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4566
msgid "Deals? Like..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4567
msgid "Forcier: Whosoever is willing to spare any information or materials. I have been trading for samples, but I lack a business partner who shares my sense of purpose in this matter."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4568
msgid "Forcier: But, I'm willing to pay the cost."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4569
msgid "Oof. I hope it's not too expensive."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4570
msgid "* Forcier smiles. * I'm not sure you can put a price on what farming could mean for Pira City. Before I started this garden, I will admit that I felt hopeless at times. I know that Pira is just barely hospitable."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4571
msgid "Forcier: I also know that the rest of the world is just as bad, if not completely uninhabitable. Pollution, drought, radiation... And in the places where habitation is still possible, Megacorps."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4572
msgid "Forcier: There are so many obstacles to prosperity. These plants are my hope. I... * They breathe in, I think to avoid tearing up."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4573
msgid "Forcier: They could be the start of something much bigger. I'm not sure how, yet, logistically. I just know how important it is.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4574
msgid "That's fucking beautiful as shit. * I pause. * Sorry. That came out too aggressively..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4575
msgid "* Forcier laughs. * Aggressive is just the response I am looking for, actually."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4576
msgid "Forcier: Anyway, I had plans to transfer some new starters into the bed, but... * I follow their gaze to the massive trench leading to the sidewalk. * A Root Street root..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4577
msgid "I bet I can get that out for you, if you'd like?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4578
msgid "Forcier: I would appreciate that greatly."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4579
msgid "Forcier: Unfortunately, I have identified it as Acidbinder. Most of its mass, I believe, lies beneath the pavement of the sidewalk."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4580
msgid "Forcier: I wouldn't mind so much if it wasn't so damaging to the soil and to other organisms."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4581
msgid "Forcier: It's sneaky. Just recently it managed to disguise itself as a beautiful yellow moon pod."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4582
msgid "Forcier: That stung me. Laying eyes upon that fabled flower is one of my deepest botanical dreams. * They look up towards the sky. * In full bloom... It glows."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4583
msgid "Forcier: The acidbinder is a poor lookalike at best, though."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4584
msgid "Forcier: It's glow only lasts for a day or so, then the pods pop and emit a rather noxious smelling odor."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4585
msgid "* They have an odd grin talking about this. * It's all so fascinating, though."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4586
msgid "Forcier: I originally believed it to be a defense mechanism, but I now theorize that it is simply a waste product of the polluted water it leeches from the earth."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4587
msgid "Forcier: It's not an incredibly uncommon plant, but I'd like to dig it up and take samples. Perform some additional research."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4588
msgid "Forcier: I can't have it growing out of control in my garden. I need to keep my fragile seedlings as guarded as possible."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4589
msgid "* Forcier hunches over their baby plants with pride while talking. I'm beginning to see the bigger picture, and what these little guys mean to them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4590
msgid "Forcier: Ok, let's get that root out! * We head back to the sidewalk, following the massive root to the point that it disappears underneath Root Street."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4591
msgid "* They offer me gardening gloves that are slightly too big, and a variety of shovels. I study the jagged edges of the thing. It looks angry, like it's warning me not to mess with it..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4592
msgid "Ok, lil' root. I'm just gonna... * I pause when I hear Forcier giggling behind me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4593
msgid "Forcier: No, keep going! I apologize. I, too, have been talking to the root for the better part of the day."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4594
msgid "* I grip a spot on the root that looks the least dangerous and channel all of my strength into yanking out the plant."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4595
msgid "* Way too much energy, as it turns out. I pull backwards and it rips out violently and I land on my ass. Hard."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4596
msgid "* Forcier lets out a sharp noise, a gasp that devolves into laughter. * I suppose my arm strength is not quite what I thought it was! "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4597
msgid "* I hop up, trying to look cool. * Nah, I'm just... ridiculously strong! * Forcier looks pleased."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4598
msgid "Forcier: I can't thank you enough for this! What an absolute relief."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4599
msgid "Forcier: You know, as much as I love this place, it can get overwhelming to tend to at times..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4600
msgid "Forcier: Olivia helps occasionally but she's usually tied up with hacking and hypnotizing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4601
msgid "* They smile. * As you probably know. * Wow, they're calling me out... I blush a little and nod."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4602
msgid "Sure do! * I'm embarrassed by my cheesy answer, but they get back to the topic."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4603
msgid "Forcier: Yes, well, if you'd like, I'm always looking for friends to help out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4604
msgid "Forcier: This garden is very experimental, so the tasks may involve some research..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4605
msgid "Forcier: Also maintenance. And you can, of course, drop by anytime just to find some peace and quiet."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4606
msgid "Sounds Great!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4607
msgid "I don't want to mess up your garden..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4608
msgid "Forcier: Glad to hear it! I will notify you when I need assistance."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4609
msgid "* They clap their hands together. * I am looking forward to introducing you to my weird collection of plants!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4610
msgid "Forcier: Oh, I wouldn't be worried about that in the slightest. The conditions are monitored and automatically corrected. Or, when something unexpected occurs... * They kick the root. * I'm notified."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4611
msgid "Forcier: Additionally, I'm constantly messing up my garden. * They laugh."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4612
msgid "Forcier: Not long ago I crossbred a giant 'Deathshead Driplily', with an 'Oozing Red Bristlebulb'..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4613
msgid "Forcier: It was an attempt to create a frightening present for a horror themed party Cadence was throwing. A humanoid flower dripping with 'blood'..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4614
msgid "Forcier: Instead, the flowing chimera issued an olfactory assault that evacuated the adjacent buildings... I was quite unpopular amongst Decima's clique for a while. * They smile thinking about it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4615
msgid "Forcier: But! I learned quite a bit about the biology of these two plants in the process... So, I suppose I welcome a little mess in the name of science."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4616
msgid "You have some STRANGE plants, Forcier..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4617
msgid "Forcier: Oh, yes. Much stranger than those two, in fact. I'm excited to show you all of them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4618
msgid "Forcier: In fact, I'll have to send you off with one today, for all your help! * They gather up three small potted vegetables."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4619
msgid "Forcier: Totally inedible, I'm afraid, but not without some aesthetic charm. Which do you prefer?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4620
msgid "Forcier: This is a Gunkmelon."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4621
msgid "Forcier: The Scumato."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4622
msgid "Forcier: And, the crapcarrot... terrible name, I know."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4623
msgid "Gunkmelon."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4624
msgid "Scumato."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4625
msgid "Crapcarrot."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4626
msgid "* They grab the Gunkmelon off off their nearby workbench and give it a little water before handing it to me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4627
msgid "* They grab the Scumato off their nearby workbench and give it a little water before handing it to me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4628
msgid "* They grab the Crapcarrot off their nearby workbench and give it a little water before handing it to me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4629
msgid "Forcier: This should last for a very long time with just an occasional splash of water."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4630
msgid "Forcier: Excellent. Here you are. * They hand the plant carefully into my palms. I thank them and hold the little pot to my chest."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4631
msgid "* It's a simple gesture, but through it, I can feel so much of Forcier's warmth. I can't stop smiling during the walk back to my apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4632
msgid "* I make my way down Root Street and dip in the alley next to Decima's workshop."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4633
msgid "* The walk to their garden is kind of creepy. The alley is long and dark, randomly scattered with metal scraps and old droid parts."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4634
msgid "* Luckily, it opens up into a surprisingly lush garden of Forcier's making. It's peaceful and quiet."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4635
msgid "* Forcier is waiting for me, holding two large axes... They look serious."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4636
msgid "Forcier: Thank you for coming, HC."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4637
msgid "Forcier: I need a bit of help with a small problem in my garden building."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4638
msgid "Forcier: You'll need, * They hand me one of the axes. * One of these."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4639
msgid "You know... I do trust you and all, Forcier. But what exactly are we doing here?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4640
msgid "Forcier: Great question! Unfortunately, the best answer I can give you is simply to show you."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4641
msgid "* They lead me into a crumbling two story building, filled with mounds of dirt and spotted with dried grass."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4642
msgid "* They eye one of the crumbling support pillars as we pass. * I am still in the process of reinforcing the structural integrity, so for now it would be best to tread carefully. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4643
msgid "So, are we in danger in here? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4644
msgid "* They stop walking and turn to me. * I would estimate the danger to be moderate, but only because of the state of the building..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4645
msgid "Forcier: Also, I consider all of Pira to be moderately dangerous, if that makes any difference."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4646
msgid "Ok, yeah. Fair enough! As long as you're planning repairs, cause this thing isn't gonna stand for long..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4647
msgid "Forcier: Exactly right. And that's where you come in."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4648
msgid "* We reach the mound, a mess of concrete rubble onto which the roofs dusty runoff has been directed. The result almost resembles a pile of dirt, crowned by a bush."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4649
msgid "Oh, just a bush? You want me to chop it down? No problem."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4650
msgid "Forcier: Oh, no not at all. The bush is annoying, and semi invasive, but manageable."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4651
msgid "Forcier: However, If you look over the hill... * They lead me to the top of the grassy mound. * There's our problem."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4652
msgid "Slime. Of course. * I peer over the steep decline beyond the bush, down into what was once a basement, now opened to the air."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4653
msgid "* In its deepest recess, glinting at me from the dark, is the distinct pinkish hue associated with the slime. And it's moving."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4654
msgid "Forcier: I was working in relative peace in here until I noticed more and more of the slime creeping through the grate."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4655
msgid "Forcier: It seems to be taking up residence here, which isn't ideal... * They join me in gazing into the abyss, taking a noticeably more cautious stance."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4656
msgid "Did you tell Olivia? Or Decima? They might have some sort of weird contraption to get rid of it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4657
msgid "Forcier: Indeed. Decima had no shortage of ideas, none of which seemed completely appropriate."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4658
msgid "* They clear their throat. * Most of them involved... Fire..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4659
msgid "Forcier: And Olivia... She hasn't visited the garden much, yet. I believe she wants to let me forge my own path."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4660
msgid "She doesn't want to interfere?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4661
msgid "* Forcier pauses. * Olivia has a greater need for alone time than I do. Minimizing distraction is conducive to her productivity."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4662
msgid "Forcier: I would feel more comfortable calling on her aid once her alone time requirements have been met."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4663
msgid "Oh, that makes sense. How do you fe--"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4664
msgid "Forcier: HC, careful! * They grab my arm and wrench my body into their arms with ease."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4665
msgid "* I look back at where I was standing and see a tentacle inching up over the edge, right where my foot was a second ago."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4666
msgid "WHOA! * I grab tightly onto Forcier's torso."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4667
msgid "* Forcier chops the tentacle in half with their axe, sending chunks of gelatinous material flying. The stump retreats to the darkness to reform."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4668
msgid "Forcier: If you feel ready, there are more tentacles coming our way!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4669
msgid "* I realize with a rush of embarrassment that I am still grabbing onto them for dear life."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4670
msgid "Yep! Let's slay some slime! * And now I've added a cheesy line on top of it all..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4671
msgid "* Oh well, gotta focus."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4672
msgid "* Forcier is swinging at a swarm of slimy arms, chopping them off one by one. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4673
msgid "* Trailing behind the swarm is a stream of goo tracing back to the source..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4674
msgid "* At the bottom of the dirt hill I see a pillar of slime forming into a humanoid creature."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4675
msgid "* In the pool of slime next to the forming creature, smaller appendages try to form."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4676
msgid "* This must be a cluster of monsters, all writhing together, trying to fulfill their duty with the primitive programming imbedded in their cells."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4677
msgid "* I need to get to the source, but Forcier is struggling to deal with the tentacles they've sent up to attack..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4678
msgid "* Help Forcier."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4679
msgid "* Get to the source."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4680
msgid "* The swarm seems to be growing two arms for every one that Forcier cuts down."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4681
msgid "* Should I go for the beefier tentacles with one hard swing, or should I do a series of quick attacks at the smaller ones?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4682
msgid "* Hit hard."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4683
msgid "* Hit fast."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4684
msgid "* Best to go straight to the meat."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4685
msgid "* I brace myself, grip the handle hard, ready my swing..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4686
msgid "* And drive it through the meatiest mass within range, a mighty arch of violence that sends liquefied slime spattering through the building... * SCHLOP!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4687
msgid "* I manage to cut the swarm of tentacles from the root, leaving a squealing puddle of dying tendrils and a large trunk of slime leading down to the monster."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4688
msgid "* Forcier is getting overwhelmed by the dozens of tendrils, so I need to act fast."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4689
msgid "* I don't think too much about my strategy. I'll just swing as much as possible."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4690
msgid "* I get in real close to the mass of tentacles, focus my flurry of axe swings on the tendrils headed for Forcier. A blurred, bladed shield."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4691
msgid "* I manage to slice off at least a half dozen before they refocus their attention on me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4692
msgid "* They land a series of wet slaps that surprise me, despite their relative harmlessness."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4693 result.py:4712 result.py:4731
msgid "DODGE"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4694
msgid "* My hardwired agility is intact but not always reliable. Luckily, this time I manage to lean out of the reach of the swarm."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4695
msgid "* It makes a disappointed farting sound and coils back, readying for another try. I need to slice it when it comes in close again... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4696 result.py:4715
msgid "SLICE"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4697
msgid "I roll back, but not quite fast enough."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4698
msgid "* A stealthy tentacle lands an uppercut on my jaw, lifting me into the air and dumping me on my ass."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4699
msgid "* Forcier sprints over and slams their axe into the tentacle just as it comes in for another blow."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4700
msgid "* What's left of the damaged limb retreats back down the hillside."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4701
msgid "Forcier: HC! We must retreat! The creatures are multiplying! * They point to the slime mass at the base of the mound."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4702
msgid "* There are at least four more rudimentary looking bodies forming, and the one that is farthest along is starting to glide up to us."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4703
msgid "I'm fine! We gotta get rid of these things! * I stand up and do a quick evaluation of my body."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4704
msgid "* Just a few bruises, nothing too bad. I grab my axe and give a quick thumbs up to Forcier. They still look concerned."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4705
msgid "Forcier: Apologies, but I cannot put you in danger like this. We'll need to get help."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4706
msgid "* The biggest creature, a misshapen facsimile of the human form, is no more than 10 feet away. We don't have much of a choice now..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4707
msgid "Ok! * I grab their arm and we start to retreat."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4708
msgid "* And I completely miss..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4709
msgid "I'm going to the source!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4710
msgid "* I make my way down the mound, to the left of the slime stream."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4711
msgid "* But the half formed creature spots me and sends a ripple up the goo, forming it into large, dripping arm aimed right at me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4713
msgid "* I fall to the ground just as the giant tentacle swings over me. I catch some of the drops of goo on my cheek, but I'm spared a punch."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4714
msgid "* I don't have time to recover. The tentacle coils back and moves in, faster this time, right at my face. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4716
msgid "* Still on my back on the dirt, I wait for the slime arm to get close to me, then grab my axe and muster all the strength I can."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4717
msgid "SPLAT!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4718
msgid "* I detach the limb and watch as the monster reels back in pain and kneels down. What's left of the arm is slurped back towards the monster."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4719
msgid "* Kind of pathetic to watch, but I know it's just healing itself. I don't have time to waste."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4720
msgid "Forcier: Brilliant! * They bend down, breathing hard. * I apologize, I did not expect such an ordeal!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4721
msgid "No problem! But we aren't finished! * The creature stands, a misshapen facsimile of the human form, micro tendrils pulling the detached arm back into place."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4722
msgid "You ready? * I look at Forcier and they nod."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4723
msgid "Get behind me! * They follow me down the hill, both of our axes at the ready."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4724
msgid "* The slime monster reabsorbs its injured limb and focuses its bubbling, eyeless face in our direction."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4725
msgid "* I have to decide the best course of action to defeat this beast..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4726
msgid "* Get in close."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4727
msgid "* Throw the axe."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4728
msgid "* I decide to rush down the hill. Maybe I can decapitate this monster before it knows what's up. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4729
msgid "* The monster deploys a tentacle my way. Looks like this thing has the same idea as me..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4730
msgid "* the whip-like tendril is swinging fast right at my neck."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4732
msgid "* I roll back, but not quite fast enough."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4733
msgid "* It smacks me in the throat. It may have wanted to slice my head off, but there's only so much a slime rope can do..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4734
msgid "* It does, however, manage to whack my axe out of my hands, far out of reach."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4735
msgid "* All the while, a few new tentacles form and start to snake back towards me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4736 result.py:4744
msgid "SPLORT!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4737 result.py:4745
msgid "* Despite being able to land hefty slaps, they are easily destroyed with my droid strength punch."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4738
msgid "* I can't stop to think too hard. I swing the axe back, aim for the face, and throw as hard as possible."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4739
msgid "* It flies through the air in a glorious arc, headed straight for hoard of monsters."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4740
msgid "* The slime monster blocks it just in time with it's almost formed arm."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4741
msgid "* It tries to create fingers good enough to grip the handle, the shapes straining to work together."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4742
msgid "* All the while, a few new tentacles form and try to snake thirstily towards my crotch."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4743
msgid "NOT TODAY U WRETCHED CREATURE! NOT AFTER U STOLE MY FRIENDS AXE!!!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4746
msgid "* It gains on us fast, though, and send out extra tentacles to keep us off balance."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4747
msgid "* One of them slaps at my arm, hard enough that I can feel some of the slime stick to my joints, trying to sneak inside.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4748
msgid "* I quickly scrape off the slime, and we slap away as much slime as we can, but I'm starting to think that this building may be toast."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4749
msgid "* There are at least ten individual slime forms now, in different stages of growth, gliding up the hill..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4750
msgid "* Then a fireball erupts in front of us, the three monsters disappear in a blinding white light for a moment, then... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4751
msgid "* Decima crests the mound, some ungodly machine of blackest iron slung at her waist, wreathed in tubes of mismatched colors, flames snorting from its long, rainbow-tempered neck. * FOR HORSEHAT! "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4752
msgid "* Chunks of slime cubes are falling around us, tumbling down the dirt mound, gathering against the back wall in a giant puddle."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4753
msgid "Decima: Ok, that was fucking better than I thought it'd be! I mean, you saw that, right!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4754
msgid "* We both turn and see Decima, standing on the very top of the dirt mound, brandishing her garbage-cobbled blaster, grinning like a madwoman."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4755
msgid "* She looks..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4756
msgid "Decima: Heroic, am I right! I'm like a freaking superhero up here!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4757
msgid "* She grabs one of Forcier's hoses and yanks it down the hill and sprays the goo back towards the basement drain."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4758 result.py:4827
msgid "* Once satisfied that the slime is contained, she pulls an aerosol can from her belt and begins blasting. A foul smelling, foaming material plugs up the drain, then hardens into a shiny, rubbery mass."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4759 result.py:4828
msgid "* I realize both of us have just been staring down at her, speechless."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4760 result.py:4829
msgid "Forcier: Impressive. I wonder, though, if that material is... um... Environmentally friendly?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4761 result.py:4830
msgid "* She gives it a final couple of squirts. * Friendlier than that slime, am I right?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4762
msgid "* She looks back up at us, smiling proud. * So, wanna tell me why you didn't invite me to this lil' party?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4763
msgid "Forcier: Oh, Decima. I apologize. I would have, it's just... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4764
msgid "Forcier: Well, your idea. It sounded a bit..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4765
msgid "Decima: Explosive, yeah. Nah, it's all good. Luckily I was testing out a new toy in the alley and heard some commotion!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4766
msgid "Decima: I am so telling this story to Cadence... She's gonna be so fuckin' impressed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4767
msgid "* Forcier smiles. * That much is certain. I'm just glad the building didn't collapse..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4768
msgid "* They gaze around. * speaking of which, we should probably get out of here. That couldn't have been good for the structural integrity."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4769 result.py:4840
msgid "Decima: Great call! "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4770 result.py:4841
msgid "* The air outside is a pleasant change from the weird, musty smell that slimes produce..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4771 result.py:4842
msgid "* We walk through the alley, back to Root Street."
