msgid "* They grip my head tighter and I can feel their metallic knees wobble. They cry out. * I apologize, I think...."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4996
msgid "* Their orgasm catches me by surprise, and their magnificent glowing cock spurts loads of cum into my mouth, down my throat."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4997
msgid "* I manage to swallow everything, despite my shock, and they collapse onto the couch and pull me close to them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4998
msgid "Forcier: I think I may be close to orgasm, is what I was attempting to articulate... * They eventually say, after several moments of lustful silence."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:4999
msgid "Is that right? * I laugh."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5000
msgid "* They cradle me in their arms for a while, before going into the bathroom to clean up and take a shower."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5001
msgid "Forcier: Oh! Olivia should be back any minute. Could you put those seeds in my seed box? It's under the couch. * They peak their head out of the bathroom and point at the box."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5002
msgid "Yep! * I rummage around until I see a small magnetically clasped box labelled, 'Forcier's garden seeds'."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5003 result.py:5036
msgid "* I tilt open the box and place the seeds on top of a few other similar packs. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5004 result.py:5037
msgid "* As I start to close it up again, something catches my eye. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5005 result.py:5038
msgid "* A picture of Forcier is sticking out at the bottom of the box. I look at the bathroom door, then back down. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5006 result.py:5039
msgid "* Without thinking I grab it and yank it out of the box."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5007 result.py:5040
msgid "* My breath catches in my throat. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5008 result.py:5041
msgid "* It's the manor district. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5009 result.py:5042
msgid "* My manor district. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5010 result.py:5043
msgid "* It's an ID badge with Forcier's face on it, 'Crystalica City Hall Employee'. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5011 result.py:5044
msgid "* Now my mind is racing... Forcier... Crystalica. Is this some sort of weird joke?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5012 result.py:5045
msgid "* Or worse... Were they sent here? For me... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5013 result.py:5046
msgid "* Just then I hear the doorknob turning, and Olivia opens the door. I shove the badge back in, close the little magnetic tab. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5014 result.py:5047
msgid "Olivia: Hey HC! "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5015 result.py:5048
msgid "* I feel trapped all of a sudden, but I force myself to take a deep breath. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5016 result.py:5049
msgid "* There has to be a logical explanation... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5017 result.py:5050
msgid "Olivia! How'd Decima like your upgrade? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5018 result.py:5051
msgid "* Olivia jumps on the couch next to me. * Not to brag or anything, but... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5019 result.py:5052
msgid "Olivia: She was super impressed! "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5020
msgid "Olivia: Your hypno-speriences are about to level up! "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5021
msgid "* A moan emits from the bathroom and Olivia chuckles. * Forcier couldn't wait to pleasure themselves, huh? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5022
msgid "Wow, they must be at it again! We just, well I just helped them, you know..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5023
msgid "* Olivia is grinning. * They just cannot get enough, can they!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5024 result.py:5055
msgid "Olivia: Oh Forcieeeer! * She sings and taps on the bathroom door. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5025 result.py:5056
msgid "Forcier: Just! * They moan, and then it's quiet for a moment... * A second! "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5026 result.py:5057
msgid "* The door opens and they walk out, a huge grin on their face. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5027 result.py:5058
msgid "Forcier: Oh, hello Olivia! I was just... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5028
msgid "Right, Ok I'll meet you back at your place, then! * I laugh quietly as they speed walk back to their apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5029
msgid "Forcier: I'll be just a few minutes! * they yell through the bathroom door as I walk in."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5030
msgid "* Not a problem! * I laugh and take a seat on their couch. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5031
msgid "* They're still so shy about their new dick, which is adorable. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5032
msgid "* I can hear muffled whimpers seeping through the bathroom walls. They're trying not to be too loud, I'm sure. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5033
msgid "* As I wait, I take the package of seeds out of my pocket.. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5034
msgid "Do you want--- * The seeds anywhere in particular, I was going to say, but I'm cut off by a loud gasp from Forcier... There's no way they can hear me. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5035
msgid "Never mind! * I giggle. I notice their small seed box on the coffee table and figure that's probably where they want them. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5053
msgid "Olivia: You're hypno-speriences are about to level up! "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5054
msgid "* Another moan emits from the bathroom and Olivia chuckles. * Forcier couldn't wait to pleasure themselves, huh? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5059
msgid "Forcier: Taking a shower... And possibly relieving myself..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5060
msgid "Olivia: Mhmmm. * She bursts out laughing.. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5061
msgid "Forcier: Yes, it can be quite inconvenient... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5062
msgid "* Olivia makes a space for them and falls into their arms. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5063
msgid "Olivia: Hey, making up for lost time. I get it, babe!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5064
msgid "Forcier: Yes, I suppose that's what's happening."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5065
msgid "* Olivia and Forcier cuddle up next to me on their couch. Olivia switches on a monitor on her wall. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5066
msgid "Olivia: Wanna watch a little movie I found? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5067
msgid "Forcier: I would love to. HC? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5068
msgid "* I have the urge to ask about the ID badge, but I'm nervous to know the answer... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5069
msgid "* Instead I blurt out-- * I actually gotta go... Uh, but I'll see you soon! "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5070
msgid "* I make a more awkward exit that I wanted to. I know there has to be some explanation that isn't sinister..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5071
msgid "* Forcier couldn't lie to me if they wanted, I know that."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5072
msgid "* I'll work up the courage to ask them next time we meet. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5073
msgid "* That Crystalica ID is still on my mind. City hall. The nexus of law in the land of oppulence. Home to those who enforced my subservience."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5074
msgid "* Maybe they just vacationed there. The ID was old... It's hard to imagine a human crossing those black, razor-glass dunes for something so casual... There's no transport to Pira."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5075
msgid "* It's nothing, though. It has to be nothing. They're my friend. There's no reason for me to be haunted like this."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5076
msgid "* I'm barely taking in the crumpled sidewalk below me. Broken glass crackles like dead leaves from Crystalica's curated gardens.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5077
msgid "* I'm spiraling hard for no good reason. I hate how helpless I feel. How cruel. Like the only time I can open the valve that holds back the vitriol is when it's pointed at someone I care about."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5078
msgid "* Forcier is usually in one of two places on Root Street. I'll check their apartment first."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5079
msgid "* Olivia answers the door. The room is lit only by her array of flickering monitors. Pulsing electronic music blasting from somewhere out of sight."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5080
msgid "Olivia: Forcier's at their garden. Sorry, I'm super in my creativity mode so if you wanna hang out we can, but it won't be fun... For you, anyway."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5081
msgid "As tempting as that sounds, I'll just go see what Forcier's up to."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5082
msgid "Olivia: Disappointing. * They crack a smile. * But understandable. They left like an hour ago."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5083
msgid "Olivia: Come back soon so I can test out some new tech on y--... So we can test some tech together."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5084
msgid "* I nod as she shuts the door, sealing away the fan noises and computer heat."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5085
msgid "* Next stop, East Root street. That garden they're always tending. Follow the back ways till the footprints change from dust to mud."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5086
msgid "* Forcier's garden is quiet and I enter it feeling like a loaded gun. Cool air and a gentle breeze, but fire in my head."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5087
msgid "* Most of Pira has a distinct chemical smell and a multi colored haze from the endless pollution clouds hovering over us, but it feels less oppressive here."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5088
msgid "* Walking into their garden feels like finding an oasis. Even if it's mostly full of weeds right now, the air feels cleaner. It must get somewhat filtered through the plants."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5089
msgid "* Maybe that's just my imagination. I don't know what to trust right now. Hopefully I can figure out what's happening."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5090
msgid "* Forcier is on their hands and knees wrenching less desirable flora from where it's invaded their bed. They smile soft and calm against the jagged backdrop of concrete and the skeletal skyscrapers.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5091
msgid "* Ok, here it goes. * Hey, Forcier. How, uh, how's it going?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5092
msgid "* They turn towards me and smile, *  Oh, hello HC. * They pause, wipe some dirt off their hands."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5093
msgid "* Forcier lays down the trowel, ponders. * How is it going...."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5094
msgid "* Of course they aren't satisfied with a quick 'fine' or 'OK'. They contemplate for a few seconds."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5095
msgid "Forcier: I am making strong progress with my garden, but the theraputic effect this place usually has is evading me, at present.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5096
msgid "Forcier: Ambivalent, in a word. Olivia is on my mind."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5097
msgid "Oh, yeah? * I crouch next to them, press a palm into the rich soil. * What about her?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5098
msgid "Forcier: Her work has her in somewhat of a trance, and I've found it difficult to engage her in conversation."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5099
msgid "Forcier: Self care. I need to figure out... * They dig their nails into the dirt at the base a weed, grapple with the bulb."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5100
msgid "* I pick up the trowel and shoo their fingers away. The right tool makes it easy."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5101
msgid "Forcier: I have a deep graditude for my garden. It's important work, I think. Even if it sometimes feels like I'm doing it for selfish reasons."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5102
msgid "* I'm momentarily distracted from my idiot anxieties to wonder how their garden could be considered selfish."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5103
msgid "Well, cool? About your plants. And sorry about your thoughts, being all over the place and everything."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5104
msgid "Forcier: Not to worry. They'll settle soon enough."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5105
msgid "Forcier: Now... * They turn to me, genuine interest blossoming in their eyes. * How are you doing?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5106
msgid "* This can't be sinister, right? They're not some trust fund fuck larping poverty. They feel as Pira as anyone. Maybe I should just ask them..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5107
msgid "I'm fine!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5108
msgid "* Confront them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5109
msgid "I'm fine! * I say enthusiastically. I'm not sure how to confront them. I'll have to bring it up casually."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5110
msgid "* I notice Forcier isn't saying anything, just waiting. Oh, right. They want more details."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5111
msgid "And... I am also grateful for your plants. And you! I think... * Hmmm... I think that I can't think of anything else to say..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5112
msgid "* Forcier sits in the silence for a while. They seem more comfortable with it than I am."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5113
msgid "So, yeah! That's how I am! * I give them a weak smile, almost apologetic."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5114
msgid "Forcier: I'm glad you are doing fine."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5115
msgid "Forcier: Would you like to stay around for a bit? I could use some company."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5116
msgid "Why do you have an ID card from Crystalica?!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5117
msgid "* It comes out way louder and more aggressively than planned."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5118
msgid "* It's difficult to read Forcier's expression. * Where did you see that?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5119
msgid "* My thoughts are a hypocrisy pileup. You couldn't scrape together a single soul from all the people in Crystalica, but I know Forcier to be bright, alive, human."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5120
msgid "It was... it wasn't on purpose. I saw it in the seed box."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5121
msgid "* They're silent. I know if I open my mouth to elaborate, I'll say something stupid. The urge to burn the bridge, avoid this microscopic confrontation, is resounding."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5122
msgid "I just want to know if you're... * If you're what? Kin with the people who turned my life to hell?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5123
msgid "* As if they could read the dumb thoughts through my face, Forcier takes me hand.  * Oh, HC. No."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5124
msgid "Forcier: No, I have the ID card because, well..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5125
msgid "Forcier: I suppose I have it just as one reminder of how far I've come..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5126
msgid "Yeah, of course. What are you up to?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5127
msgid "Forcier: I would love some companionship while I clear out these weeds. * They point to a tangley mess of gray, prickley shrubs."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5128
msgid "* A second trowel is produced and we sit on opposite sides of the nest of weeds. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5129
msgid "Forcier: Once I get this bed cleared out, I'll plant the row of Sea Lilies for Olivia."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5130
msgid "Forcier: They bloom in shades of blue and purple, then fiery red in their declining weeks."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5131
msgid "Forcier: And there, at the end of the bed, maybe a bench? I'm not sure yet."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5132
msgid "Forcier: It may be wishful thinking. She tells me she loves my garden... * Forcier swallows. * However, she is reluctant join me in my little haven. Facsimile though it may be."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5133
msgid "You dont think she'll visit?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5134
msgid "Forcier: I would just like to strengthen the probability that she'll visit out of something other than an obligation to me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5135
msgid "Forcier: At the same time, I'm unsure if doing all of this will have the adverse effect of... I'm not sure. Seeming needy, perhaps. An accidental coersion. Emotional... * They trail off."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5136
msgid "* Brittle fibers of a prickly root crumble between their fingers. They flick them to the wind."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5137
msgid "* I'm not fully listening. My mind is in Crystalica, among sycophantic grins, the clinking of glasses. Trying to picture Forcier in the mix."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5138
msgid "*  They continue. * I suppose I'll just have to take that risk. * They move onto another pile of weeds."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5139
msgid "Forcier: This one, here. I swear I pulled it a month ago. Won't stop coming up. * They grunt, pull at it. * ...Won't let me-- * Another yank..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5140
msgid "Forcier: Root it out! * On the third pull it rips out of the ground and they tumble backwards, holding the sickly pink tuber."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5141
msgid "Forcier: I am always in awe of the way plants manage to found themselves so firmly in the earth."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5142
msgid "* They toss the root into the compost pile. * Especially the irritating ones."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5143
msgid "Forcier: Someday Pira is going to be filled with beautiful plants. * They smile thinking about it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5144
msgid "Forcier: I imagine it being a maze of green vines and trees and a rainbow of flowers."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5145
msgid "The Manor District had beautiful plants and gardens. One of the only good things about it, I guess..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5146
msgid "* I watch their face as I say this, look for any change in emotion, but there's nothing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5147
msgid "* I have to confront them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5148
msgid "You know more about it than you're letting on, don't you? About Crystalica..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5149
msgid "* They look up at me, confused.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5150
msgid "* I stare, wishing this had gone more like it had in my head. Gotcha, Forcier! Can't pull one over on old HC!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5151
msgid "The ID... I found it in a crate... Your picture..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5152
msgid "* A sad smile creases their eyes. * I grew up in a Manor District in Crystalica."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5153
msgid "Oh... * This is all that I can think to say. I have so many questions. I didn't think anyone left my district..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5154
msgid "* I try to imagine Forcier growing up behind the wall, suited, sipping on a cocktail mixed with the last of earths lifeblood. It's not computing..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5155
msgid "Why didn't you tell me? * I try to make this sound as gentle as possible, but I'm so confused. It's like my main thing. I'm that fucked up droid from that place everyone hates."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5156
msgid "Forcier: I haven't been for years. It's just a memory, now..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5157
msgid "* Forcier cringes. The slight disruption to their normal calm carries weight I can only guess at."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5158
msgid "* They turn from me, hold themselves stiffly, braced against a torrent of past trauma. * Manor Districts find you quite ...Disposable... If you don't hold up to their standards."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5159
msgid "* I look at their legs, metal trunks of brutal trees powering up through the parking-lot periphery of the garden."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5160
msgid "* They look back, sympathy in their glistening eyes. * Not a lesson you need to be taught, I'm sure."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5161
msgid "* I nod, try not to show my gritted teeth, try not to let my mind slip any further back to those days. But I can't help it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5162
msgid "* The superficial charm of the place, the perfectly coiffed lawns, the practiced smiles of the residents. I was load-bearing hardware installed in memory hell. The nail that hammers itself."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5163
msgid "* I shake my head. * Yeah... There isn't room for mistakes..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5164
msgid "Forcier: There isn't room for anything less than perfection."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5165
msgid "* They start digging up roots again, more aggressively now. I realize I stopped working a while ago."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5166
msgid "* I pick my trowel back up and dig around lazily, putting on a show of productivity more than anything. The silence is uncomfortable, but now that feels right."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5167
msgid "* Forcier works their trowel around a large root. * I had a quiet, comfortable job maintaining the gardens at City Center."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5168
msgid "Forcier: I was oblivious, honestly. I had no idea about the working conditions underground. The invisible infrastructure. Factories, heating systems, power generators."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5169
msgid "* They look at me, their usual gentle expression is less controlled, almost vulnerable."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5170
msgid "Forcier: Did you hear about the incident at City Hall?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5171
msgid "* I shake my head. I only have a few memories of the place; escorting Mr. or Mrs. Laurence to balls and dinners."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5172
msgid "Forcier: I didn't think you would. It's been completely forgotten, I'm sure. It was years before your time..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5173
msgid "Forcier: The council had been wanting to renovate the city hall for a while."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5174
msgid "Forcier: They decided on a controlled implosion, to completely rebuild it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5175
msgid "Forcier: I looked at the designs for it. * They smile. * It was breathtaking."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5176
msgid "Forcier: The Gardens would be sprawling. It would turn the entire roof into a small park, with a trail winding through it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5177
msgid "Forcier: They hired a private company to implode the structure, who insisted they could set it all up while everyone was still working."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5178
msgid "Forcier: You know, to have the absolute least downtime in work hours."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5179
msgid "Forcier: I was tasked with transferring plants to a temporary greenhouse. My manager told me it was safe to work even until the morning of the implosion."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5180
msgid "Forcier: I was on the north terrace, removing a particularly beautiful Tangled Wisteria... * They squeeze their eyes shut."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5181
msgid "* I know where this is going and it makes me feel nauseous. I want to tell them it's ok, that they can stop, but my own shit has me frozen."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5182
msgid "* They must sense my worry..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5183
msgid "Forcier: I'm all right, though. * They give me a small smile. * It's more of a dull pain, now. I've worked through it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5184
msgid "Forcier: I don't remember the explosion, just waking up in the hospital."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5185
msgid "Forcier: I only survived because I was with my plants, farther away from the main building."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5186
msgid "Forcier: After the hospital, I learned how disposable I had become. Without the ability to work at full speed for the city, I was rejected."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5187
msgid "Even though it was their fault, right!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5188
msgid "Forcier: The aftermath was a flurry of propaganda, speeches, promises, plans. None of which addressed the dead, helping the injured, or involved accountability in any way."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5189
msgid "Forcier: I left."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5190
msgid "* I don't know what to say... The Crystalica I knew was a minute world made of up only a handful of people in a single house. The politics were familial. The conflict was personal. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5191
msgid "Forcier: I hope I haven't overwhelmed you again."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5192
msgid "No, no. Or, maybe. I dunno... But I'm really glad you told me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5193
msgid "Just another reason to hate Crystalica, you know? And... Well I'm glad you got out of there, but I'm sorry it had to be like that."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5194
msgid "* Another silence, cut with the occasional jab of trowels into dry, packed earth."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5195
msgid "Forcier: That became serious venting before I realized it. I'm the one who should be sorry, HC."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5196
msgid "No, I'm overwhelmed because... I've been dreading my past finding me here. Not that you're a part of all that! I'm just...."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5197
msgid "* I realize how ridiculous this sounds now, after everything they've told me. But they just nod."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5198
msgid "Forcier: I'm so sorry I led you to believe that by witholding this information."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5199
msgid "Forcier: I hope I've cleared things up."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5200
msgid "Yeah, everything makes sense. My thoughts just spiraled I guess. * They reach forward and grab my hand."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5201
msgid "* We sit in silence for a bit, but it's not uncomfortable anymore."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5202
msgid "* I'm just enjoying the feeling of their hand in mine."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5203
msgid "* After a while, I ask, * How did you end up here?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5204
msgid "Forcier: I had long distance friends who set me up with transport. It wasn't dramatic."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5205
msgid "Forcier: Olivia was doing missions for them. Offered me a place at her apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5206
msgid "Forcier: She got me everything I needed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5207
msgid "Forcier: She stole the best prosthetics she could find from Crystalica, just for me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5208
msgid "Forcier: And she introduced me to everyone I know."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5209
msgid "Forcier: I don't want to recreate the gardens of Crystalica. I want something vital, with healthy roots. Something independent. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5210
msgid "Forcier: And I'm starting here. * She picks up a weed, then chuckles. * It's going to take some time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5211
msgid "Yeah, but I love it. Really. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5212
msgid "* We clear out the bed eventually. I can see it being a peaceful place for Olivia. This is one of the quietest places in Pira."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5213
msgid "* Before I leave in the evening, Forcier shows me another bed towards the edge of the garden, a small raised planter that is covered with debris and weeds."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5214
msgid "Forcier: I'm at a loss at what to do with this particular bed. But I want to offer it to you to use, if you'd like? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5215
msgid "Yeah! That sounds great, Forcier! Thanks. * Then I give them a big hug, and they hug me back."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5216
msgid "* They smile. * It might take a while to clean it out, get the rest of the garden in working order. But I'll let you know. * They keep working as I head out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5217
msgid "* I leave the garden and notice I haven't taken a good breath in a while."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5218
msgid "* It isn't until I exhale that I realize I'm feeling immense relief. I mean, I'm angry that they went through what they did at the hands of Crystalica."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5219
msgid "* But that just means we can relate on a deeper level. They're just Forcier, my friend."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5220
msgid "* As I head back to my place, I can't help but smile."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5221
msgid "* This afternoon it's chilly outside, and I notice that the thin plastic walls don't do nearly enough to insulate the apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5222
msgid "* I'm debating whether or not to crawl back into my warm bed and call it a day, when I hear a knock at the door and Forcier's voice."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5223
msgid "Forcier: Are you available, HC?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5224
msgid "* I open the door to let them in. * Hey, Forcier, What's up!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5225
msgid "Forcier: I was hoping to show you my progress on Olivia's garden bed. I have it just about finished, but I would love your input."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5226
msgid "Forcier: That is the main reason for my visit, however I am also feeling rather spontaneous today and decided to drop by."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5227
msgid "Forcier: And now... Well, now I'm here, hoping I'm not interrupting anything? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5228
msgid "Only me sitting on my bed trying to think of something to do! * I step aside and let them in."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5229
msgid "* They have to duck slightly to get in through the low doorframe, and my ceiling is only a couple inches above them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5230
msgid "Sorry about the low ceilings. One of the many reasons they call this the Crappy Apartment Building."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5231
msgid "* Forcier smiles. * Is that what they call it? I don't know, this isn't all that bad..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5232
msgid "Forcier: Anyway, these legs are the issue."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5233
msgid "Forcier: I adore them, of course, but Olivia's only option when picking out a size was about four inches taller than my previous legs."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5234
msgid "Oh, that makes sense. She probably couldn't ask the Crystalica people to customize them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5235
msgid "For the record, though, I also adore your legs."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5236
msgid "Forcier: Thank you, HC.  I adore your legs as well, if we are stating matters for the record."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5237
msgid "* They pause, a slightly devious smile forming. * As well as other parts of you..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5238
msgid "* I can't hold back my smile. * Are you... flirting?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5239
msgid "Forcier: I believe I was attempting to? Very poorly."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5240
msgid "Forcier: It is not something that comes easily to me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5241
msgid "No, it was amazing. Really. I like all the other parts of you too, if you know... what I'm sayin'. * I wink, then cringe."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5242
msgid "Wow, ok, talk about bad at flirting. Sorry you had to witness that."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5243
msgid "* Forcier chuckles. * I enjoyed it. * They hold my gaze for a few seconds. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5244
msgid "Forcier: May I kiss you?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5245
msgid "* The most Forcier way to initiate a kiss, sweet but direct."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5246
msgid "* Accept."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5248
msgid "Yes, you may kiss me. * I'll keep it as formal as they'd like."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5249
msgid "* Forcier has to bend over just slightly, Letting me meet their lips half way."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5250
msgid "* Their kiss is gentle, thoughtful. They don't grab me or touch me, something that I'd find awkward with anyone else, but this just seems to be Forcier's method."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5251
msgid "* When they speak, their voice is calm, but a little breathy."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5252
msgid "Forcier: You must have a lot of... Experience."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5253
msgid "* They open their eyes finally and compose themselves, * What I mean to say is, you are a great kisser."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5254
msgid "You must have a lot of... Experience as well. * I smile. * You are also a great kisser."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5255
msgid "Forcier: That is kind. * They let their eyes trail downwards."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5256
msgid "Forcier: I would love to keep going..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5257
msgid "What do you want to do?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5259
msgid "Forcier: I think, * They step closer to me and I feel their lips brush against mine, but then they tilt their head to the side."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5260
msgid "Forcier: Your neck..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5261
msgid "* Their hair brushes against my cheeks as they place their lips against my neck, teasing me with gentle kisses."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5262
msgid "* Then they move down to my chest. * Your shoulders. * They kneel down..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5263
msgid "Forcier: May I? * They have my shirt in their hands."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5264
msgid "* I can hardly get the words out, but I manage a breathy, * Yeah."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5265
msgid "* They slip it off with care, folding it up and placing it beside them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5266
msgid "* They run their hands over my chest, sending chills racing up and down my body, and a sharp intake of breath."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5267
msgid "* They place their soft, warm lips all over my chest with small kisses, not lingering anywhere, enjoying every section of me they encounter."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5268
msgid "* I feel my face burning hotter and hotter as they draw circles around my breasts with their fingers."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5269
msgid "Forcier: Is this ok? * They whisper and their warm breath tickles me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5270
msgid "* I manage a smile and a smaller, quieter 'Yes'. I'm weak in my knees now, and I have to drape my arms across them to stay upright.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5271
msgid "* They kiss each of my hardened nipples, slowly and carefully."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5272
msgid "* I can imagine them studying my body as thoroughly as they do my emotions, taking account of every whimper and twitch."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5273
msgid "* It becomes unbearably intimate being examined, every inch of me being picked apart so lovingly and cautiously."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5274
msgid "* I take a breath, place my hand on their chin and guide their eyes up to mine."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5275
msgid "* Their eyes are filled with lust but somehow look more kind and gentle than ever."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5276
msgid "I want to kiss you again."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5277
msgid "Forcier: I would love that. * They stand back up, towering over me again, and they lift my chin up, gaze into my eyes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5278
msgid "* Then they bend down and kiss me once again."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5279
msgid "* This time it's somehow even better. They pull me close to their body and I can feel my breasts against the fabric of their shirt."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5280
msgid "* I run my hands across their chest and feel their quickening heart beat."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5281
msgid "* Then I pull them back against my chest and kiss them one more time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5282
msgid "* They slide their hands down my abdomen until they reach my hips, fingers exploring dangerously close to my crotch. They reach for my panties and slide them over..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5283
msgid "* They're just teasing me, though. They release their lips from mine and smile down at me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5284
msgid "Forcier: I've got to show you the garden before dark."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5285
msgid "* I sigh, wanting more. * Oh, yeah..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5286
msgid "Forcier: Trust me, you will love it. Come on."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5287
msgid "Let's save that for later. I wanna check out the garden!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5288
msgid "Forcier: Of course. I believe you will find it is growing quite well."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5289
msgid "* As we round the corner onto Root Street, Forcier looks over at me. * I did want to check in..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5290
msgid "* I look up. Their brow is furrowed. * What's up?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5291
msgid "Forcier: Are you still all right? After my slightly clunky revelation about my beginnings in Crystalica."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5292
msgid "Forcier: I hope this is obvious, but I have never been on board with their governing methods."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5293
msgid "Yeah, * I smile. * I don't feel anything negative towards you, Forcier."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5294
msgid "* And now they're doing that thing where they look deep into my soul, search my eyes for any sign of hesitancy."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5295
msgid "Forcier: I don't mind if you do have negative emotions. That just means I have more explaining to do."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5296
msgid "* Forcier smiles as we round the corner to the garden. * And I do love explaining."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5297
msgid "Well, I'll definitely let you know if I need something explained. Don't worry."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5298
msgid "Really. If anyone understands what you went through, it should be me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5299
msgid "* I do feel better knowing that Forcier understands the surreal hell-scape that is Crystalica."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5300
msgid "Forcier: Thank you for believing me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5301
msgid "* As we reach the end of the alleyway, Forcier slows down and takes a deep breath. * You can already smell the Sea Lilies."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5302
msgid "* I take a deep breath as well. I do notice a distinctly strong, fresh scent."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5303
msgid "Forcier: Mmm. Slightly sweet, crisp, citrusy even."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5304
msgid "Forcier: Mostly, they remind me of pictures that I see of wildflowers in mountain meadows."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5305
msgid "Forcier: When I am working here in my garden I like to imagine I'm in those images. * They lead me over to the Sea Lilies in Olivia's garden bed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5306
msgid "* They've grown considerably since I was here last. They are just about to bloom; the petals transition their colors from a deep purple at the base all the way to a light blue at the very tip."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5307
msgid "Forcier: Aren't they incredible? * They cradle one of the flowers in their fingers and bend down to take a deep breath."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5308
msgid "* There's a metal bench set up against the wall of the bed, surrounded by the vegetation. * I find sitting in the bench lends itself to fully experiencing the flowers."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5309
msgid "* I take a seat. Forcier smiles at me, waiting for a reaction, I assume."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5310
msgid "This is really cool, Forcier. * I probably don't get quite the satisfaction that Forcier does, but this garden bed is undoubtedly the most beautiful spot in Pira."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5311
msgid "Forcier: Isn't it? These Sea Lilies in particular used to grow wild around giant trees. I'll show you, * they hurry over to a small shed and return with a large book."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5312
msgid "* The cover has been torn off and most of the pages are detached from the binding, but the photos are brilliant."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5313
msgid "Forcier: I don't know where these pictures are from, but this is what the world used to look like... * They sit on the bench next to me to show me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5314
msgid "* Forcier flips through pages of endless meadows and mountain ranges. Most surprising of all are the clear blue skies, seemingly devoid of any pollution."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5315
msgid "* My gaze moves from the pages to the garden and back as I try to imagine massive trunks of ancient trees jutting up hundreds of feet around them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5316
msgid "Are they all gone? * The tallest plant I've seen around Pira couldn't have been more than seven feet."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5317
msgid "Forcier: I suppose that the small shrubs growing in Pira are relatives of these trees... And the ones in Crystalica grew up to around twenty five to thirty feet."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5318
msgid "Forcier: These plants are nothing if not resilient, though."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5319
msgid "* I notice the tendrils of the Sea Lily's vines twist their way to the nearest wall or branch or railing, even tangling itself together to climb upwards."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5320
msgid "Forcier: We've managed to drive most species to extinction, but I'd imagine that these plants will eventually grow back as strong as ever."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5321
msgid "Forcier: If the photos are to be believed, they used to span thousands of miles."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5322
msgid "Forcier: Those trees used to provide the oxygen for the world that the Gel Corp Breath machines do for Pira today."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5323
msgid "* They keep flipping through the pages until they land on a photo, or I think it's a photo anyway, of a vast mountain scape."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5324
msgid "* It looks unreal, completely clear skies over hundreds of mountain peaks and a seemingly infinite number of trees."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5325
msgid "Forcier: I can't say for sure, however I believe, * They run their fingers across the page. * Pira City is somewhere around here."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5326
msgid "How do you know that?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5327
msgid "Forcier: Do you recall, back in Crystalica, the tour groups?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5328
msgid "* I nod. The richest Crystalica citizens were able to travel to ancient ruins with guides, using backpacks that generated enough oxygen for a few days."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5329
msgid "Forcier: I would have given anything to go on one, after listening in on a few stories that the travelers returned with."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5330
msgid "Forcier: They had books like these as well as old tracking chips that they used to mark off locations that they believed they found."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5331
msgid "I'm guessing they didn't look like these pictures?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5332
msgid "Forcier: Oh, no. The only real trees that grow are in Manor Districts, so out there... It's all bare, unfertile dirt."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5333
msgid "Thousands of miles of dirt..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5334
msgid "* Forcier and I sit on the edge of Oliva's garden bed, flipping through more pages."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5335
msgid "Forcier: I can't imagine this city in any of the photos, even though Pira might be in any of them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5336
msgid "Just look for a giant hole in the ground..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5337
msgid "Forcier chuckles at that."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5338
msgid "Forcier: Well, anyway... I should get back to Olivia. She's treating me to an experimental dinner... So..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5339
msgid "That sounds... dangerous?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5340
msgid "Forcier: Given that she does not usually enjoy cooking, yes. I am somewhat nervous."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5341
msgid "* We try to predict what the meal could be as we walk back to their apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5342
msgid "Roasted Gelcorp drone, maybe?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5343
msgid "* Forcier laughs. * Quite possibly. Or a soup involving a slime monster base."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5344
msgid "Oooh, that sounds kind of good. Maybe some sort of swamp fish stew."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5345
msgid "* The sun has set when we get back to their apartment, and I reluctantly wave goodbye to them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5346
msgid "* I wish them luck at the base of their apartment stairs, and then head back into the city."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5347
msgid "* I see Forcier and Olivia in one of the booths through the window. Olivia has a sea lily in her hair and another she has in her hands, fiddling with a petal."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5348
msgid "* Forcier must have shown her the garden. I better stop in to see how the unveiling went."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5349
msgid "* Forcier notices me first, and waves me over. * Hello there!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5350
msgid "* Olivia sees me and blurts out, * You knew about this? * She shakes her head. * Of course you knew! You are too good at keeping secrets."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5351
msgid "Forcier: She helped me, actually. Finding seeds and such."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5352
msgid "Olivia: Did you? * She scoots over and pats the bench. * Have a seat, then!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5353
msgid "You must be talking about the garden bed. * I slide in next to Olivia."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5354
msgid "* Forcier nods. * I couldn't wait any longer to show her!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5355
msgid "* Sparky rolls over before I'm fully seated. The mechanical creaking of his rusty gears gives him away every time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5356
msgid "Sparky: Greetings --CUSTOMER--. May I interest you in our daily special? Today, we have on the menu--EXPIRED--"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5357
msgid "* There's a pause. Sparky seems to have the name of the special on the tip of its tongue."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5358
msgid "* Or, not tongue, but metal-face-input-hole?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5359
msgid "* Olivia leans over to me and whispers, * I think you broke Sparky..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5360
msgid "Is the daily special expired? Or..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5361
msgid "Sparky: EXPIRED"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5362
msgid "* I hear a loud sigh from the counter as Frank leans over and shouts. * Sparks! What'cha doin'?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5363
msgid "Frank: Shit, I forgot to turn off the daily specials. It's too much for Sparky to handle, apparently."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5364
msgid "Sparky: EXPIRED."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5365
msgid "Frank: Yep, buddy. We freakin' get it, alright? Come on, back to the front."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5366
msgid "* Sparky wheels away, replaced by Frank and his impatient finger tapping."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5367
msgid "Frank: Whatch'a want?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5368
msgid "Frank: The daily special is 'Slug on a Bug!'. Got that, Sparks? Not too hard."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5369
msgid "Frank: I mean, listen. I love the guy, right? Just a bit frustratin' sometimes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5370
msgid "Olivia: Wait... Slug on a bug? Is that, like... Edible?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5371
msgid "Frank: Edible? Definitely, it is most likely edible."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5372
msgid "Olivia: Mmm... Reassuring."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5373
msgid "Frank: Good. Now, want it or not?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5374
msgid "Hey, why not? I'll take the special..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5375
msgid "Frank: Ho ho ho! You are not gonna regret this!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5376
msgid "* Olivia laughs as Frank walks away. * You're gonna regret it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5377
msgid "Forcier: I commend your bravery."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5378
msgid "Olivia: Anyway, I was just saying to Forcier that they better believe I'm gonna be spending time in their garden!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5379
msgid "Forcier: Really? That makes my heart warm, Olivia."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5380
msgid "Olivia: I thought you didn't want me to bother you there!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5381
msgid "Olivia: And, you know, I get sucked into my work. But listen, I'm gonna be there so fucking much now. You are gonna be sooooo annoyed!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5382
msgid "Forcier: I would never be annoyed by you. In fact, I want to build more for you! * They slam their hands on the table in excitement, more expressive than I've ever seen them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5383
msgid "Olivia: Whoa there, babe! One step at a time. This is perfect."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5384
msgid "* Forcier takes a deep breath. * Of course, yes. I had a burst of energy that may have come off a bit too strong."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5385
msgid "* They're still grinning. * But it's hard to contain!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5386
msgid "* Olivia slides across the table and kisses Forcier. Then they turn to me. * Do you see this dork!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5387
msgid "Olivia: My beautiful, caring, passionate dork."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5388
msgid "* Sparky creaks back over, holding a massive plate that it plops down in front of me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5389
msgid "Sparky: Enjoy your meal of --EXPIRED--"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5390
msgid "Frank: No! Not expired! Sparky, come on!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5391
msgid "* Sparky spins back around and heads back to Frank."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5392
msgid "Olivia: Yep. That is for sure a slug on a bug."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5393
msgid "* A giant, gooey, green slug lined with grill marks, laying atop a hard shelled beetle."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5394
msgid "Not quite sure why I ordered this..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5395
msgid "Olivia: You definitely should not eat it. Frank has been getting really creative lately with his recipes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5396
msgid "Olivia: Like, there is no way any of this is edible... * She digs around the gooey mass with my fork."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5397
msgid "Olivia: I can appreciate it, of course. I love a good experiment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5398
msgid "* Forcier chuckles. * Ah, yes. By the way, HC, the experimental dinner Olivia provided me was quite interesting."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5399
msgid "Olivia: Oh, you mean the freeze-dried slime noodles?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5400
msgid "Forcier: That is what I'm referring to."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5401
msgid "Olivia: Surprisingly dope, right?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5402
msgid "* Forcier squints. * ...Yes? Well, surprisingly... innovative."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5403
msgid "Olivia: I might have to try and sell it to Frank, honestly."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5404
msgid "* Looking at the slug on a bug, I can definitely imagine a bed of freeze-dried slime noodles underneath."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5405
msgid "Olivia: You should keep that beetle, though. That's a collectible if I've ever seen one!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5406
msgid "Forcier: You'll need to preserve it, first... If you'd like, I could do that part for you?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5407
msgid "Forcier: I even have a glass dome I believe would fit this specimen perfectly."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5408
msgid "* I carefully slip the slug off the shell of the beetle. * Sure! It'd be a way better use than wherever it would end up otherwise..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5409
msgid "* Forcier helps me clean off the beetle and I mash the slug up a bit, hoping to make it look like I ate at least some of it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5410
msgid "Olivia: Hey, babe, d'ya wanna go back to my garden bed, have a, you know, private moment?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5411
msgid "Olivia: Break in my new garden bed? * She winks at Forcier, and suddenly I feel as if I have overtayed my welcome."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5412
msgid "* Forcier nods, too excited to act cool. * I would love nothing more!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5413
msgid "Forcier: You are free to join in, HC, if you'd like? * They seem to be earnest in asking, however I get the feeling Olivia wants some one-on-one time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5414
msgid "Nah, I'm all right. I should be heading back to my place. Thanks, though."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5415
msgid "* As we leave the Acorn, Forcier stops me. * Oh! I have a small gift I would like you to have. I will be no more than two minutes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5416
msgid "* They run into their apartment and appear way less than two minutes later with a metal vase full of Sea Lilies."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5417
msgid "Forcier: It's my go to gift for friends, so I apologize for the lack of creativity. But I wanted to give you something for helping me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5418
msgid "Aww, Forcier. This is really sweet, thanks!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5419
msgid "Forcier: You're welcome. And Just so you know, I haven't forgotten about your section of the garden. I will keep you updated."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5420
msgid "* Olivia is tugging at Forcier's shirt impatiently, so I respond with a quick, * Sounds great! * "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5421
msgid "* The two of them wave to me and head off to Forcier's garden."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5422
msgid "* I head to the Workshop, eager to catch Decima and Forcier again. See them at work, or even better, let them do some work on me. I can't help smiling as I push through the door."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5423
msgid "* Sure enough, they're inside, working together on what appears to be a pretty considerable clean up effort. Decima is sweeping the scrap-strewn floor while Forcier shelves newly filled boxes of parts."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5424
msgid "Dang, what happened in here? * I survey the mess. Conduction fluid stains the workbench and stacks of half-finished projects loom in the corners."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5425
msgid "* Decima's hoarse laugh widens my smile. * Would you believe that nothing happened? I guess I just hadn't cleaned in a while. Probably wouldn't have, either, but Forcier offered to help."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5426
msgid "Forcier: Indeed. * They pick up a fresh box and start packing it with loose servos. * I've noticed that the most engaging conversations between Decima and I transpire in parallel with productivity."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:5427
