#: result.py:7021
msgid "No, you first!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7022
msgid "If you insist... * I walk up a few steps until I end up face to face with a giant spider."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7023
msgid "* I don't scare easily, at least not with things like creepy insects. It just wasn't programmed into me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7024
msgid "* Heather jumps back, though. * Oh my god! That thing is massive!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7025
msgid "* I duck under it before she does, and she smiles. * See, this is why I wanted you to go first!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7026
msgid "* I puff out my chest, * I do have superior droid reflexes, don't I?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7027
msgid "Heather: Yeah, yeah. Don't get too confident. We aren't even in the building yet."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7028
msgid "Whoa, no way! You're the brave one today, remember?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7029
msgid "* Heather sighs, * Oh, right. I did say that, didn't I..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7030
msgid "* She turns to walk up the stairs, and marches right into a large spider web."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7031
msgid "Heather: Ah! Phffff! * She spits and waves around her arms, detaching the web as the little spider crawls to safety on the side of the building. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7032
msgid "* She glares at me..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7033
msgid "What, you wanted me to walk into that!?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7034
msgid "Heather: No! I didn't...I mean, ok fine. I guess one of us had to."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7035
msgid "I wouldn't have, * I gloat. * Superior droid reflexes, remember?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7036
msgid "* She keeps glaring."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7037
msgid "And...* Feeling worse by the second. * I will lead the way."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7038
msgid "Heather: That's right."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7039
msgid "* I peer into the ticket booth at the top of the stairs but there's a thick slab of plywood nailed to the inside."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7040
msgid "* Heather knocks on the front entrance. * Not that anyone is gonna hear this...It looks empty in there."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7041
msgid "* She has her hands cupped over the glass, and I do the same, seeing a dusty lobby to a theater."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7042
msgid "* Nothing that suggests a workshop of any kind."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7043
msgid "* I pull at both doors. Locked, of course."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7044
msgid "Maybe she meant another theater? Not that there would be another theater named 'Root Street Theater'..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7045
msgid "* Heather tries the door again, unsuccessfully, then nods. * Yeah, whatever, we tried!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7046
msgid "* I head back down the stairs, but Heather calls out. * Wait!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7047
msgid "* I swing back around. She's waving at me to come back up."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7048
msgid "* She's pressing a small button to the left of the door, hidden in the shadow."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7049
msgid "A voice breaks through the silence, coming from somewhere above us."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7050
msgid "?: This better not be another god forsaken salesperson, I swear to that giant hole in Pira--"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7051
msgid "Heather: No! We, uh, we aren't selling anything! We, we met at the mall, remember?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7052
msgid "* Nova's tone changes immediately, * Oh, goodness, yes! I'll unlock, come on back through the stage entrance."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7053
msgid "* The intercom crackles and the door clicks."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7054
msgid "* Heather looks at me. I just shrug."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7055
msgid "* She tries the door again and it opens, creaking loudly from lack of use."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7056
msgid "* Nova meets us on the large, empty stage. Bigger than I would have thought. This place could fit a lot of people back in the day, maybe a few hundred with the balcony in back."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7057
msgid "Nova: Ladies! I am so sorry for my harsh tone out there. It's these merciless sales people. I've had two already today, selling some sort of miracle drink."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7058
msgid "Nova: A word to the wise, those beverages are just dead slime mixed with swamp water."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7059
msgid "Nova: Anywhoo, you don't want to hear an old lady complaining, I'm sure of that..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7060
msgid "* She pauses and looks from me to Heather, then back at me. * Did I ever get your names?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7061
msgid "* Heather shoots her hand out. * Heather! * She shakes Nova's hand for a moment too long before letting go."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7062
msgid "And HC!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7063
msgid "Nova: Heather, HC. Which of you is the seamstress?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7064
msgid "Heather: Heather! * She smiles proudly, pointing at herself. * Well, I actually don't know if I can call myself that..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7065
msgid "Heather: But I do like to make costumes and clothes and stuff."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7066
msgid "Nova: Mmm, wonderful. * She checks her watch, * Well, if I remember correctly, you two are hunting for some materials."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7067
msgid "* Heather nods, * There's this costume contest thing I wanted to try out at the art convention."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7068
msgid "Nova: Why don't we head back to my workshop and you can have a look around."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7069
msgid "* She leads us into a musty room right behind the stage. Probably used to be a dressing room for actors."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7070
msgid "* It's dimly lit with a couple of dangling overhead lights and, from what I can see, it's overflowing with fabric and boxes of sewing supplies."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7071
msgid "Nova: I have a few students coming in soon, but I'm sure they won't mind two extra people."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7072
msgid "* I can't tell if Heather can hear what Nova's saying. She's already rummaging through piles of fabric."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7073
msgid "Heather: Wow! This place is amazing!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7074
msgid "* Nova laughs. * Most people would call it a dump."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7075
msgid "Heather: They better not!! Where do you find this stuff? * She picks up a large roll of glittery red fabric and runs her fingers over it as if it's precious gold."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7076
msgid "Nova: Wherever I can find it. Big factories that supply wealthier suburbs leave their trucks open sometimes..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7077
msgid "* Heather looks up at her, * So, what's for sale?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7078
msgid "* Nova looks puzzled. * Sale? No, just take what you need. Trust me, this place needs a little clean out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7079
msgid "* Heather shakes her head. * No! I'm gonna pay you. * She unzips her purse and rummages through it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7080
msgid "Nova: I won't accept it! * She chuckles, * I don't need it. I'm mostly self sufficient, anyway."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7081
msgid "Nova: I've got a good little community of people. We make sure we all have what we need."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7082
msgid "Heather: Sounds dreamy... * She zips back up her purse. * better than working for Gel, anyway."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7083
msgid "Nova: Well, yes! Is that where you work? * She doesn't wait for an answer. * Lot's of people here used to work at places such as that, you know."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7084
msgid "* We hear the sound of footsteps echoing through the theater, like shoes clanging on metal or something."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7085
msgid "Nova: Early, as usual. * She's looking at her watch again, shaking her head. * I suppose that's better than late, but just barely."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7086
msgid "* A moment later, two people walk in, arm in arm, both holding a large basket."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7087
msgid "?: We just made these last night, so they're very, very fresh. * They both hand her their baskets and she peers at the contents."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7088
msgid "Nova: Ooooh, you certainly know how to make preserves, I'll tell you that much."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7089
msgid "* One of them looks at us and nods. * Who're they? New students?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7090
msgid "Nova: Oh! How rude of me. This is Heather and * She looks at me, squints, purses her lips."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7091
msgid "HC! * I remind her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7092
msgid "* She exhales. * HC! Right, right. As you can tell, my memory is like that of a small slug these days."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7093
msgid "Nova: Yes, Heather and HC, This is Randi and Talli. They are learning how to make their own clothes with me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7094
msgid "Randi: Slowly and poorly, but yeah, some day we'll be pros."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7095
msgid "Nova: Someday soon! You two are naturals."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7096
msgid "Nova: And I just recently met Heather at the mall while we were both looking through Fern's fabric scraps."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7097
msgid "Nova: She's doing some sort of, what did you say, dear? Artistic clothing competition?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7098
msgid "Heather: A costume contest! At the Pira Art Convention."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7099
msgid "Talli: Oh, sick! That's a cool little fair they have. I'll probably see you there! I'm selling some... * She looks at Nova, then clears her throat."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7100
msgid "Randi: Some lube. She's selling lube."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7101
msgid "* Talli jabs his arm. * Ok, Randi! Way to scream it to the world!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7102
msgid "Nova: Oh, you two! You should be proud of your product. It is high quality."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7103
msgid "Nova: Now, you two, get your materials and head to the stage. I'll be out there very soon and we can resume our progress."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7104
msgid "* Randi and Talli head back out onto the stage, and Nova turns her attention back to us."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7105
msgid "* Heather is immediately back in the piles of fabric, both of them gushing over textures and patterns."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7106
msgid "* And I'm wandering around, keeping out of their way but not trying to seem too out of place. I just don't think I'd add anything to the conversation, beyond the limited clothing knowledge I was programed with."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7107
msgid "Heather: HC! Come here for a sec, I gotta see how this would fit around you!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7108
msgid "* Finally feeling useful, I stand in front of Nova and Heather as she slips the swath of silvery fabric around my waist."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7109
msgid "Heather: Perfect, right?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7110
msgid "* She has a stack of cloth that reaches above her head when she's finished picking things out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7111
msgid "Heather: Nova, * She peers around her giant pile, * you gotta tell me what I can do to repay you for all this."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7112
msgid "Nova: Just show me your creations when you're finished, how about that? Maybe someday we can trade outfits?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7113
msgid "Heather: I mean, I can definitely do that!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7114
msgid "Nova: Good. Now, if you'll excuse me, I've got some teaching to do... feel free to stay as long as you'd like."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7115
msgid "* Luckily, Heather seems to have gotten all the fabric she wants, and we head back to her apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7116
msgid "Heather: How did I not know about that place, HC! I'd love to be in a little community of... Well, I don't know exactly what they do, actually..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7117
msgid "* She sorts through her pile of cloth, separating it into two piles. * Mine, mine... yours... HC, your costume is gonna be so cute, you don't even know."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7118
msgid "Heather: Ok, I gotta get to work, so if you wanna stay here, go for it, but I will not be doing any talking. I am so ready to make this thing!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7119
msgid "Oh, I'll leave you to it, don't worry. Unless you need help?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7120
msgid "Heather: Just a kiss? Yeah, a kiss would help..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7121
msgid "* Kiss."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7122
msgid "* No kiss."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7123
msgid "I think I can help with that..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7124
msgid "Heather: Good, * She reaches up and wraps her hands around my neck and pulls me down to her, onto her soft, waiting lips."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7125
msgid "* She pulls away just briefly to say. * Oh yeah, definitely helping. * Then she's back to kissing me, her mouth opening slightly to draw me in closer."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7126
msgid "* She moans quietly into my mouth as I run my fingers down her back, to her waist, her hips."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7127
msgid "* She makes a louder, more desperate sound and runs her hands down my chest..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7128
msgid "Heather: Mmm... * She whispers, then suddenly comes back down, * Wait a second, I gotta actually get work done!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7129
msgid "Heather: Not that I don't want more help with, well, you know, but we have to win this contest, HC!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7130
msgid "* I put my hands up in defeat. * Ok, ok! I'll leave you to it, if I must."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7131
msgid "* Heather laughs. * Very unfortunately, you must! * She spins around and gets right to work."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7132
msgid "Whoa, whoa whoa! Not until the costumes are done!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7133
msgid "Heather: Ok, finnnnnnne! More motivation, I guess. * She grins, * Well get going, then!!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7134
msgid "* I make my way out of her bedroom and back to mine. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7135
msgid "Heather: HC! Are you in there?! * It's early in the morning, and I'm still in bed when Heather's voice breaks through the silence."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7136
msgid "* I rub my eyes and stretch my arms up, brushing the cracked, gravely ceiling with my fingertips. A piece breaks off and falls directly into my eye. Figures."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7137
msgid "Ah, fuck! * My eye floods with conduction fluid. I'm fine, just startled."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7138
msgid "Heather: HC? Oh my god are you ok?! * She doesn't wait for me to answer, just bursts through the door."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7139
msgid "Hey, Heather! I'm good, just got a little ceiling in my eye."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7140
msgid "Heather: Goodness! That stuff's super toxic. Here, let me have a look!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7141
msgid "Heather: Stop-- * She slaps my hand away. * Rubbing it! You'll get it in your brain!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7142
msgid "Hmmm, I somehow doubt that... Anyway, I'm not human, I can take a bit of toxic dust to the brain. * But I stop rubbing my eye anyway."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7143
msgid "* She brushes her hand over my forehead and grabs my chin and stares right into my eye."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7144
msgid "Heather: Mhmm, yes, very interesting... * She squints her eyes and turns the corners of her mouth down."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7145
msgid "So what's the verdict, doctor H? * She stands up and laughs."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7146
msgid "Heather: Follow me to the operating room! * She leads me into my cramped bathroom."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7147
msgid "Heather: I believe you're supposed to... pour water into your eye."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7148
msgid "Oh, well since you sound so confident..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7149
msgid "Heather: It's what I do! Come on, I'll do it quick. * She lowers me down to the sink and turns my head up."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7150
msgid "Heather: Ok... * She cradles my head in one hand and holds the faucet with the other. * quick splash!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7151
msgid "* She turns it on, just slightly, and I can see a big drop hanging onto the ring of the faucet before it breaks free and lands right on my eyeball. I'm ready though, and I don't blink."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7152
msgid "* Heather does a little body shiver. * Dang HC, you didn't even wince."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7153
msgid "Oh, my bad. * Internally, I let up a bit on my droid reflex restraint. It's not a feature I enjoy using anyway. Redirected anxiety can manifest in weird ways."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7154
msgid "* She turns it a little more and I grimace but keep my eye open until I can't stand it anymore and pull away fast, right smack into Heather's forehead"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7155
msgid "Heather: Jeez, HC! You're gonna give me a concussion! * She rubs her head and laughs."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7156
msgid "I'm so sorry! I just kind of freaked out! * I run my hand over her face where I hit her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7157
msgid "Heather: As long as I don't have brain damage, I think I'm good to go! Did it at least work?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7158
msgid "Uh... * I blink my eye a few times, waiting for pain."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7159
msgid "I think so. Thanks!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7160
msgid "Heather: Hey, no problem!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7161
msgid "Heather: See ya later, HC!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7162
msgid "Heather: Wait... that's not even why I was here!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7163
msgid "* She turns her head down and looks up at me with big eyes. * Uh... I need a huge favor..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7164
msgid "I suppose I owe you one... * I cross my arms and fake a scowl."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7165
msgid "Heather: Yeah you do! * Heather smiles and puts her finger up. * One sec."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7166
msgid "* She sneaks out the door and returns with a hefty tablet."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7167
msgid "Heather: Ok, I need you to take, like, lots of pictures of me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7168
msgid "For any particular reason?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7169
msgid "Heather: Well, kind of? I want to take some pictures of outfits I've made, so I can show Nova!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7170
msgid "Heather: She told me she wanted to see some of my work, you know? I don't want to bring all of my clothes to the theater."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7171
msgid "Heather: Also, I suck at taking pics of myself!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7172
msgid "You think I can do better?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7173 result.py:15677 result.py:18545
msgid "I'd love to."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7174
msgid "Heather: Well not if you don't believe in yourself!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7175
msgid "I don't believe in myself!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7176
msgid "Heather: Excuse me!!!! * She huffs. * Well I guess I'll have to believe in you for yourself."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7177
msgid "* She disappears into her room for a second before emerging with her camera. * Just point and click, seriously!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7178
msgid "* Heather grins. * You are the best! * She disappears into her room for a second before emerging with her camera."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7179
msgid "Heather: OK, the hallway should be a decent enough background. * She hands me the camera. * I will be right back."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7180
msgid "* She runs into her room to change. I fiddle with her camera in the hallway, change the color settings, make little flowers appear on the edge of the frame."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7181
msgid "Shit! * I accidently snap a photo. A nice blank wall."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7182
msgid "Heather: Everything ok out there?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7183
msgid "Uh, yeah, all good! * I switch the camera to the front, right at my face."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7184
msgid "Whoa. * Not incredibly flattering. I press a little star icon and the filter menu pops up. On the screen, the image of my body turns to transparent shimmering crystal orbited by cute pastel stars."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7185
msgid "* Better! Actually, not bad at all... maybe I should take a secret practice selfie..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7186
msgid "* Take a photo"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7187
msgid "* Focus on the task at hand."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7188
msgid "Better not. Don't want to embarrass myself too much."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7189
msgid "* I make a series of weird, contorted smiles, trying to find the angle that makes me seem cute and chill and casual."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7190
msgid "* Heather walks out right as I switch the camera back. * Ok, time for the first one!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7191
msgid "* She's wearing a full suit of studded leather armor, hand stitched by the look of it, and a shiny purple bow by her side."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7192
msgid "Damn, Heather! Impressive, as usual!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7193
msgid "* Heather blushes. * Thanks. I like this one too."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7194
msgid "Heather: Anyway, uh, how should I pose?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7195
msgid "Try a heroic pose."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7196
msgid "Do an action Pose."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7197
msgid "You should choose."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7198
msgid "Stand up straight, but like, arch your back and lift your chin up like you're, uh, too cool."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7199
msgid "Heather: Wow, HC, really getting into the photographer role!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7200 result.py:7206
msgid "* This time I blush. * or, uh, you know... whatever you want."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7201
msgid "Heather: No I like it! Here, like this? * She gets into the pose, hands on her bow, chin raised, stoic expression."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7202
msgid "Perfect. * I focus the frame. * Ok, stay... very... still... there! What do you think? * I flip it around for her to see."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7203
msgid "Heather: Lovely! Next one!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7204
msgid "Oooh, what about an action shot? Like you're loading up an arrow?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7205
msgid "Heather: Getting into this photographer role pretty well, I see!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7207
msgid "Heather: No, I like it! Here, something like this? * She takes an arrow out of the quiver and freezes as she lines it up."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7208
msgid "Perfect. * I focus the frame * Ok, stay... very... still... there! What do you think? * I flip it around for her to see."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7209 result.py:7214
msgid "Heather: Lovely! On to the next one!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7210
msgid "Hmm, maybe just do the first pose that comes to mind."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7211
msgid "* She thinks for a moment and then settles into a casual pose, one hand on her hip and the other leaning on her bow."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7212
msgid "Heather: Something like this?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7213
msgid "Exactly! You're a natural model! * I focus the frame. * Ok, stay... very... still... there! What do you think? * I flip it around for her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7215
msgid "* She shuts the door and turns on music in her room. * Don't judge!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7216
msgid "* It's upbeat, bouncy. I guess that's not surprising."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7217
msgid "I like it! * I yell, probably not loud enough. * It's actually pretty catchy."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7218
msgid "* I know a lot of technical information about music and dancing, but I'm not running any explicit dancing or singing software."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7219
msgid "* Still, I'm slightly bored, and I kind of want to try..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7220
msgid "* Dance."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7221
msgid "* Dance and sing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7222
msgid "* Just wait."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7223 result.py:7231
msgid "* I risk embarrassment and start tapping my foot. I can really feel the vibrations rushing through me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7224 result.py:7233
msgid "* I move my shoulders back and forth with each beat, then raise my hands a bit."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7225 result.py:7234
msgid "* I get into the movement. I feel like a rock star, like a professional dancer... my hands are waving in a perfect motion with my legs..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7226 result.py:7235
msgid "* Until I trip over nothing, a piece of air maybe, and fall right into Heather."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7227 result.py:7236
msgid "Heather: Oh my god, keep going! I was loving it! * I fall right into her arms and She's looking down at me, wearing a full trench coat with some sort of leotard underneath."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7228 result.py:7237
msgid "* I clear my throat. * You, ahem, didn't see anything! * I lift myself up and laugh."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7229
msgid "Heather: Oh, I saw something! Don't worry, it was magical. * She giggles."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7230
msgid "At least I didn't ruin your costume! It's fucking amazing. * It's long, flowing, and cut deep in the front. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7232
msgid "* I have no idea what the lyrics are, but I attempt to sing anyway. * The! .... It!... Uh, In the sky! Tonight!..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7238
msgid "Heather: Oh, I saw something! Don't worry, it was magical. * She giggles. * Didn't know you were a singer!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7239
msgid "Oh god, you heard me too! Well, at least I didn't ruin your costume! It's fucking amazing. * It's long, flowing, and cut deep in the front. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7240
msgid "Heather: It's actually from Wastewood! June gets dressed up and goes undercover. It's amazing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:7241
msgid "Ha, I should have known! * She poses seductively, with her hand on her hip, looking down at the camera."
