msgid "Decima: I mean, like, don't get me wrong, I love it, but why does it feel good? * She turns to face us, walking backward at the head of the pack."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9558
msgid "Magdalena: You don't have to analyze it; just let it be fun. Enjoy yourself."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9559
msgid "Cadence: Being in a huge crowd and bumping into people and freaking out in unison is, like, I dunno. I think it's a social thing?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9560
msgid "Beryl: I-I think it has to do with just feeling yourself move... The music awakens something in you, a-and you have to follow the feeling..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9561
msgid "* I'm lost in what Beryl said for a moment. * ...What about you, Decima? What do you think?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9562
msgid "Decima: I think it's a matter of simple instinct. I'm a natural dancer in that I'm naturally seductive when I dance. It's how I attract a mate."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9563
msgid "* Cadence bursts out laughing, followed by Beryl. Even Magdalena cracks a smile."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9564
msgid "Decima: That's right, everyone: laugh your jealousy away. * She lowers her eyelids and smirks as she looks off in the distance, feigning a serene, proud expression. * What about you, HC?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9565
msgid "No clue..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9566
msgid "* We make it to The Lemon and begin to file in through the door. The walls of the club are vibrating with the din of music and socializing patrons."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9567
msgid "* A group of intoxicated club-goers stumble out of the door, tiddies out, kissing and laughing and drinking as they walk. Cadence waggles her eyebrows at us as they pass."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9568
msgid "* Cadence, Decima and Beryl disappear through the door, but before I can enter, Mags stops me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9569
msgid "Magdalena: Let's skip this. I'm not feeling it. * She smiles. Sort of..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9570
msgid "This was your idea, right?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9571
msgid "* Magdalena sighs and looks away. Am I disappointing her?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9572
msgid "Ok, well, what should we do?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9573
msgid "* She leads me around the corner of the building and leans against the wall. Her expression is playful, but severe and nervous. I can't really get a read on her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9574
msgid "Magdalena: Do you wanna kiss me? * She leans forward, staring at me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9576 result.py:16461 result.py:16536
msgid "No."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9578
msgid "* She puts her arms around my waist and pulls me into a deep kiss. It's nice, and lasts for a bit, but then she breaks it suddenly."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9579
msgid "* She glances around like she's lost something, avoiding eye contact, and then turns her back to me. * Fuck... * Her voice is almost a whisper."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9580
msgid "* After a brief pause, she suddenly cuts away from me, walking as fast as she can. It doesn't even look like she picked a direction."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9581
msgid "* Go after her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9582 result.py:16464
msgid "* Let her leave."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9583
msgid "* Magdalena scowls. * What the fuck... I'm being a normal, nice, social girl. Why is that a problem...?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9584
msgid "Hey, Magdalena? * I try to gather my thoughts as I jog to catch up with her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9585
msgid "* When she hears me coming, she whirls to meet my gaze. She's truly, deeply terrified. She's wide-eyed, her breathing heavy, her hands shaking. Is she terrified of me? I stop dead, feeling gutted. She runs off."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9586
msgid "* I stand there, feeling sick and monstrous, hoping she's ok, and wondering what's going on. Eventually, I decide I should tell someone."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9587
msgid "* I go back into The Lemon and find Beryl, being shy and watching people dance. I let her know what's up using as few words as possible. She's concerned but says nothing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9588
msgid "* We leave together, but I head home alone."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9589
msgid "* I'm not sure what's going on, but I don't think Magdalena wants to be around me. I stand there, hoping she's ok and wondering what caused this reaction. I should tell someone eventually..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9590
msgid "* I let myself into the apartment. Beryl Is chilling on the bed with her Laptop, but Magdalena is missing. Weird. She offered to meet me here."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9591
msgid "Beryl: Hey HC! Ahh, you're not here to hang out a-are you? I'm heading back to work in like, a few minutes... * She blushes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9592
msgid "Oh, no, actually I was here for Magdalena. She was supposed to be here... * I glance around awkwardly."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9593
msgid "* Beryl looks authentically unconcerned. * Huh. * She clicks a few times. * She's offline. I'll ch-check if she's posting."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9594
msgid "* Beryl messes with her computer a bit. * Yeah she's talking about... * She frowns. * She's posting. Ten minutes ago. Wherever she is, she's all right. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9595
msgid "Beryl: I'm sure she'll be b-back soon. Feel free to wait here after I leave. * She gets up and tosses her laptop onto the bed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9596
msgid "What's she posting about?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9597
msgid "Thanks Beryl."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9598
msgid "* Beryl squints at the screen. * She's literally just venting about some d-dude who... bought the last cup of melon boba tea."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9599
msgid "* I giggle. * An unforgivable sin."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9600
msgid "Beryl: Now she's talking about c-c-cute boys. I can't tell if she's complaining about them or... lusting for them. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9601
msgid "Maybe both?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9602
msgid "* We both laugh. * That's a mood. Ok, I better go. See you later, HC!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9603
msgid "Ok! Thanks Beryl!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9604
msgid "Beryl: Oh, no p-problem. You're pretty much always welcome here... * She pulls up her leg warmers and puts her shoes on."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9605
msgid "* That's not something I'm eager to test, especially while things with Magdalena are so... I dunno... Uncertain?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9606
msgid "Thanks..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9607
msgid "* Beryl pauses. * I know something weird went down last time... Mags is really trying though. She j-just... She's been through a lot. * She pats me on the shoulder."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9608
msgid "Beryl: See you later, HC! * She smiles and waves as she walks out the door."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9609
msgid "* Being alone in someone else's place is a familiar feeling with bad connotations. I don't feel like I'm being stored, but I'm still anxious for some reason. I wonder when she'll get here."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9610 result.py:9626
msgid "* Wait 20 minutes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9612
msgid "* Nothing. I wonder what's going on."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9613
msgid "She probably hates me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9614
msgid "I hope she's ok."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9615
msgid "* Cool. I can feel the obsession begin. I take a seat on the bed and start massaging my temples."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9616
msgid "* I really fucked this up. She can't hold this low an opinion of me without it affecting the group dynamic. It'll be Beryl next I bet. Shit, I'm gonna panic if I keep this up."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9617 result.py:9623
msgid "* I try and calm down a little. Deep breaths."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9618
msgid "* I'm probably just being dumb anyway. There's no real reason for me to jump to this conclusion, at least not now. It's not like she can hate me more than she already did."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9619 result.py:9625
msgid "* Just gotta wait.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9620
msgid "* I force myself to try and think positive. Gotta hold onto whatever comforting thoughts I can if I don't want to panic."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9621
msgid "* I'm sure she has a good reason for being late. I'm a little confused at how hard this is. I wouldn't typically worry this hard about this kind of thing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9622
msgid "* I really hope she's not mad at me. Am I secretly hoping that something bad did happen to her, so she has an excuse? What the fuck is wrong with me. I'm bad..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9624
msgid "* I'm just being dumb. To avoid jumping to any more stupid conclusions, I'll just try and keep my mind clear. Everything's fine. I take a seat on the bed and start massaging my temples."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9628
msgid "* Still no Magdalena. This sucks."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9629
msgid "* I start bouncing my leg. This is dumb. What am I even still doing here. She's not coming. And if she does, she's just gonna know how much of an idiot I am for waiting so long. Damn it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9630
msgid "* I should probably go before I freak myself out too bad."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9632
msgid "Annoyed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9633
msgid "Sad."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9634
msgid "* I get to be mad at her, right? I didn't fuck up, did I? If I was waiting on Beryl or anyone, I wouldn't be feeling like this I'm pretty sure."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9635
msgid "* Yeah, fuck her. Or, you know... that, but milder. She might be stuck somewhere. Damn, I can't even be mad correctly. Whatever."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9636
msgid "* Why does she have to treat me like this... I don't know what I could have done wrong."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9637
msgid "* That gross heavy feeling sinks into my flesh. My blood feels cold and heavy. I shouldn't have let this get this bad."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9638
msgid "* I get up and walk out. I probably should have bailed on this 40 minutes ago. I could have skipped a lot of bad feelings..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9639
msgid "* I arrive at the apartment. I'm not super sure how I should handle this whole 'Magdalena ditching me' thing. I knock, but then change my mind and open the door."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9640
msgid "* Magdalena is sitting on the bed with her laptop and I can hear Beryl singing in the shower."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9641
msgid "Hey, Magdalena. * I only kinda smile."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9642
msgid "* She glances at me. * Hey. What's up?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9643
msgid "Uh, well. I dunno... * I take a deep breath. * Hey, I was waiting for you last time. You said you'd be there..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9644
msgid "* Magdalena glares at me. Instant aggression. * I got caught up. It happens."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9645
msgid "Magdalena, we've gotta talk about this, ok?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9646
msgid "Magdalena: I don't know what there is to talk about. * She slouches down behind her laptop, almost breaking eye contact."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9647
msgid "You're acting super weird and mean and I wanna know why. Did I do something?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9648
msgid "* She rolls her eyes. * We've already been through this, remember? In the library?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9649
msgid "* I don't give her a chance to summarize. * Yeah, I remember, it was dangerous for your girlfriend to stick her neck out for me and you think I'm responsible for the horniness anomaly or something."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9650
msgid "That kinda made sense to me at the time, for some reason. But it doesn't now, and it's super inconsistent with how you've been acting."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9651
msgid "I think we should talk about that night at The Lemon. What was that? You seemed really upset..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9652
msgid "Magdalena: Yeah, well, I didn't wanna be there. Didn't know that was against the rules. * She scowls and sinks behind the laptop."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9653
msgid "It's not against the rules, I just wanted... Fuck. Fuck it. I just want to know if... I dunno, I'm hurting you somehow."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9654
msgid "* I pause to let her respond, but she just sits there motionless, face obscured."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9655
msgid "* I start to choke up. I just want things to be ok. Damn it..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9656
msgid "Magdalena... Please... * My voice cracks."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9657
msgid "* She speaks quietly and is muffled by the laptop. * Sorry..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9658
msgid "Magdalena? * I take a seat on the bed, making sure to keep my distance."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9659
msgid "* She lowers the laptop. Her face is deadpan. She doesn't look like she's been crying, but her face is wet with tears."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9661
msgid "* Her voice stays soft. * ...No."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9663
msgid "* She shrugs and clears her throat. It really seems like she's trying to not burst into tears. * I don't know what's wrong with me... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9665
msgid "* Her voice is so quiet I can barely make out her words. * I've been doing bad. Since you got here. Panicking more than usual."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9666
msgid "* I pause. * Do you have any idea why?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9667
msgid "* The bathroom door opens. I guess I was too engaged to hear the shower turn off. Beryl appears, wrapped in a towel. She seems happy to see me for the second before she reads the tension."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9668
msgid "Beryl: HC! ...Oh... What's going on."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9669
msgid "* I glance at Magdalena, who offers no indication of an intent to reply. * Uh, we're just talking about stuff."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9670
msgid "Magdalena: About me..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9671
msgid "* Beryl crawls onto the bed next to her. * What is it?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9672
msgid "* Magdalena takes a deep breath. * I've just been super overwhelmed with everything that's been going on. It's too much. I don't know how to deal with it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9673
msgid "Beryl: You mean with HC?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9674
msgid "Magdalena: No, just everything. I've gotta be constantly ready for these big, stressful group events. It's like constant performance. It's breaking me down."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9675
msgid "* That's surprisingly relatable. * Oh, yeah, that makes sense. You wanna do social stuff on your own terms. You don't want the pressure of people expecting you to be available, maybe? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9676
msgid "Magdalena: Yeah, maybe. I dunno. * She looks away."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9677
msgid "* Beryl scoots closer and speaks extra soft. * Hey, Mags? No one expects you to do anything, ok? You've got no obligations in this group. None. I promise."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9678
msgid "* Magdalena grits her teeth and her voice becomes strained. * Yeah, I know. It doesn't really work that way though. It's like, every time I'm just waiting for it to happen."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9679
msgid "* Her knuckles are white against the laptop. * I'm so weak to that shit... I can't deal with it. * She chokes down a sob."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9680
msgid "* Oh shit. This is probably a dumb thing to ask, but it sounds important. * Deal with what?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9681
msgid "* Mags looks at me but doesn't look like she can make herself speak. Beryl answers. * Like, sexual stuff..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9682
msgid "* Magdalena chokes out a few words. * God damn it. Why am I like this... * I feel tears start to well in my eyes. That's weird."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9683
msgid "* Beryl turns back towards her. * You're dealing with bad stuff as best you can. You're so good, Mags... * I start silently crying. I don't know Mags well, but I want good things for her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9684
msgid "We can set up boundaries for this. We can totally avoid doing anything like that when you're part of the group."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9685
msgid "Magdalena: No, no, I don't wanna stop you guys from having fun. I can't... ...be a burden. It's not worth it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9686
msgid "Beryl: You're not a burden. At all. We're happy to do this. We don't need to fuck all the time. It's no problem at all. Let's try it out, ok?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9687
msgid "Magdalena: Fuck... Ok... * She tries to straighten up, but she still looks ready to cry. * You can ask me. If you really need to..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9688
msgid "* Beryl smiles a little. * Oh my g-gosh... Mags, you're silly."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9689
msgid "* Magdalena lets out a little sob-laugh and leans over onto Beryl's shoulder, who starts gently playing with her hair. I laugh a little too, and so does Beryl. A tear runs down her smiling face."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9690
msgid "* Magdalena looks up and laughs. * Oh my god, are we all crying now? What a bunch of nerds."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9691
msgid "* Beryl laughs through her tears. * Y-You're the nerd! * She hugs Magdalena tightly."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9692
msgid "* Mags buries her face in Beryl's chest, drying her tears and muffling her voice with her shirt. * Psh, I'm not a nerd. I do crimes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9693
msgid "Beryl: Oh my god. Name one c-crime."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9694
msgid "* Magdalena whines into Beryl's shirt. * Nooooo, it's embarrassing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9695
msgid "* Beryl looks kinda excited. * Nice! We're about to play the question game, aren't we? HC, t-tell us your best crime."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9696 result.py:9699
msgid "Uh, I don't crime."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9697 result.py:9700
msgid "* Tell a story. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9698
msgid "What's the question game?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9701
msgid "Beryl: It's this thing where we ask each other questions and you have to answer. I d-don't really know if that c-counts as a game, but, it's fun."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9702
msgid "What if I don't want to answer?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9703
msgid "Beryl: I mean, no one is actually making you answer. If someone gets uncomfortable, the game usually just ends. So, what's your crime?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9704
msgid "* Beryl laughs. * Sounds fake, b-but ok. I'll go. Uhhh, hmmmm. One time I squeezed a bunch of mustard packets into a dudes pocket on the train."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9705
msgid "* Magdalena snorts. * No you didn't, don't lie. You're perfect."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9706
msgid "Beryl: Yeah, I d-did! He heckled some girl as she was getting out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9707
msgid "* Magdalena smiles. * Aww, see? You are perfect. * She kisses Beryl on the cheek."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9708
msgid "* Beryl blushes. * Uh, o-ok, your t-turn now!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9709
msgid "Uh, this isn't really a crime, but sometimes when my owners would make me do stuff, I'd like, overact the whole 'droid' thing. * I look down and smile as I recollect."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9710
msgid "They'd make me cook and I'd do stuff like... I'd bring them dinner and be like, 'your past preferences have indicated you prefer your dinner prepared \"medium rare.\" I have prepared your chicken torchon accordingly.'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9711
msgid "Stuff like that. It really pissed them off, but I just kept playing dumb. * I laugh."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9712
msgid "* Magdalena starts laughing too. And Beryl. When they calm down, Beryl speaks. * Oh my god, that's so good HC. Ok, Mags, your turn."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9713
msgid "Magdalena: Ok, fine, fine. Uh... * She looks embarrassed. * When I was younger, I, um..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9714
msgid "* She looks away. * I always walked past this girls house on my way home from school, and she always left her shoes on the porch."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9715
msgid "* Magdalena's face goes a little red. * One day, she got new shoes. And I took 'em."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9716
msgid "Beryl: Really? Why?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9717
msgid "Magdalena: I wanted girl shoes. They were cute. I was dumb. * She laughs."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9718
msgid "* I smile at her. * That's super cute, Magdalena..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9719
msgid "Magdalena: Psh, no it's not. Question game over."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9720
msgid "Beryl: Cool, cool. I've learned a lot. * She smiles. * It was fun..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9721
msgid "Agreed. Maybe it's time for me to go, though. Uh, thanks for talking to me, Magdalena..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9722
msgid "* Magdalena locks eyes with me and her smile fades. * It's ok... Sorry I've been rude. I... Dunno how easy this is going to be. It's gonna take time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9723
msgid "Magdalena: I'm glad you're friends with Beryl. I dunno if I'm really ready for that kinda thing yet though. I'm still getting used to this. I need to warm up to you. Sorry..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9724
msgid "* Beryl almost shouts. * D&D! Oh my god! We've gotta play D&D, that's the answer! * She bounces with excitement."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9725
msgid "* A smile creeps onto Magdalena's face. * Oh no. You're right..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9726
msgid "* Beryl squeaks. * Yes! I'm gonna set up the game! Ah, it's gonna be so great! We could even resume the old one! "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9727
msgid "* Magdalena speaks flatly, but her smile betrays her enthusiasm. * We'll see. I'm sure Beryl will give you the details, HC."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9728
msgid "Beryl: Of course! I'll make sure everyone is super aware of your boundaries, too."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9729
msgid "Magdalena: Uh, yeah... Thanks... Anyway, yeah. I'll see you later HC. This was... good."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9730
msgid "* I wave goodbye and let myself out. That went way better than expected..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9731
msgid "* As I head out of my apartment, I notice Magdalena standing just outside the front entrance."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9732
msgid "* Shrouded in a lingering carpet of morning fog, face illuminated a pale blue from whatever game she's playing on her phone, I could almost mistake her for a specter of death."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9733
msgid "* Is she waiting for me? I open the door cautiously, and she jerks her head up and glares."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9734
msgid "Magdalena: What are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9735
msgid "* The sheer boldness of her question catches me off guard. What am I doing here? At the building in which I literally live?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9736
msgid "* Humor her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9737
msgid "I live here..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9738
msgid "Oh, just heading outside for a bit! * I take an exaggerated breath of the cold air. As a demonstration. * How's it going?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9739
msgid "Magdalena: Cool, cool. * She smiles and twirls a strand of bright green hair."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9740
msgid "Magdalena: Hey... Since you're here, I might as well ask you..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9741
msgid "Mags, come on. I live here. You know that! * As I speak the words, doubt blossoms. * Or... ...Did you forget that I live here?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9742
msgid "* Magdalena frowns. * Whatever. Am I not allowed near your apartment?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9743
msgid "* Just Mags being Mags, I guess. I turn to leave. * All right, well it was nice seein--"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9744
msgid "Magdalena: Excuse me? You're gonna turn your back on these?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9745
msgid "* Sighing, I face her. She's pocketed her phone and produced a pair of dirty binoculars. She's fondling them, really. At tit level. Tryna make the ancient tech look provocative."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9746
msgid "Mags: The Tunnel Girls are doing roller derby tonight. Thought you might wanna peep it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9747
msgid "Are you inviting me?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9748
msgid "* Mags looks annoyed. * Obviously. Are you in?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9749
msgid "Sure, yeah. No idea what I'm getting into here, though..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9750
msgid "Magdalena: I don't either. This is like, not really a public event, you know."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9751
msgid "Magdalena: But I thought, maybe they'll let us in? Cause we're on good terms and all..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9752
msgid "Magdalena: Listen, if you're gonna come, swing by my apartment at eight o'clock."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9753
msgid "* She walks away before I can say much more."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9754
msgid "--- Eight O'clock ---"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9755
msgid "* It's dark and cold outside when I get to Magdalena's place. She's reclining against the rusted 'Sunshine Girders' sign, bouncing her knee at what must be a thousand BPM."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9756
msgid "* I hesitate for a second before walking over to her... Maybe I should ask Beryl why she didn't want to go?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9757
msgid "* Probably because the Tunnel Girls are scary and don't want the public at their roller derby matches..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9758
msgid "Magdalena: Thought you wouldn't show up. * She sees me and glares, glances down at the time on her phone. * Eight o' two.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9759
msgid "Already pissed off at me?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9760
msgid "Sorry."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9761
msgid "Magdalena frowns, and opens her mouth to say something, probably an insult, but then her shoulders relax."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9762
msgid "Magdalena: Fuck, you're right. That's just me being a bitch. Let's go."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9763
msgid "Magdalena: Nah, that's just me being a bitch. You're pretty much on time. Let's go."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9764
msgid "* The rusted entrance to the tunnel is shut. Only a few people are grouped around the door."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9765
