#: result.py:9948
msgid "Quinn: Oh, is that an Emotistar? Where did you find this old thing? * He looks surprised."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9949
msgid "* Cadence smiles at Mags. * Ah, you've found a gamer. Cool. * She hoists the plastic thing like a trophy."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9950
msgid "Cadence: Yes! The true aficionados among you will identify the Emotistar, an Emotiscan based console from, like, years ago. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9951
msgid "* She looks back at Quinn. * My friend Decima gave it to me. Found it in a trash compactor, I'm pretty sure. Fixed it up for me. Mostly, at least."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9952
msgid "Quinn: Sick. She must be pretty handy... Aren't those things like, a hundred years old? Or something? * He scrutinizes it. * Man, and this is like, a special edition one and everything..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9953
msgid "Magdalena: Ok, jeez, no need to, like... * She flicks her fingers at him. * Nerd out. Or anything. What game did you bring, Cadence?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9954
msgid "* She describes a sort of emotionally-based guitar hero where manifesting different emotions is required to perform each note. We decide that it sounds like a headache, so we switch to a hype-controlled racing game."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9955
msgid "* The situation has me wondering..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9956
msgid "Are my emotions real?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9957
msgid "Can I use my droid reflexes to win?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9958
msgid "Am I about to make a new friend?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9959
msgid "* It's an anxiety that perishes almost as soon as it crops up. It takes me about as long as the rest of them, minus Cadence, to figure out how to control my little light speed angel avatar. Dope."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9960
msgid "* It's a question that resolves almost as soon as it crops up. I can move my body and my logical mind in extraordinary ways, but I'm bound to the very human speed at which I process and manifest my emotions."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9961
msgid "*  I lose, but I'm happy about it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9962
msgid "* Only time can tell, I guess. I find myself looking at him when I laugh and smiling at him when he speaks to us. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9963
msgid "* I'm shy, but he gets that, and we share those quiet looks that shy people so heavily rely on. It's nice."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9964
msgid "* Quinn is excited to play the game but honestly sucks at it. Doesn't seem to mind when it's his turn to sit out though."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9965
msgid "* Cadence goes hard and makes many loud noises but only wins a few times. Overall, fun as heck."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9966
msgid "* Eventually, Cadence passes control to Mags and grabs the conversational wheel. * Ok, I know we've moved on from the topic, but like..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9967
msgid "* She claps a hand on Quinns shoulder, looks him in the eye. * My guy. If you want to expand your fashion horizons, I have clothes you can try on. I have hella clothes. I will get them right now if you want. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9968
msgid "* Quinn looks thoroughly flustered by the sudden turn. * Oh, uhh..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9969
msgid "* Cadence leans in, speaks softly. * You need only ask."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9970
msgid "* Magdalena smirks. * Yeah, I've got some stuff I'd, like, adore seeing you in."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9971
msgid "Beryl: I don't have as much as C-Cadence, but you're totally p-permitted to look through it if you'd like!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9972
msgid "* Quinn laughs softly and awkwardly. * Uh, it's not that simple... I wouldn't even know what to pick. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9973
msgid "Cadence: You need to just follow your heart. Be one with the clothes heap. Unleash your inner... * She looks at the rest of us. * How do I say 'girl' without saying 'girl?'"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9974
msgid "Magdalena: Or, just let us pick for you. I'm sure we can collaborate on some outfits."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9975
msgid "* Cadence bounces. * Dress up? DRESS UP?? Should I get my clothes?? I'll get them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9976
msgid "* Beryl speaks up. * Wait! * She looks at Quinn. * Are you c-comfortable with this? It's completely up to you."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9977
msgid "* He shrinks back into his hoodie, protruding only enough for us to witness his blushing cheeks blur with a vigorous nod."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9978
msgid "* We all giggle while Cadence bolts out of the room. Magdalena begins to peruse her dresser, plucking up the occasional component to whatever outfit ideas are blossoming in her brain."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9979
msgid "* When she has an appropriate armful, she deposits it on the bed in a neat stack, just in time for Cadence to burst in and throw an armload on top. Clothes abound, and Quinn fails to hide his excitement."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9980
msgid "Quinn: J-jeez, that's a lot! Am I gonna be trying all that on?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9981
msgid "Cadence: As much of it as you'd like! Starting with... * She grabs some shirts from the pile and holds them up. * What do you prefer? Pink, white, or black?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9982
msgid "Quinn: Uhh..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9983
msgid "Cadence: If you can't choose, a lot of my stuff is both pink, white, and black! * She laughs."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9984
msgid "Quinn: I think... * He considers for a long while. * The... The white?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9985
msgid "Cadence: Good choice. Sad boi aesthetic. I love it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9986
msgid "* She tosses him the shirt and he starts unzipping his hoodie. The shirt beneath it is just as plain. He switches quickly, with his back turned to us, then spins back around."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9987
msgid "Beryl: Adorable! * She walks around, taking in the look."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9988
msgid "* Cadence rifles through the pile some more. * I think it'll go super well with this! * She tosses him a short, pleated skirt."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9989
msgid "* Mags turns toward him, holding something shiny, black, and semitransparent. * This. Under the shirt."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9990
msgid "Cadence: Oh, perfect! That's gonna look killer!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9991
msgid "Magdalena: I might even have matching thigh-highs... * She shifts to a different drawer. * Wait. No. This is even better..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9992
msgid "* She turns around holding a pair of blue and white striped thigh-high socks."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9993
msgid "Beryl: Oh my gosh, yes!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9994
msgid "Magdalena: Not a better match, per say, but a sort of... Tradition. * She tosses him the socks."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9995
msgid "* Quinn catches the socks with the same awkward maneuvers he used for the rest of the torrent of clothes that had been aimed at him. * Ok! One sec... Nobody look!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9996
msgid "* We all turn our backs and listen to the sound of cloth on cloth, a fumbled zipper, the squeak of acrylic, and finally, his voice. * How do I look?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9997
msgid "* We turn and catch him blushing impossibly hard, standing shyly, limbs closed in a protective self-hug. Despite the clothes not sitting quite right, he looks utterly precious."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9998
msgid "* There's a moment of pause before a cacophony of cooing begins. We close in, turning him around, admiring."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:9999
msgid "Cadence: Holy shit. You look good as hell!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10000
msgid "Magdalena: Yeah, this is honestly such an improvement."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10001
msgid "Beryl: You look wonderful! Not that you didn't before! * She smiles."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10002
msgid "Quinn: Th-thanks, everyone! Uh... * He pauses. * Time to take it off?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10003
msgid "Magdalena: I dunno. Do you like it?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10004
msgid "* Quinn can't seem to stop smiling. * Y-yes?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10005
msgid "* Magdalena seems to sense how close to being overwhelmed he is. * Then why not keep it on? We can play some more games? Chill out for a while."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10006
msgid "* Can't tell how you feel about clothes until  you've worn 'em for a bit, anyway..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10007
msgid "* He agrees, and Mags takes a subtle charge of the group, limiting the energy and focusing attention away from Quinn. He seems to appreciate it. It's as chill as she promised."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10008
msgid "* He passes on his turn to play, but only out of comfort, it seems. He spends the whole time smiling like crazy and leaning against Mags' shoulder watching us play."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10009
msgid "* I get strong urges to pat him on the head, but I resist."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10010
msgid "* After a while, he un-snuggles himself from the little pocket he'd curled up in, and sighs. * I should probably head back to the store. I've been away for a while. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10011
msgid "Magdalena: Sure, thing. I'll walk you back?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10012
msgid "Quinn: Dope. * He pauses. * Uh, I'll just get changed, then."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10013
msgid "Magdalena: Cool. If you wanna borrow any of my stuff, feel free."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10014
msgid "Cadence: Same! Literally, I have so much!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10015
msgid "* Quinn smiles. * Rad. I'll skip it this time, but... We should do this again! If you guys feel like it! Or whatever!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10016
msgid "Cadence: Hell yeah! I'm thinking we add some make-up to the mix next time?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10017
msgid "* Magdalena smiles. * Beryl's right, though. No pressure. Also, keep the socks, at the very least. Pretty sure that pair had never even been worn."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10018
msgid "Beryl: You can have these ones as well! I don't have much in terms of clothing variety, but striped thigh highs are classic. * She tosses him a pair of green and purple ones."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10019
msgid "Cadence: You know what? I think I have some too! * She retrieves a pair of pink and greys from the heap. * And thus, we pass our legacy unto you. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10020
msgid "* She strikes a pose. * GO NOW! MAY YOUR STRIPEY THIGH-HIGHS KEEP YOU SAFE AMONGST THE SHADOWS OF THIS HARSH WORLD!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10021
msgid "* He changes, tucks the wad of socks under his arms, and continues to giggle-blush. Just like that, Mags and Quinn wave their goodbyes and head out towards Skipnoise. I let myself out as well."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10022
msgid "* The call of a nice chill friend pile is strong today. Think I'll head to Sunshine Girders to see who's around."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10023
msgid "* I do the walk, climb the stairs, assess the hall. The door to Magdalena and Beryl's place is open, and there are voices coming from within."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10024
msgid "* I slip inside. Beryl is sitting at her drafting table, pen to paper, and Cadence is bouncing on the edge of her bed, looking over her shoulder."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10025
msgid "Cadence: Beautiful! Ok, now give it another dick! On the end of it's tail!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10026
msgid "Beryl: You're the boss! Although, I need to p-point out that it already has five d-dicks."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10027
msgid "Cadence: Oh, you sweet, innocent noodle. * She waves at me. * Hi HC!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10028
msgid "Heya! * I join Cadence on the bed. * So, watcha drawing?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10029
msgid "Beryl: Oh, it's just a demon. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10030
msgid "Cadence: A CUM demon! From GAY HELL! And I wanna suck it's tail-dick so BAD! * She laughs and gives Beryl a smooch on the cheek."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10031
msgid "* Suddenly, Mags and Quinn push through the door and into the apartment. In a blur of almost droid-like speed, Beryl whips the dick drawing off the table and buries it in the closest bin."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10032
msgid "* Mags notices, gives her a knowing smile. * Hey, babe. Getting into trouble?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10033
msgid "Beryl: Psh! Nothing but wholesome stuff going on here!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10034
msgid "* We all laugh, except for Quinn, who just finds a corner to prop his longboard. It's beat to hell, but some sweet-looking chrome shows through the filth."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10035
msgid "* Mags dumps the sweatshirt she's been carrying into a clothes pile in front of a closet door, then walks over to Beryl, gives her a kiss, exchanges an 'I love you.' Cute."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10036
msgid "Quinn: Oh, yo. You're like, an artist? * He walks around the room, examining all the little drawings that have been taped up. * That's sick. You're really good."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10037
msgid "Beryl: Th-thanks! * She turns and busies herself drawing, tries to look like she's doing something cooler than making embarrassed inky spirals on the page."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10038
msgid "Magdalena: Yeah, she's amazing. Check this out. * She points towards a cluster of pages taped up above their bed. * She was doing self-portraits for a while."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10039
msgid "Beryl: Yeah! To study! You know?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10040
msgid "* Magdalena gazes at the visage emerging from the mess of charcoal on the largest of the pages. * Takes a lot of skill to capture this kinda beauty. These drawings are my fave."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10041
msgid "* Quinn examines them. * Damn, yeah. These are hella... * He leans closer. * Hella dope."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10042
msgid "* Beryl squeaks in embarrassment. * Thank you! So, what are we up t-to? Something other th-than showering my shy little self with praise?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10043
msgid "* Quinn wanders through the laughter, trying to look like he's retreating to Magdalena's side, trying to keep from dropping his chill despite, once again, plunging into the deep end of the trans girl pool."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10044
msgid "* I study him, trying to find a clue as to how to bridge the gap, but his getup is infinitely nondescript. There's information in the excessive rolls of hoodie and baggy jeans, but nothing that tells me to engage."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10045
msgid "Magdalena: Nothing. Just unloading some stuff before Quinn and I hit the Lemon."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10046
msgid "Quinn: Yeah, I'm not tryna lug my longboard there. And home is a ways away."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10047
msgid "* Magdalena smirks. * I mean, you coulda left it at the convenience store. * She turns to the rest of us. * I think he wanted to get changed, too."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10048
msgid "* He blushes, chuckles, gives Magdalena and gentle shove. * Bitch..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10049
msgid "* Cadence's eyes sparkle. * Don't be embarrassed! We'd love to dress you up again!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10050
msgid "Magdalena: Or, you know, do be embarrassed. It's pretty fucking precious."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10051
msgid "* He clears his throat, brushes off Mags' comment. * It's Cadence, right? * He smiles at her. * No Emotistar this time?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10052
msgid "Cadence: No, I left it at home with my other consoles. I played it too much and got one of those Emotiscan headaches. I live literally next door though, if you want me to go snag it!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10053
msgid "Quinn: Nah, it's cool. I got my ass kicked enough last time. * He laughs."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10054
msgid "* Cadence grins. * What can I say. I love to kick an ass or two."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10055
msgid "* Magdalena opens the fridge in the kitchen alcove, raises her voice enough to carry to us clearly. * It's not a joke. She will kick your real life ass."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10056
msgid "Cadence: Psh. All things considered, kicking isn't all that high on the list of things I like to do to assess. I'm a lover, not a fighter."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10057
msgid "Beryl: You can k-kick my ass, Cadence. * She snickers. * That's a, um, invitation, not a statement of fact."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10058
msgid "I mean, it's probably both, right? No offense, Beryl."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10059
msgid "Beryl: It's true. * She peels away from the drawing table and flops onto the bed, then gives Cadence's bicep a squeeze. * Have you felt this thing? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10060
msgid "* I give the muscle a squeeze. She's soft and hard at the same time. Not much, compared to me, but still impressive. * Damn, Cadence."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10061
msgid "* Mags returns with a glass of water and some kinda jelly-filled tube snack."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10062
msgid "Quinn: Oh, snap, I could snack, too! If you've got anything."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10063
msgid "Magdalena: Duh. Kitchen's right there. * She nods back over her shoulder towards the densely-packed nook."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10064
msgid "Beryl: Rude! He's our guest! Want me t-to get you something?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10065
msgid "Quinn: No, it's cool, I can manage. * His laugh is a cue, not a reflex. A sound he makes to fill space and to signal that everything is fine."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10066
msgid "* Magdalena looks pleased. * He likes it when I boss him around."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10067
msgid "* This time, the laugh is authentic, unavoidable, and revealing. * You just like to power trip! No point tryna stop that train..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10068
msgid "* He disappears, giggling, into the kitchen nook. Mags takes a seat on the stool next to the bed, smiles at us. * God, he's so fucking cute."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10069
msgid "Beryl: I remember those days! Just starting out on the whole g-gender experimentation thing. I'm really glad he's having fun."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10070
msgid "Cadence: Hell yes! More tgirls for the tgirl heap! * Cadence cranes to peek into the kitchen. * You're right, she's crazy cute!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10071
msgid "* Mags' smile fades. * Chill, Cadence. It's gonna be a lot less cathartic for him if he's under pressure."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10072
msgid "Beryl: Yeah, I get the feeling he's about t-to stray from a predetermined gender path. No need to push him towards another one."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10073
msgid "* Cadence snorts. * I mean sure, but like, look at the signs! I'll bet you a six pack of 'glug that he's gonna turn out to be a girl!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10074
msgid "Magdalena: Ugh! I'm literally not saying he's not a trans girl. I have no idea what he is and I just think it's a dick move to start assuming things."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10075
msgid "* Cadence's smile disappears as well. * Sure but like, no one told me I could just be a girl. I had to figure that shit out. I would have loved it if a bunch of transes showed me the way."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10076
msgid "Magdalena: Seriously, Cadence. Just be chill."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10077
msgid "* Quinn returns from the kitchen with a tube of his own. Same as the one Mags was slurping, but a different color."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10078
msgid "Quinn: Watcha talking about?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10079
msgid "* Beryl responds a little too quickly. * Nothing! Just..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10080
msgid "Cadence: Just... things!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10081
msgid "Quinn: Cool, cool... I like..... Things...."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10082
msgid "* He stares at his longboard propped up in the corner, as if he's dreading that anyone will use it as the mild conversation starter it could easily become."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10083
msgid "* Mags breaks the lull. * Um, excuse me? Are you eating the last blue raspberry?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10084
msgid "* Quinn glances at the tube in his hand. * Oops. Guess so. * He takes a final swig, drains the tube of it's vital essence, lets it crumple in his hand."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10085
msgid "Magdalena: You owe me one, now, bitch. I'm gonna rob your convenience store."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10086
msgid "* Quinn laughs. * Yeah, if you wanna get fucked up."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10087
msgid "* Cadence also laughs. * Are you two gonna brawl in the parking lot? Should I make popcorn?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10088
msgid "* Beryl hops up and does a surprisingly high kick, but almost falls over. * D-dibs on fighting winner!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10089
msgid "* Mag's smirk breaks into a full-on satanic grin. * Come. Now. * She turns and heads out the door."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10090
msgid "* Quinn blushes. * Oh, uh... I thought we were just joking?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10091
msgid "* Cadence and Beryl both get up, start pushing him to the door. * Better do as she says..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10092
msgid "* Beryl giggles and grabs a two-liter of Berryglug from the fridge. * Yeah, she's a dangerous woman."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10093
msgid "* Cadence grabs the longboard as we depart. * Wouldn't want to make her wait."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10094
msgid "* We usher Quinn down the hall and to the bare, fractured cement that surrounds the building. He sighs when he sees that Mags isn't squared up, but has instead found a chunk of rubble to rest on."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10095
msgid "* Beryl and I hop up onto the concrete block next to her. The sky seems to hang a bit farther up than usual, father away than its vibrant Magenta would suggest."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10096
msgid "* Mags is smiling. * You really thought I was gonna fight you? I don't hit girls."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10097
msgid "* I watch Quinn try and articulate his internal keymashing. * I died."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10098
msgid "* He jumps up onto the block of concrete and stares at the sky with the rest of us. Except Cadence, who appears to be trying to do a longboard ollie for some reason."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10099
msgid "* Beryl Passes around the big Berryglug and we all take a swig. * It's such a nice d-day! And so quiet, this far from Gelcorp and downtown and stuff."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10100
msgid "* I look at the purple fluid sloshing around in the bottle, then up at the sky, already a tone darker than it was a bit ago. * You know, if we wait a bit? The sky will be the same color as the glug."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10101
msgid "Quinn: Man, that's kinda beautiful. * He lifts the bottle, squints, compares it to the polluted cloud. * Purple, inside and out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10102
msgid "* Mags snatches the bottle. * You fucking dork."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10103
msgid "* After twenty or so minutes of us just hanging out, watching Cadence remain uninjured and the world at large, my prophecy comes true. The sky turns Berryglug and the bottle is polished off."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10104
msgid "Magdalena: We should probably head out. It'll be full dark soon. You wanna change before we go?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10105
msgid "* Quinn glances back toward the apartment, then outward over the chasm between us and the Lemon. * Nah, I'll skip it. I'm fine like this."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10106
msgid "Magdalena: Right. Let's cruise. * She starts walking, and after a few goodbyes, Quinn follows."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10107
msgid "* Once they've disappeared into the ruins, Cadence skates over to our perch and flips the board up into her hand."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10108
msgid "* Cadence licks her teeth, gives into a sudden urge to say something she knows she'll regret. * Mags called her a girl! What a hypocrite!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10109
msgid "* Beryl sighs. * Quinn is Magdalena's friend. She knows him b-better than we do, what he responds to..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10110
msgid "How to push his buttons."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10111
msgid "Beryl: Eg-Exactly. She was just making fun of him."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10112
msgid "* Cadence shuffles around. * I know, I know. But still!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10113
msgid "Beryl: It's n-not th---"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10114
msgid "* Cadence interrupts. * I knoooooow, I'm sorry! I'm just being a noodle for some reason. I'll catch ya later."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10115
msgid "* She starts skating away towards the ruins, then stops, dismounts, and walks back."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10116
msgid "Cadence: I forgot this isn't mine... * She hoists the longboard."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10117
msgid "Beryl: It sure isn't."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10118
msgid "Cadence: And also, I live here. * She nods towards the door to Sunshine Girders."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10119
msgid "Beryl: You sure do."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10120
msgid "Cadence: Big noodle hours, I guess..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10121
msgid "* Beryl laughs and give her a hug. * G-go home, you noodle."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10122
msgid "* She does. We wait a bit longer, watch the sky darken to a velvety plum. No stars. Never stars. But still beautiful, in it's way."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10123
msgid "* And then Beryl goes back inside and I head home."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10124
msgid "* With the tension broken, we all fall into a relaxed groove. Beryl goes back to drawing and Cadence returns to her to room. After a bit, she appears at the door again with a pile of clothes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10125
msgid "* She deposits them on the back of a chair and quietly goes back to the bed. No one says anything, but Quinn is eyeing them like crazy."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10126
msgid "* Fortunately, he seems to be the type who's confidence and shyness can act in parallel, and even though he seems to be searching for an ambient role among us, he's excited to be here."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10127
msgid "* The door to Mags' and Beryl's unit is slightly cracked open."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10128
msgid "* I can hear the sounds of laughter, Cadence squealing, and the beeps and boops of some video game."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:10129
msgid "* Inside, Beryl, Cadence, and Quinn are piled on the bed with controllers in their hands, eyes darting back and forth across the screen with rapt attention."
