msgstr ""

#: result.py:13869
msgid "Olivia: Good. Not as worried about you as I am about these two, though. * She jabs a thumb in Decima and Cadence's direction."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13870
msgid "* Decima opens her mouth to let out some smartassery, but Cadence cuts her off. * I'll keep her in check."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13871
msgid "Olivia: See that you do."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13872
msgid "* Beryl laughs nervously. * Well, g-good work, everyone! * She waves."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13873
msgid "* We all follow her out, leaving Forcier and Olivia behind, then head to our respective homes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13874
msgid "* I'm halfway to Olivia and Forcier's place when I remember we arranged to meet at The Lemon. I take the long way around the chasm, cutting through the industrial ruins."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13875
msgid "* The silhouette of Gelcorp looms more ominously than usual..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13876
msgid "* Even so, the chatter of customers and heat exhaust from the buildings on Skipnoise Ave make me feel safe. I enter The Lemon and start looking around."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13877
msgid "* The crowd inside is moving, matching the energy of the pulsing music as they dance. I don't see anyone familiar until Forcier, towering over the dancers, waves me down."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13878
msgid "Forcier: Pardon this meetings unconventional venue. The apartment may not be safe. Come."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13879
msgid "* I follow them to the back where Olivia and Decima are leaning against the wall. They look concerned. Even Decima's typical cocky smile is missing. She's also wearing a weird zip coat that I've never seen on her before."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13880
msgid "Olivia: You made it. Good. Since we ran into that Gelcorp guy, we've had to put our plan into motion earlier than we thought."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13881
msgid "Olivia: Which means we don't really have a plan."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13882
msgid "Decima: Psh, this totally counts as a plan. Sometimes, simple is better, right? * She shifts uncomfortably in the heavy zip coat."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13883
msgid "Olivia: Not when you're trying to break into a chemical treatment plant inside the Gelcorp compound."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13884
msgid "Forcier: Your optimism is much appreciated though, Decima. I'm not quite sure you're wrong."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13885
msgid "Forcier: Getting inside the Gelcorp perimeter will be difficult, but the plant itself is a small satellite of Gelcorp proper. Security there should be low."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13886
msgid "Olivia: True. So, our plan is pretty much just to breach that perimeter. Beyond that, we're playing it by ear."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13887
msgid "* Decima opens her zip coat, revealing some hefty bolt cutters. * You can tell the situation is dire cause I'm not making a joke about this right now."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13888
msgid "Forcier: Shall we go meet the others?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13889
msgid "Olivia: Yeah. Take Decima and go find Cadence. I'll get Mags and meet you at the Mall."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13890
msgid "* Go with Olivia to get Mags"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13891
msgid "* Go with Forcier and Decima to get Cadence."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13892
msgid "I'll stick with you, Olivia."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13893 result.py:13906
msgid "Olivia: Excellent. Let's head out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13894 result.py:13907
msgid "* We stagger our exits on Olivia's advice, trying to blend in with other patrons as they stumble out into the street, too spent or drunk to keep dancing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13895
msgid "* Olivia explains in a hushed voice that Magdalena and Cadence are keeping watch in case the Gelcorp agent appears. We head up the street towards the bus stop where Mags was stationed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13896
msgid "* When she sees us, she lowers her phone and breathes a sigh of relief. * Finally. I have no idea why I agreed to this. I fucking hate being alone out here."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13897
msgid "Olivia: Any sign of that Gelcorp asshole?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13898
msgid "* Magdalena scoots in close to us as we start walking back. * Nope, none. So far, we're fine."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13899
msgid "Olivia: Excellent. It'd be fucked up if we blew this operation before getting to the hard part. * She cracks a smile."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13900
msgid "* We reach the top of the stairs to the second level of Skipnoise Ave and find a spot to wait outside the Mall. Shouldn't be long till Cadence, Decima, and Forcier arrive."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13901
msgid "* Mags looks me up and down, her skepticism obvious. * You sure you're ready for this? * She looks at Olivia. * She's the one going in, right?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13902
msgid "Olivia: Not sure yet, but... Probably. * She grits her teeth. * I didn't even have time to get blueprints for this fucking place... Let's just focus on getting eyes on the building. We can think of a plan from there. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13903
msgid "* Soon, the others appear at the bottom of the stairs. Despite the atmosphere, Cadence and Decima can't help smiling around each other."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13904
msgid "* As they ascend to our level, we catch the tail end of a conversation about cats."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13905
msgid "* I turn to Forcier and Decima. * I'll stick with you two."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13908
msgid "* According to Forcier, Mags and Cadence have been keeping watch during our meeting in case the Gelcorp agent appears. We head down the street towards the convenience store where Cadence was stationed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13909
msgid "* Inside, she's sitting on top of a cooler and thumbing through a magazine. When she notices us, she hops up and gives us each a hug."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13910
msgid "Forcier: It's good to see you, Cadence. I trust there's been no sign of that Gelcorp agent."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13911
msgid "* Cadence salutes the clerk as she leads us out of the store. He waves back awkwardly. * Nope! Although I was kind of distracted by that cat. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13912
msgid "* Decima gestures to the magazine still clutched in Cadence's hand. * You're bringing that?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13913
msgid "Cadence: Yeah, it felt weird to read it without buying it. * She rolls it up and tucks it in her pocket."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13914
msgid "Decima: God damn, you're so fucking adorable!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13915
msgid "* Despite the tense mood, Decima and Cadence can't help but smile around each other as we walk. By the time we make it up the stairs to Skipnoise Ave's second level, we're all doing our best to forget our stress."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13916
msgid "* As we wait, we try and ignore the encroaching thoughts of danger and failure and all the bad shit we're about to walk into. Being together helps, especially when Olivia and Mags show up. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13917
msgid "* With the group formed up, we start heading down the rubble-strewn slope behind Skipnoise Ave and towards industrial ruin. Gelcorp isn't too far from here."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13918
msgid "* The tight architecture of the businesses surrounding Skipnoise Ave give way to the vast, empty, hulking structures that jut out of the barren surface of the industrial district. We stick to the shadows as we walk."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13919
msgid "* The perimeter, marked by a 40 foot chain-link fence, cuts a vast circle in the district, beyond which the ruins have been cleared down to their foundations."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13920
msgid "* In the distance, nestled into the bases of the Gelcorp's spires and smokestacks, the employee housing is visible."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13921
msgid "* Rows of short buildings, stacked shipping containers, vehicles, and the main Gelcorp campus, all contained within a walled partition. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13922
msgid "* A dozen spotlights trace broad spirographs on the pavement surrounding this central nexus, catching intruders or escapees.  As far away as we are, the twinkling lights look almost peaceful."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13923
msgid "* To our right, the lights burn brighter, closer, marking the front gate through the perimeter. Drones and floodlights enable armed guards to scrutinize anyone trying to gain passage."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13924
msgid "* Fortunately, we're not using the gate."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13925
msgid "* We leap from the shadows and huddle around the base of the fence. Decima throws off her jacket and gets to work with the bolt cutters."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13926
msgid "* Decima speaks between strained grunts as she works her way through the links. * So, do we know where we're going once we get through?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13927
msgid "* Olivia glances at her wrist computer. * The plant is a half mile to our northwest. It's built in a lowered canal that houses the drainage pipes and stuff, so it won't be visible till we're closer."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13928
msgid "* Sure enough, in the direction she's gesturing, a sliver of pale light catches the edge of a little chasm."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13929
msgid "* The route there is dark, but extremely exposed. Beyond it, blinking surveillance drones orbit the main Gelcorp campus."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13930
msgid "* Decima clips the last link. * Time to run?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13931
msgid "Foricer: We need to stay grouped during this leg. Is everyone ready? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13932
msgid "* We all nod and slip through the gap. After waiting for a drone to fly by, Olivia gives the cue, and we take off. It's a stressful run but we're lucky to be so far outside the range of inner Gelcorp's spotlights."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13933
msgid "* Feet slamming into hard ground as we try and avoid corporate security... I'm reminded of the escape and chase that brought me here to Pira. I was gonna lay low. Figures."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13934
msgid "* I try my best to keep my shit together and not outrun my friends. When we're in range of the canals edge, we dive behind some low rubble. Not really a hiding place, but it makes us feel a little less vulnerable."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13935
msgid "* As we peep over the edge, our hearts sink. The plant is there, spanning the channel above three huge pipes leading south from Gelcorp, as we expected, but it's completely swarmed with activity."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13936
msgid "* Gelcorp workers in biohazard suits march the catwalks between the entrances to the plant and the little mobile labs that have deployed them, carrying equipment and samples for analysis."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13937
msgid "*  Pairs of security guards bestraddle each entrance and alarm lights on the walls flash. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13938
msgid "* Olivia pulls her head back and collapses on the safe side of the concrete rubble. Her whispered voice is audibly shaken. * Fuck! This is completely fucked!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13939
msgid "* Cadence's matches Olivia's volume, but it's twice as spooked. * Oh my gods... What are we gonna do? We've gotta get out of here!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13940
msgid "Decima: We've come this far, though... We might not get another chance..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13941
msgid "Olivia: As much as I'd like to finish what we started, it's not logical to keep risking everything just cause we risked so much to get here."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13942
msgid "* There's a tense pause, and for a while we can only hear the drone of the engine. We glance around at each other, except Forcier, who peers pensively over the edge.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13943
msgid "Magdalena: I think we should fucking do it. They're just people. There's gotta be a way to deal with them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13944
msgid "Forcier: I agree. It will be dangerous to continue, but based on this activity, it's likely that we've stumbled upon something far more relevant to our investigation than we hoped."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13945
msgid "Olivia: Yeah... You're right. HC, take this. I'll contact you once you're inside. * She hands me a tiny earpiece. I take it and stuff it in my ear hole."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13946
msgid "* We all look back over the edge, trying to pinpoint some weakness in the plants defenses. To our right is the main entrance and the busiest catwalk."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13947
msgid "* It's there, floating 20 feet from the door that the mobile lab is hovering."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13948
msgid "* Around the left, in the wall facing us, is a smaller back door which offers access to a few valves and small pipes leading up the exterior wall of the building. A ladder near the door also offers roof access."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13949
msgid "* Below the stilted structure, ascending between the large pipes that the plant is built above, there's another ladder."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13950
msgid "* From our vantage point, it's impossible to see where it leads, but presumably there is a tertiary entrance hatch underneath the plant."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13951
msgid "* At the foot of this ladder, more biohazard suited figures roam the soggy, algae-mottled sluice at the lowest point of the channel, surveying the filth with glowing wands and Geiger counters. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13952
msgid "* We silently count the guards; Six visible from this side of the building. At least two dozen of the faceless scientists. Three drones. There's no easy answer..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13953
msgid "If we could distract one of those guards..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13954
msgid "If we could get one of those suits...."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13955
msgid "If we could hack one of those drones..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13956
msgid "Olivia: Right. If we can get them away from a door we have a chance."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13957
msgid "* Cadence gestures to the door closest to us, out of sight of the majority of the scientists. * That's the one. I mean I guess that's obvious... Uhh, Let the record show that I did, in fact, contribute!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13958
msgid "Decima: Alright, I've got a plan. How about...... We throw Cadence at them."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13959
msgid "* Cadence almost breaks her whisper. * You bitch! For real though, how are we gonna do this?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13960
msgid "* Olivia raises her wrist computer and starts typing. * I've got an idea. Haven't used this one in a while, let's see if it still works."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13961
msgid "* With her gaze fixed on the closest guards, she taps a button on her visor. A light blinks, and she moves her wrist towards Forcier's lips."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13962
msgid "* Forcier clears their throat, then puts on a deeper, less enunciated voice. * Uhh, Can we get some help 'round here? Just dumped a sample crate and it's a hell of a mess."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13963
msgid "* There's no audible response. Apparently, Olivia's radio hack is a one way street. Either way, one guard moves a hand to the walkie talkie on his hip. The other raises his hands and takes a step back"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13964
msgid "* The first guard sighs and begrudgingly marches around toward the front of the building. The clock is now ticking."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13965
msgid "Decima: Fuck. Well, one down! That's progress! Should we have come up with another step to this plan before putting it in motion though?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13966
msgid "Olivia: No. * She points that blank, chrome visor in my direction. * You've gotta rush him, HC."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13967 result.py:13986
msgid "* Nod."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13969
msgid "* I make sure the ear piece is firmly secured, then I sprint down the edge of the channel towards the nearest catwalk, keeping my feet light and quiet. By the time the guard notices me, I'm only about 55 feet away."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13970
msgid "* His eyes widen and his hands move to the baton on his belt, but it's too late."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13971
msgid "* I'm on him, covering his mouth and pushing him through the door. In one quick motion, I leap through, slide it shut behind me, and pin him down."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13972
msgid "* With an arm around his neck, I press a knee into his back and flex. When I'm sure he's unconscious, I straighten up and survey the room."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13973
msgid "Olivia: HC, we've gotta get this done. Now. We don't have another option."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13974
msgid "B-but... * This sucks..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13975
msgid "Forcier: None of us are capable of incapacitating a guard without risking harm to both us and them. We need your help if we're going to proceed.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13976
msgid "O-ok... * I try to shake the anxiety out of my body, but shaking is as far as I get. A few deep breaths and I'm as ready as I think I'm likely to get. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13977
msgid "Decima: You wanna dress up as some kinda chemical-proof horror scientist? That's adorable! I'm also casting my vote for the dress-up plan!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13978
msgid "Olivia: If we can lure one of them far enough away from the rest, I don't see why this plan won't work. How are we gonna swing that though?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13979
msgid "Forcier: Maybe we don't need to. Those hover labs don't look big enough to include restrooms. Eventually, one of them is going to need to find some privacy."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13980
msgid "Cadence: Come on, none of those guys are dumb enough to open their suits without being in some kind of decontamination machine or something."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13981
msgid "* There's a moment of silence as we weigh Gelcorps safety standards against the intelligence of its employees."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13982
msgid "Decima: We should take bets. My money's on that bitch right there. * She points out a lumbering scientist just as they try and wipe their nose through their face mask."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13983
msgid "* We watch in silence. I guess things are too tense to engage with Decima's foolishness. A bit later, though, when the scientist Decima picked starts looking for a place to pee, we all smile. I guess it's a good omen."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13984
msgid "* The scientist wanders away from the group and behind some of the pillars that are supporting the plant. If we're gonna move on them, now is the time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13985
msgid "* Olivia points that blank, chrome visor in my direction. * You got this?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13987
msgid "* Hesitate."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13988
msgid "* I launch myself down the  40 foot cement slope at full speed, making it in only a few leaping bounds. When I hit the ground, I roll and pop up behind the scientist."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13989
msgid "*  A quick strike to the temple disorients them, giving me an opening to pick them up and run them up the slope."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13990
msgid "* About halfway up, I go ahead and throw them the rest of the way, then sprint up behind them. Mags, Decima, and Forcier are holding the scientist down and unzipping the suit."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13991
msgid "* I hunch over their chest and grab their neck. It doesn't take long for me to choke them into unconsiousness."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13992
msgid "Magdalena: Fuck it. As I said, they're just people. * She jumps up and over the ledge, then slides  40 feet down the grimy cement slope. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13993
msgid "* At the bottom, she lets the momentum carry her into a sprint, then body-slams the scientist from behind, hammering their head into the metal pillar."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13994
msgid "* The scientist slumps to the ground, unconscious, and Mags starts unzipping the suit. When she's got it off of him, she bundles it up and starts scrambling up the slope."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13995
msgid "* It isn't easy, and the constant threat that a guard will glance over doesn't help."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13996
msgid "* When she's in range, we reach down and pull her up the rest of the way. She settles down behind the rubble with us, breathing hard and frowning."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13997
msgid "* She glances at the mud and algae spattered around her ankles and on her knees. * God, that was disgusting. Whatever, someone just please take this from me. * She holds up the suit."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13998
msgid "* I take the contamination suit and slip it over my clothes, then zip it up to my neck. Slipping the mirrored plastic visage over my face completes the look, making me indistinguishable from a Gelcorp employee."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:13999
msgid "So, I just walk on into the plant? * My voice resonates in the suit. I hope they can hear me out there..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14000
msgid "Olivia: Yes. I'll be in radio contact with you once you're inside."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14001
msgid "* I do it. The nearest catwalk is a ways down the channel to our right, but once I make it, I'm in plain view to anyone working around the site. Especially the guards. I puff up my chest and try to look like I belong."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14002
msgid "* As I cross the metal grated walkway towards the door, the guards look at me. I don't slow down, and despite my body's urge to freeze up, I smoothly walk through the door."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14003
msgid "* I made it. I'm in. Panting, I unzip the suit and dump it on the floor. The clean breath of air I was hoping for tastes kinda weird though."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14004
msgid "* Olivia turns towards the skies. * That... That actually might be possible. I like the way you think, HC. Gimme a second. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14005
msgid "* She raises her wrist computer and hones in on one of the surveillance drones circling below us in the channel, aiming her visor while tracing her finger across the screen. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14006
msgid "* She smirks. * Yeah, this won't be a problem. These things are not exactly cutting edge."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14007
msgid "* Only a few seconds later, a pale greenish light pops up onto her screen, gleaming against the underside of her visor. * Got one."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14008
msgid "* Without breaking her focus on the drone, she hands me an earpiece."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14009
msgid "Olivia: Here. I'll contact you once you're on the inside."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14010
msgid "* I stuff the little device into my ear hole and return my attention to Olivia's tech magic."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14011
msgid "* We all watch as the drone starts moving erratically, matching the motions of Olivia's fingers as they glide across the touchscreen of her computer. It's almost elegant. Until the crash."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14012
msgid "* The drone slams hard into the wall of the mobile lab, causing it to tilt and dip, drifting slowing away from the catwalk at which it was docked."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14013
msgid "* Startled scientists hop out and all the guards rush towards the sound. The way is clear."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14014
msgid "Forcier: Now is the time, HC. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14015
msgid "* I nod and dash along the channel to the nearest point where the catwalk meets its edge. Grabbing the railing to help redirect my momentum, I sprint the 20 feet across the exposed bridge and to the door of the plant."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14016
msgid "* I hammer the button next to the door repeatedly, trying not to let myself glance over to where Olivia's distraction is going down, trying to forget how easy it would be for someone to spot me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14017
msgid "* The door slides open and I slip inside, shutting it behind me and letting the air out of my tense chest. It's not time to relax, but at least I'm not in direct danger. I straighten up & survey the room."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14018
msgid "* The atmosphere is thick and hazy. I don't really know what the inside of a water treatment plant is supposed to look like, but I was expecting a lot less... Slime..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14019
msgid "* Pinkish residue clings to every surface, oozing from the seams in the heavy boilers and pipes that crowd the low, utilitarian architecture. I guess finding a sample won't be as hard as I'd have guessed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14020
msgid "* Sample. Right. Ok, time to get my head in the game. I don't have long to explore in here before they get wise and come after me, so I better focus."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14021
msgid "* I need to find a sample of the slime and look for information regarding what it actually is."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14022
msgid "* Olivia's voice crackles in through the earpiece. * We're keeping watch out here. Get it done, HC."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14023
msgid "* Olivia's voice crackles in through the earpiece. * Based on the situation out here, I'd say you've got about two minutes. Get it done, HC."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14024
msgid "* I cautiously step up to the raised circular opening that's steaming ominously in the center of the room, and peer inside. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14025
msgid "* Below me, in a domed, metal cistern, is a pulsating, writhing consolidation of living slime, swirling despite its viscosity. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14026
msgid "* There must be at least five thousand gallons here, depending on how far the cistern is below the opaque surface of the slime. The mass leans tidally towards me as I approach."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14027
msgid "* Tendrils start to form and creep up the wall at my feet. My gut says run, but I hesitate. Something tells me that getting a sample from this particular slime source is gonna be important."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14028
msgid "* I produce a vial and consider the safest way to get close enough to the slime to bottle a bit of it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14029
msgid "*  Several little pseudopods begin to inch over the brim of the cistern, followed by a much girthier one. That's my target."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14030
msgid "* Pin it with my foot."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14031
msgid "* Bait it with my ass."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14032
msgid "* I stomp the tendril before it's able to progress any further. It splatters, but manages to keep enough of a form for me to scoop up a quick sample."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14033
msgid "* I screw the lid back on and kick what's left of the pseudopod back into the cistern, then withdraw."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14034
msgid "* I expose my lower half and get on all fours, ass facing the cistern, and start gently wiggling it. Immediately, I feel the tendrils start inching their way along my calves and up my legs. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14035
msgid "* A gentle slap indicates that the larger pseudopod has flopped against my ass. Having found its mark, it starts working its way around the perimeter of my hole, gently probing. I brace for penetration. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14036
msgid "* When it enters my ass, I reach backwards, between my legs, and grab it, then sit upright, pinning it under my ass as I pull a length up between my legs."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14037
msgid "* Having it restrained, I take a small vialful and replace the cap, then free the tentacle."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14038
msgid "* I slip the tentacle from my ass, then kick it back into the cistern. If only I had more time to waste."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14039
msgid "* The large clear vat appears to be undamaged, but is coated inside and out with the same thin pink residue as everything else."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14040
msgid "* The consoles here are covered in cryptic controls, nothing I recognize how to operate, except for one blinking screen in the corner. It looks like a security feed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14041
msgid "* Play it back."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14042
msgid "* Take the cartridge."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14043
msgid "* I rewind a bit and let it play..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14044
msgid "* The slime is gone. A nervous-looking scientist darts through the room, something tucked under his coat. Trembling, I fast-forward a few hours. Suddenly, the slime appears."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14045
msgid "* Hazard-suited employees move about the room, scraping the slime from various surfaces into vials, making sure to keep some distance between themselves and the central opening to the cistern. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14046
msgid "* Every once in a while, one or two guards wearing gas-masks do a sweep of the room."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14047
msgid "* I swallow, hoping that their next search isn't soon. Trying to pick up the pace, I fast forward toward the present, scanning the screen for anything that stands out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14048
msgid "* I stop when I see a familiar figure appear in the doorway. It's me. Fuck... I quickly eject the cartridge and pocket it, but there's no way they don't stream this feed somewhere offsite."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14049
msgid "* I step away from the console and try to subdue my anxiety, breathing deeply and closing my eyes. Whatever. I can break down later."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14050
msgid "* I pop the little cart out of its slot and tuck it away. There's gotta be some useful information on this thing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14051
msgid "* The silence abruptly breaks into the sharp static of an incoming radio signal. Olivia sounds panicked. * Guard incoming! You've got about 10 seconds, HC! "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14052
msgid "* Fuck Fuck Fuck Fuck Fuck Fuck ok I'd better find a place to hide real fucking quick."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14053
msgid "* I hit the floor and roll into the darkness under the control room, belly crawling back into the farthest corner and hunkering down just in time to catch the pneumatic hiss of a door sliding open."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14054
msgid "* A moment later, the heavy, armored boots of a Gelcorp security guard tramp across the grated floor, following the sweeping beam of a flashlight."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14055
msgid "* The guard pauses when he gets to the edge of the cistern, the rasping of his respirator echoing along with the wet slap of dripping slime."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14056 result.py:14062
msgid "* I hold my breath and still my heart, waiting for the bastard to turn his light in my direction, to draw the baton from his belt, to... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14057
msgid "* But it doesn't happpen. He walks on toward the far end of the room and exits. I sigh my relief and crawl out from under the control room."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14058
msgid "* I dive into the darkness behind one of the boilers, but against my expectations, there's quite a bit more slime back here than there is on the rest of the floor."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14059
msgid "* As soon as my feet hit the slick cement, they shoot out from under me and I land hard on my ass. I'm real glad my hip-chassis is made of metal, although it does make a hell of a racket."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14060
msgid "* A moment later, a door opens and the heavy, armored boots of a Gelcorp security guard tramp across the grated floor, following the sweeping beam of a flashlight. I bite my lip against the pain and hope he didn't hear me. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14061
msgid "* The guard pauses when he get's to the edge of the cistern, the rasping of his respirator echoing along with the wet slap of dripping slime."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14063
msgid "* But it doesn't happen. He walks on toward the far end of the room and exits. I sigh my relief and crawl out from behind the boiler."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14064
msgid "* I slip into the little storage closet and slide the door closed behind me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14065
msgid "* It's pitch black in here except for a slit of light around the edge of the door. I hunker down just in time to catch the muffled pneumatic hiss of a door sliding open"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14066
msgid "*  A moment later, the heavy, armored boots of a Gelcorp security guard tramp across the grated floor."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14067
msgid "*  I shut my eyes, as if that would help, and try not to imagine the door opening and the guard standing in front of me, baton in hand."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14068
msgid "* Suddenly, the footsteps stop. No, please. Please keep walking. Please just leave me alone. Please. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14069
msgid "* I don't know how much time passes, but I keep still and quiet, and eventually, the footsteps resume, leading across the room and out the door."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14070
msgid "* I let out all that air and take a few breaths, trying to calm down, then I step out of the closet."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14071 result.py:14078
msgid "* I'm fucked. Whatever little time I had to find a good hiding place is wasted just trying to keep myself from falling apart under the pressure. My eyes dart around the room, heart hammering..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14072
msgid "* There is that big, steaming, slime-filled hole in the middle of the room. I'm gonna regret this, but I'm out of options."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14073
msgid "* I go for it, grabbing the edge and throwing myself into the cistern, dangling just above the churning vortex of tentacles. Tendrils immediately extend in my direction, forcing me to hoist my legs out of reach."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14074
msgid "* Above me, the pneumatic hiss of a sliding door precedes the heavy footfalls of an armored Gelcorp security guard as he approaches. I really fucking hope he doesn't notice my fingers."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14075
msgid "* Curled into a ball, clinging for my life, and trying not to breath too loudly, I hang in the humid, glowy space between two messed-up fates. The footsteps above me come to a halt."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14076
msgid "* I squeeze my eyes shut, as if that would help. Please, just start walking again. Please just get the fuck out of here before my finger strength gives out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14077
msgid "* After what feels like ages, the footsteps resume, fading as the guard traverses the room and exits through the far door. I let out a long sigh and haul myself out of the cistern."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14079
msgid "* Behind me, the pneumatic hiss of a sliding door sends a shiver down my spine. I turn around slowly..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14080
msgid "* In the doorway, the bulky frame of an armored Gelcorp security guard towers, baton holstered at his waist and respirator strapped to his face. There's a beat as we size each other up, then we leap into action."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14081
msgid "* The guard whips out the baton and yells something. I don't even process it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14082
msgid "* I can close the distance to him long before making it to the opposite door, and if I can get inside his swing, he doesn't stand much of a chance."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14083
msgid "* Attack."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14084 result.py:14086
msgid "* I sprint forward, duck under the swinging baton, and deliver an open palm strike to the guards chin, fracturing the gas-mask and leaving it's remains dangling on either side of his stubbly grimace."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14085 result.py:14087
msgid "* Another quick blow to the chest and he's on the ground, gasping. In a moment, he'll catch his breath and radio backup. I better get the fuck out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14088
msgid "* To my left, in the little raised control room, I see the blinking, staticky screen of what looks like a surveillance system. Before making my escape, I dart up the stairs and grab the cartridge out of the recorder. This could be important."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14089 result.py:14095
msgid "* I freeze up, hesitating before lunging in the guards direction. I duck, but his baton finds purchase on my temple, throwing me off balance. Instead of a precise attack, I crash into him and we both crumple against the wall, my collected items scattering everywhere. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14090
msgid "* Pinning me with his elbow, he frees his hand and hits me in the gut. I buckle in pain, struggling to lift his muscled arm. Breaking free, I start to desperately scramble away."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14091
msgid "* He reaches for me, but I turn back and let loose a wild punch towards his face. It catches his chin, shattering the gas mask and leaving it's remains dangling on either side of his stubbly grimace."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14092
msgid "* I hit him again, hard, on the nose. He lurches back, blood dribbling down his chin, and releases me from his grip. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14093
msgid "* To my left, in the little raised control room, I see the blinking, staticky screen of what looks like a surveillance system."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14094
msgid "* Before making my escape, I dart up the stairs and grab the cartridge out of the recorder. This could be important."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14096
msgid "* I struggle to keep him grappled while I search for the surveillance cart. I reach for it, but in that opening, the guard strikes me where my kidney would be. I buckle."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14097
msgid "* I turn back and let loose a wild punch towards his face. It catches his chin, shattering the gas mask and leaving it's remains dangling on either side of his stubbly grimace."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14098
msgid "* I hit him again, hard, on the nose. He lurches back, blood dribbling down his chin, and releases me from his grip. I struggle to my feet and grab the cartridge."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14099 result.py:14103
msgid "* Olivia's voice chips through my earpiece. * The guard just exited through the front door. I'm assuming you're ok? Report."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14100 result.py:14104
msgid "** Uh, yeah, it's all good. He didn't find me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14101 result.py:14105
msgid "Olivia: Good, but still. Get out of there, HC. There's a lot of activity, so avoid the --- "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14102 result.py:14106
msgid "* At that moment, the front door slides open and another guard spies me from across the room. This time, he's not between me and the door, so I bolt."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14107
msgid "* As I'm making my escape I see the blinking, staticky screen of what looks like a surveillance system in the little raised control room."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14108
msgid "* I quickly dart up the stairs and grab the cartridge out of the recorder. This could be important."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14109
msgid "* By the time I reach the door, the guard is already on the radio behind, yelling about a breach, and an intruder, requesting aid."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14110
msgid "* Fuck. I body slam the sliding door, ripping it out of its tracks and sending it tumbling down into the ravine. I'm out."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14111
msgid "* But I'm not in the clear. The drones form up and hit me with a spotlight. I run hard across the narrow catwalks towards the little spot where my friends are hiding."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14112
msgid "* They're already running. I'm assuming that means they know I can catch up."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14113
msgid "* When I reach the end of the catwalk and my feet meet solid ground, five guards are only 30 feet behind me, sprinting and yelling."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14114
msgid "* I catch up to the group, spread out in panic, Decima and Cadence starting to straggle behind."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14115
msgid "* There's so much ground to cover before we make it back to the fence, but on foot, I think we stand a good chance against the bulkily outfitted guards."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14116
msgid "* The spotlights are terrifying. No matter how hard we run, and how much ground we cover, the drones above us match our speed, holding us steadily in their blinding white beams."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14117
msgid "* A distant siren blares to life. Across the bleak expanse, lights ignite near what must be the main perimeter entrance."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14118
msgid "*  Engine sounds soon join them. We've ditched the guards behind us, but something is speeding along the fence, aiming to cut us off."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14119
msgid "* Every footfall sends a jolt through my chassis and up into my chest like I'm about to run myself to pieces. The speeding shape comes into clearer view. A hover transport, probably filled with at least 15 guards. Fuck."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14120
msgid "* Just. Run. Just fucking make it. Please. Just... My friends are in danger. We need this to work. We need to be ok."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14121
msgid "* As we close in, it really looks like we're gonna make it. 80 feet. 50. 30. They're still a half minute away. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14122
msgid "* We did it. We fucking did it. As long as we can all get through the gap in the fence in time... And as long as the guards can't follow..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14123
msgid "* From somewhere out of sight in the ruins beyond the fence, a heavy hover van pulls up, blocking our exit. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14124
msgid "* A door on it's side slides open, revealing a dark, utilitarian interior, easily big enough for a squad of guards."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14125
msgid "* In the opening, a figure wrapped in a long, dark trench coat appears, face obscured by a brimmed hat. It's the motherfucker we ran into in the hallway outside Olivia and Forcier's apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14126
msgid "* He speaks in a low, gravely voice. * Get in, and be quick about it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14127
msgid "* We all freeze, paralyzed by a seemingly impossible decision. Which terrible stand are we gonna make? My heart pounds dizzyingly fast and hard, and I ball up my fists, preparing for a hopeless last stand."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14128
msgid "* Forcier is the first to move, slipping through the gash in the fence as we all watch in horror. They turn and speak, calm as ever."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14129
msgid "Forcier: I'm quite certain we have a better chance of overpowering this man than we do against anything inside the perimeter. Please, hurry."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14130
msgid "* They disappear into the van. Olivia follows, then Mags and Decima. Cadence and I hesitate."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14131
msgid "* Take her hand and go."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14132
msgid "* Wait for her to go first."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14133
msgid "* I grab Cadence by the hand, give her a reassuring look, and guide her through the fence. We join the others in the van and the door slides shut, sealing out the sounds of chaos."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14134 result.py:14137
msgid "* The trench coated man is in the driver seat, and doesn't waste any time crushing that accelerator."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14135
msgid "* I can't make myself move. I just stand there by her side, mind reduced to a single, unsteady directive. Protect. Tears come to my eyes as I get ready to... I don't even know. To do whatever I need to, I guess."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14136
msgid "* But a moment later, Cadence grabs my hand and guides me through the fence. We join the others in the van and the door slides shut, sealing out the sounds of chaos."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14138
msgid "* The van isn't as fast as the guard's hover transport, but with the fence between us and the cover of the ruins, we let our despair relax into a vague hopefulness."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14139
msgid "* Panting and sweat-drenched, we collapse, giving ourselves somewhat to the mercy of the stranger. In the back of my mind, I hold onto the idea of springing up and fighting, but for now, I just look around."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14140
msgid "* The back of the van is a mess of boxed paper files, beige plastic cases, binders, notepads, hard drives, and other, unidentifiable clutter."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14141
msgid "* It all feels a little antiquated. Not at all like I'd imagine the interior of a Gelcorp agents mobile command center."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14142
msgid "* Decima crawls up into the front passenger seat. * So, are you like, gonna murder us all or something? Cause I gotta warn you, I'm highly resistant to murder."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14143
msgid "* A raspy laugh from the stranger breaks into a cough. * You all looked like you were in a tight spot. Thought I'd lend a hand, that's all."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14144
msgid "* From behind me, Olivia speaks. * Bullshit. You were at our apartment, you had Gelcorp files. Tell us what's really going on."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14145
msgid "* Another laugh. * I live there, as a matter of fact. Names Sal."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14146
msgid "* He takes off his hat, revealing a dowdy man in maybe his late forties or early fifties, unshaven and kind-eyed. * And I'm a PI. Been investigating Gelcorp. Trying, anyway."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14147
msgid "Forcier: What a suspiciously fortuitous coincidence. You wouldn't be pursuing the source of the anomaly as well, would you?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14148
msgid "Sal: Anomaly? I dunno what the hell you're talking about. I'm on the case of a missing Gelcorp employee."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14149
msgid "Sal: Got hired by his wife a while ago, but I haven't turned up much. Real hard to get close to the company without being a company man."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14150
msgid "Forcier: Perhaps it would be beneficial to us both to exchange our findings. After we confirm your identity, of course."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14151
msgid "* Sal chuckles again. * Friend, I don't think you have the privilege. Gelcorp is onto you. Whatever you're into, you need to get out. Fast. Before someone gets hurt."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14152
msgid "Olivia: We know the stakes. If you don't wanna help, that's fine, but we don't need your fucking advice."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14153
msgid "Sal: You don't get it. You're just a bunch of kids. If the company thinks you know too much, they ain't gonna be shy about coming after you. I've seen it before."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14154
msgid "Decima: Excuse me? I'll have you know I'm like... 30, I'm pretty sure. Aren't you like 32, Forcier?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14155
msgid "Forcier: I'm 28, but yes, we are not children, and we are more than capable of handling the situation with caution. * They look at Olivia. * We are more experienced than it appears you've assumed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14156
msgid "Decima: Wait, am I the oldest? Fuck yeah! From now on, this bitch is in charge!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14157
msgid "Magdalena: Yeah, I'm gonna veto that right now."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14158
msgid "* Sal shakes his head. * Alright, alright, I get the picture. Just try to keep 'em away from the apartment then. Don't blow my cover."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14159
msgid "* We take a winding route through the back alleys and abandoned ruins of Pira, in case we're being followed. By the time we make it home, the city is mostly sleeping. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14160
msgid "* Sal tucks the van between some dumpsters in the dark alley behind the brick apartment complex. We made it. We're home. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14161
msgid "* We all get out and Sal locks up the car. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14162
msgid "Cadence: Thank's for saving us, bro! Uh... Yeah! * She smiles."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14163
msgid "Sal: Don't worry about it. And you're right, We should compare notes. I've got work to do, but I'll be in touch. * He turns to leave, but then pauses. * Good luck."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14164
msgid "* Sal walks down the dark alleyway, coat catching the breeze. When he's almost lost to the darkness, he lights up a cigarette. We follow the glow with our eyes until it's gone from sight."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14165
msgid "Cadence: Well that was lucky, I guess. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14166
msgid "Magdalena: I dunno about that. I'm not convinced we can trust him. He kinda gives me the creeps."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14167
msgid "Decima: True, but also, I do feel a bit unmurdered. Or something. Man, I'm fucking tired."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14168
msgid "Forcier: Yes, I believe we could all use some rest. Let's meet again soon to discuss our findings. Good work everyone. * They look at me. * Truly. That was a difficult mission, and you all performed admirably. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14169
msgid "Thanks. * I shuffle my feet. I guess I did kinda carry that one. Whatever."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14170
msgid "* We all say our goodbyes and finally head home. It's late and I'm really looking forward to a bed and a shower. Today was rough, but I guess it did go pretty well, all things considered."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14171
msgid ", "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14172 result.py:14173
msgid "* I tuck the little pack of components under my arm. Maybe when I've finished all the actual mission stuff I have to do, I can sell these."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14174
msgid "* I pass through the rusting door and into Forcier and Olivia's apartment. Olivia is alone, angrily finger-jabbing keys at her desktop."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14175
msgid "* She regards me with a weary smile as I enter. * Oh, HC! Good! I could use a break. * It's hard to read her expression behind her visor, but she's definitely tired."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14176
msgid "What are you working on?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14177
msgid "Olivia: I'm trying to hack... stuff. Drones, I mean. Well, I WAS trying to. * She walks over to the couch and collapses onto it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14178
msgid "Olivia: Sorry, my brain is... slow at switching between talking to computers and talking to people..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14179
msgid "It's cool. I'm kinda both. * I smile. * I know what you mean, though..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14180
msgid "* She smiles back at me without moving her head as she leans back into the couch. She lets her body go limp, sighing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14181
msgid "When you say you're hacking drones, do you mean those surveillance drones that are all over the place?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14182
msgid "Olivia: Yeah. Dunno how long you've been in Pira, but, used to be, there weren't so many of those guys. Over the last several days, though, they've really started pouring into the streets."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14183
msgid "I wonder what they're after..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14184
msgid "Olivia: Well, they're GelCorp-owned, so it probably has something to do with the horniness anomaly. The Hornomaly."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14185
msgid "The horno-... Wow."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14186
msgid "Makes sense."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14187
msgid "Olivia: Hey, I'm tired. Anyway, I was trying to hack one of those drones, maybe get a look inside GelCorp, but so far I've made literally zero progress."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14188
msgid "Olivia: Right? Anyway, I was trying to hack one of those drones, maybe get a look inside GelCorp, but so far I've made literally zero progress."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14189
msgid "Olivia: I don't think I have a chance of interfacing with one unless I have it here with me, in person. I suppose that means I have to go hunting."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14190
msgid "Sounds fun. I can help."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14191
msgid "Olivia: Excellent. * Olivia seems to have found new energy. She hops off the couch, smiling. * I'll gather my things."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14192
msgid "* I wait by the door as Olivia rifles through various bits of complicated-looking technology that covers tabletops and fills the desk drawers of the apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14193
msgid "* Eventually she finds what she's looking for: a dark, metallic cube about the size of a fist."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14194
msgid "What's that thing do?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14195
msgid "Olivia: This is a two-point-three-kilogram cube of elemental iron. I was hoping you could throw it at one of the drones... You're strong, right? * She hands me the cube."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14197
msgid "Why do you have that?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14198
msgid "Olivia: Perfect. Ok, let's go."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14199
msgid "* Olivia looks at me with the expression of someone about to use the word 'layperson.' * Anyway... let's go."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14200
msgid "* We exit the apartment and start walking down Root Street together. She messes with her wrist computer and we chat a little, but it doesn't take long for us to make progress."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14201
msgid "* Olivia glances toward a nearby alley. * I'm picking up an electronic object hovering down there. About the size of a chicken."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14202
msgid "* I follow her to the source. Sure enough, a drone is drifting lazily through the alleyway."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14203
msgid "* Olivia whispers urgently, despite the drone not being able to process speech. * Quick! Hit it!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14204
msgid "* I consider the chunk of iron in my hand. I'm not sure it could survive a blow from this thing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14205
msgid "Hmm...we need it intact, right? "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14206
msgid "Olivia: You're having second thoughts about this plan? Kinda late for that, don't you think!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14207
msgid "Psh, I've got this."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14208
msgid "* Hit it with the cube."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14209
msgid "* Distract it and grab it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14210
msgid "* I plot the perfect arc and let the chunk fly. It crashes into the drone, knocking it into a wall with a hollow metallic crunch. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14211
msgid "* I dive forward with cupped hands, catching the drone before it hits the ground. It's still pretty messed up, though. I hold its smoking chassis aloft so Olivia can get a good look."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14212
msgid "Olivia: Fuck, maybe you were right. Whatever; I'll make do."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14213
msgid "* I hurl the iron chunk at the wall behind the drone, sending a thunderous clatter up and down the alleyway and pelting the drone with particles of brick. Despite this, the drone doesn't react at all."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14214
msgid "* Regardless, the plan is in motion. I leap forward, grappling the drone mid-air. It sags under my weight, but manages to stay afloat a few feet from the ground. A piercing alarm sounds from within its casing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14215
msgid "Ok, cool, NOW it notices..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14216
msgid "Olivia: Jesus-fucking-Christ. * She hugs my legs, rooting me to the ground, her face level with my crotch. I can read her expression now: she looks pretty annoyed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14217
msgid "* We both work it to the ground, whereupon I dig my feet into the dirt and unleash a few punches at its big blinking face-light until it sputters and dies. We rise to our feet and dust ourselves off."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14218
msgid "Olivia: Uh, let's get out of here..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14219
msgid "* We stroll back to the apartment, the drone carcass slung over Olivia's shoulder. We stop at the staircase leading into the building."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14220
msgid "I think it's about time for me to head home. It was nice hanging out with you, Olivia."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14221
msgid "Oliva: No problem. I'll keep you updated on my progress with the hack. I assume I can count on you if I need anything else?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14223
msgid "We'll see."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14224
msgid "Olivia: Excellent. See you later, HC. * She ascends the stairs and disappears into her apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14225
msgid "Olivia: I guess we will. Later, HC. * She ascends the stairs and disappears into her apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14226
msgid "* I leave Root Street and head back to my apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14227
msgid "* I meet Olivia alone in her apartment. The drone is lying inert on her desk, its outer casing open and overflowing with multicolored wires. Most of them lead to Oliva's computer."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14228
msgid "Hey, Olivia! You mentioned you could use my help?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14229
msgid "Olivia: Yes, I could. Thank you for coming. * She closes whatever she was looking at on her computer and swivels her chair to face me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14230
msgid "* Her spread legs and rosy cheeks give her away. She's being affected by the anomaly."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14231
