msgid "* We chill, talk about tech stuff and Gelcorp, and watch the neon glow fade to evening. Eventually, it gets to be time for me to go."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14428
msgid "Olivia: It was nice to see you, HC."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14430
msgid "* It's a beautiful day under Pira City's ever-present argon cloud. I don't rush down to Root Street, just let myself take in the sights, the sounds, whatever breaks through the desolation."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14431
msgid "* Passing the Acorn, I come to the open stairway leading into Olivia and Forcier's apartment."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14432
msgid "* It's not a tall building, but from the street its pipe-bound stories tower over me, dotted with exhaust ports belching steam."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14433
msgid "* My footsteps echo through the stairway until I reach the door. Sticker residue and cobwebs plaster the walls, broken by the occasional access panel."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14434
msgid "*  This place used to require a key card, but the lock has long since busted."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14435
msgid "* Navigating the short hallway, I find Oliva's door and let myself in."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14436
msgid "* Olivia is alone, sitting on the couch, rifling through a small plastic crate. It's plastic exterior shows nearly as much wear as the building's facade."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14437
msgid "Hey, Olivia! Whatcha got there?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14438
msgid "* She smiles that hard-to-read Olivia smile. Almost malicious. * This is the centerpiece of the latest iteration of my hypno-visor. * She lifts a small, blue item out of the box."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14439
msgid "* I join her on the couch, examining the colorful little thing. Seems to be a toy of some kind. Cheap plastic. Vaguely humanoid and small enough to fit in her palm, sprayed with a cartoonish set of facial features."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14440
msgid "* It almost looks like a little eggplant? Or maybe a bunny? It catches the light from the window and I notice a dark glass panel on the base. Its leaves start swaying back and forth under its new-found solar energy."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14441
msgid "Olivia: Forcier found a crate of these while they were out scavenging. It has a simple AI that was meant to interface with the type of smart-house systems that were popular a few hundred years ago."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14442 result.py:14443
msgid "* There's a small embossing on the side, which reads Luckyfriend Eggyplant. * So, how is this supposed to work with the hypno thing?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14444
msgid "* Olivia chuckles. * You'll see. * She looks away from me towards the little guy in my hands. * Lucky. Give us the time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14445
msgid "* A little light on its nose flares red and a tinny speaker somewhere inside sounds a squeaky voice. * The time is -- four - nineteen- AM"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14446
msgid "Well, that's extremely incorrect. This thing seems kinda... I dunno... Useless? What are you really doing with these, Olivia?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14447
msgid "Olivia: Tech is only useless insofar as it doesn't serve us. * She whips out a small knife and picks up the toy, cracks its casing and cuts a wire."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14448
msgid "Olivia: Lucky, give us the time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14449
msgid "* The red light blinks, but this time, no sound emanates from the little device. She sets the toy down, walks over to her desk, carefully slides open a drawer."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14450
msgid "Olivia: There's a way you can serve me, HC. But you'll have to trust me. * She lifts the hypno visor, now adorned with some extra circlets, and walks it back to the couch."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14451
msgid "Of course I trust you."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14452
msgid "I'm gonna need more info."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14453
msgid "I'm not in the mood for games."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14454
msgid "* It's true. She can be bold with her hacking and stuff, but I feel in my core that I'll always be safe when she's around. Even when she's fucking me up."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14455
msgid "* She frowns. * Fine. I have a bit of a... an out of body experience planned for you. You're going to get to watch as I play with your luscious, helpless body. Sound good?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14456
msgid "Ok, sounds good."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14457
msgid "I'm not interested."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14458
msgid "Olivia: Good. * She hands me the visor, its cold weight calling me back to our last little adventure. It's chunkier this time. A network of sensors form a dome behind the eyes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14459
msgid "Olivia: Well? Be a good hypnoslut and put it on."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14460
msgid "* Put it on."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14461
msgid "Make me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14462
msgid "Actually, I changed my mind."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14463
msgid "* I slip the helmet over my head, blocking my vision. Outside, I hear Olivia's slightly muffled voice. * Let's reduce you, shall we? Let's turn you into something I can work with."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14464
msgid "* A brisk slap smarts across my cheek. Nowhere near her full strength. I'm guessing she doesn't want to deter me too much, since we're just getting started. I crack a smile. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14465
msgid "Olivia: People are so much harder to manipulate than code. * She grabs the helmet, crowns me, tucks some wires behind my ear. * Let's reduce you, shall we? Let's turn you into something I can work with.  "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14466
msgid "* A storm of flickering pixels ignites behind the visor, churning along patterns that distort my sense of space, depth, orientation. The light propels me out of the material world, pushes it from my memory."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14467
msgid "* Olivia's voice reaches me as if from the end of a tunnel. * Tell me, HC. What do you see?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14468
msgid "* I drift through the aether of my quickly draining mind, grasping at what few faculties I could still recognize. Speech. Perfect. * I... I see... "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14469
msgid "* The cascade of pixels seems to rush at me, to flee, to flow, to scatter, all at once. I can feel my mind peeling apart in each futile pursuit. Beyond it all, though, I see a humanoid form."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14470
msgid "I see... A person... * I vaguely recollect my friend beyond the veil, Olivia. Her hair, her dress... Just a dim silhouette quickly slipping away. Gone. Now it's just me, the storm, and the voice."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14471
msgid "The voice: Good. That's good. Now relax. * The pixels shift in response to the voice, forming concentric, shifting sigils, lightning blues and burning crimsons."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14472
msgid "* I relax and watch them bloom like roses from the pits of my eyes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14473
msgid "* The voice echoes all around me. * Strip. * Mentally, I obey, but my body has become unfixed to any sense I can recognize. Somewhere, far way, I hope it complies."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14474
msgid "The voice: Wake."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14475
msgid "* The curtains of color are slowly drawn back and the figure swims back into view. My... Friend. Right?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14476
msgid "* The pixels are bigger now, assembling like pieces of a puzzle."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14477
msgid "* The world is warped and two-dimensional, smeared with a wrongness that I can't quite place. A stage forms. The figure is joined by a second, shorter, wearing a dress."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14478
msgid "* I return to physicality with a half-asleep vertigo jolt. A tiny start, followed by the utter impact of paralysis. I try to move. Command executed. But I feel nothing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14479
msgid "* The voice sounds once more, filling me with a deep sense of calm. * You're back! Excellent."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14480
msgid "* The figure, the progenitor of that beautiful voice, approaches, looms over me. Behind her, another body, limp and naked on the floor."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14481
msgid "* Her massive hand reaches down, lifts me toward her face. She's smiling, vast and enthralling."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14482
msgid "The voice: Can you hear me?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14483
msgid "* I had a module for this, once. Speech. I don't remember it well, but I feel its absence. I search for an alternative, running through the hollow structure of my remnant mind."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14484
msgid "* Here's something. Boolean. It'll have to do. A red light ignites between my eyes. What the fuck..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14485
msgid "* The smile parts, those lush lips filling my view. * I'll take that as a yes. How about your leaves? Can you wiggle for me?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14486
msgid "* My leaves? Somehow, I understand. I wiggle for her, watch her face light up. In the reflection of the chrome visor resting on my friends brow, I can kinda make out..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14487
msgid "* Holy fuck... I'm a god damn eggplant. My little solar panel glints, my plastic leaves move up and down at my whim. I flash my nose-light. That's all I got."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14488
msgid "The voice: That's right, little hypnoslut! You're literally a fucking toy! You're a half-coupon worth of cheap plastic and microchips!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14489
msgid "* She brings me real close, whispers. * How does it feel to be disposable?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14490
msgid "* Blink my light."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14491
msgid "* Wave my leaves."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14492
msgid " * Do nothing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14493
msgid "The voice: That's right, blink your light! Pray that I can understand your feeble attempt at communication. * She laughs. * I can't. And I don't want to. I'm a higher organism than you now."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14494
msgid "The voice: That's right, wave your leaves! Pray that I can understand your feeble attempt at communication. * She laughs. * I can't. And I don't want to. I'm a higher organism than you now."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14495
msgid "The voice: What's the matter, given up already? I thought breaking you would be a little more fun than that... * She laughs."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14496
msgid "* She drops me, letting me hit the floor and bounce, my rigid body jarring my camera with the impact. The vibration is disorienting, and I'm not sure what I'm looking at, till her giant foot plants itself in front of me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14497
msgid "* It lifts again, carrying her towards the limp body across the room, further into my range of vision. Her legs shrink and that pretty dress comes into view. The angle is still wrong though."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14498
msgid "* She bends over the blue-gray skin of the naked figure, whispers in it's ear. I'm too far away to hear her, but still, her words register with me somehow, subconciously. I don't know how I work anymore..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14499
msgid "The voice: Rise. * The body arches, lifting to its knees, head still slumped over. With a single finger under its chin, she raises its head towards hers. I can feel the bliss of vicarious obedience rush through me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14500
msgid "The voice: Feast. * She lifts the dress and the figure pushes its face into her crotch. Somewhere, far away, I'm aware of the layers of pleasure my ghost is feeling."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14501
msgid "* By the time it gets to me though, it's just simple affirmation."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14502
msgid "* I drift back into a dreamy trance, lost in my desire to please the voice. To Obey. To collect what little I can of this feeble mind and offer it to her to use however she wants. I find myself fanning my leaves."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14503
msgid "* Despite the mental fog, the figures remain clear, their eager sex driving all other thoughts from my mind. The voice grinds on the blue figures face, gripping its head and moaning.  "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14504
msgid "* The moans reach my mic, but the sensation of her cumming in my mouth is filtered through some cruel proxy that I don't quite understand. It leaves me longing for the firsthand experience that I'm missing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14505
msgid "* All I can do is wiggle my leaves while the owner of the voice shakes and bucks in ecstasy, breathes hard, and eventually relaxes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14506
msgid "* My little mind feels only envy and the raw wound where my capacity for more was removed."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14507
msgid "* When the blue body finally slumps back over, lips and chin glistening, eyes blank and hypno-dazed, the owner of the voice gets up, walks back towards my spot on the floor."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14508
msgid "* She reaches down, picks up my fragile form. The voice shakes my soul, making me wish I could move, wiggle my way deeper into the nest of her palms."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14509
msgid "The voice: I've had my fun. Your body makes an excellent toy, HC. * HC? What's that supposed to mean..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14510
msgid "The voice: Time to send you back where you came from. I could reverse the process using the same link I used to trap you in this little eggplant. But really, any sufficient amount of destruction should do the trick."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14511
msgid "* The smile once again fills my view. * So, what'll it be, HC? Should I send you back the proper way? Or would you prefer to be crushed to dust under your mistresses heel?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14512
msgid "* The smile widens. * Oh, right. The communication thing. Wave your leaves if you want me to destroy you. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14513 result.py:14518
msgid "* Blink no."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14514 result.py:14519
msgid "* Wave yes."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14515
msgid "I try to respond, but she hand moves to cover my solar panel. Immediately, my vision darkens. Mind functions reduce. Low power... Low...."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14516
msgid "* She moves her hand and I revive, as if waking from a dreamless sleep, gradually recalling my situation."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14517
msgid "* She laughs in my face. * What was that? I couldn't hear you. Try harder, hypnoslut! Do you want me to crush you or not!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14520
msgid "* She chuckles. * Suit yourself. * Her wrist computer rises and the typing begins. Soon, I'm tossed back into the pixely chaos from before, disoriented, depersonalized, and finally, rebuilt in my old body."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14521
msgid "The voice: That's a good hypnoslut. * She drops me to the ground, again letting me clatter. I come to land on my back, staring upwards. From the floor, from these little eyes, she's colossal. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14522
msgid "The voice: You know, if you could speak, I'd make you beg for this. I guess you've earned it though, letting me turn you into such a pathetic piece of junk. Letting me use your body like that."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14523
msgid "* From down here, I can see everything. Her dress sways with every shift of her hips, every breath. Every ounce of my attention is consumed by the massive foot, the black rubber sole of her heels, hovering above me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14524
msgid "* It descends. All else fades, her laughter, the room, the body behind her. Everything is chased from my mind by the primal anticipation of obliteration under her heel."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14525
msgid "* It hits me slow. Pressure, my splitting seams. Vision distorts. Static. Each output torn away, each circuit broken. Wires twist and snap and --"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14526
msgid "..........................................."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14527
msgid "* My eyes flash open. I'm limp on the floor, Olivia is standing over me, the hypnovisor in her hands. She sets it down, then helps me up, leads me to the couch."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14528
msgid "Olivia: Take a seat, HC. This type of mental fuckery might take a few minutes to recover from. * She clasps my shoulder. * I'm gonna run some scans, make sure everything's working."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14529
msgid "* She sits down on the end of the couch, kicks off her shoes, pivots towards me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14530
msgid "* Light from the computer on her wrist travels across me. Her bare feet are cold against my thigh, and I watch her toes wiggle while she works."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14531
msgid "Olivia: Yeah, everything looks good. Excellent. * She lowers her arm to her ankles, leans towards me. There's a bounce in her, a delightful energy radiating from her soul. I feel a cuddly closeness to her."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14532
msgid "Olivia: How'd it feel? * She's a pleasant combination of concerned for my wellbeing and just geeking out about her invention."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14533
msgid "Weird as fuck, not gonna lie. Was I like, literally outside of my body? I saw the body... My body... moving under your control. I had no idea that kind of hacking was even possible."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14534
msgid "Olivia: Actually, that part wasn't hacking. You were wirelessly connected to Lucky, but your mind was still in your own body. It was just hypnosis and your own subconscious desires that made you obey. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14535
msgid "* She cocks her head. * I guess hypnosis could be considered a type of hacking, but... * She shakes her head. * But I'm not gonna get into that. If I get started, I'll never stop. Let's just relax and talk."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14536
msgid "Olivia: Understood. I can find someone else to test this on. Let's just relax. It's been a while since we just talked. * She sinks into the couch, pulls the visor into her lap."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14537
msgid "Yeah, talking is nice. * I rest my head on her shoulder."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14538
msgid "Olivia: I do tend to hyper focus when I've got a project to work on. Forcier brought me dinner at my desk last night and next thing I know, the sun is rising and I haven't left my station."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14539
msgid "Olivia: Mind if I tinker while we chill?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14540
msgid "Go for it. I like watching you work."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14541
msgid "* Olivia smiles. * Excellent. I can focus more easily when my hands are busy. * She opens a panel on the side of the visor, runs a cord between it and her wrist computer."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14542
msgid "What is it you're doing? * I crane my neck into the exposed circuitry, but I can make no sense of it."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14543
msgid "Olivia: Touching something up. There's a subsystem in here that works fine but felt bad to write. I get the most done towards the end of my code-benders, but it also usually gets kinda incoherent."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14544
msgid "Olivia: The fix came to me in a dream, though. * She laughs, soft and short, as if she does't even notice. * Do this long enough and it starts to become how you think."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14545
msgid "You mean, like, you have a logical, mathematical mind? Is that not..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14546
msgid "useful?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14547
msgid "more a Forcier thing?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14548
msgid "* Amusement touches her cheeks. * That's not at all what I mean."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14549
msgid "* Olivia laughs deeper this time, more consciously, more surprised."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14550
msgid "Olivia: No, you've got them wrong. Mathematical is the opposite of what Forcier is. They're smart in an emotional way. It's one of the reasons I love them so much."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14551
msgid "* She pauses, looks up from the wrist computer for the first time since we sat back. * That's not really what I mean anyway though."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14552
msgid "Olivia: It's not as fundamental as being a logical person. I'm just talking about how when I close my eyes, all I see is lines of code scrolling across my eyelids."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14553
msgid "Olivia: What about you, HC? What do you see?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14554
msgid "* I close my eyes, let the darkness ferment..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14555
msgid "I see..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14556
msgid "...stars over the wasteland."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14557
msgid "...my friends at the Acorn."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14558
msgid "...bouncing titties."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14559
msgid "...nothing good."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14560
msgid "Olivia: Ah, man... That sounds beautiful."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14561
msgid "* There's another spacey laugh as she recollects. * When I was a kid, I spent the aftermath of one of my amateur jobs in the wasteland, hunkering down, trying to not get caught."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14562
msgid "Olivia: That was before I trusted the anarchists enough to rely on their protection. I spent a few nights there, and it fucking sucked. Taught me the value of safe houses and community protection."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14563
msgid "Olvia: The wasteland blows for a ton of reasons, but that clear sky made it a positive memory. Code brain or not, I'm never gonna forget seeing low-orbit satellites drifting in front of the moon..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14564
msgid "That's funny, I was out there on the run, too. I totally agree, it sucks. But yeah. It can be pretty..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14565
msgid "* We rest on each other and try to imagine stars. I can see them. I hope Olivia can too."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14566
msgid "Olivia: That's... that's really cute. * There's a tinge of sadness in her voice, but an honest pride as well."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14567
msgid "It's funny though. I don't even need to eat. We just laugh and have a good time. * I pause. * You're there. Sharing tots with Decima. * I let my imagination bloom."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14568
msgid "* She laughs softly, then says nothing. The silence is warm and safe. We rest on each other and think about greasy food and good friends."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14569
msgid "* She laughs hard. * Of course you do. Anyone's titties in particular? Or is it just a sample-pack type situation?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14570
msgid "They're mine."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14571
msgid "They're yours."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14572
msgid "They're all my friends."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14573
msgid "It's a sample-pack, yeah."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14574
msgid "* She smirks. * Good choice. * She glances down at them. * Honestly, that's a very good choice."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14575
msgid "* She chuckles. * You flatter me. * She does a little hop in her seat, bouncing them under her dress, as if to evaluate them. * Good choice though."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14576
msgid "Olivia: That's... that's really cute. * She looks honestly kinda charmed. * You're precious, HC."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14577
msgid "Olivia: Makes sense. There are a lot of good titties out there. * She ruminates for a bit. * You could say that all titties are good titties."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14578
msgid "Agreed. * We rest on each other and imagine the world of breasts that exists beyond this room, this apartment, this city. Damn. That's a bunch of titties..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14579
msgid "* We rest on each other, smiling, and imagine various bouncing breasts, their softness, their cuteness. Being next to her makes me feel soft and cute. I hope she feels the same. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14580
msgid "Olivia: That fucking blows. Maybe code is a blessing.."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14581
msgid "* There's a long pause as she thinks of something to say. Her cool is faltered, just a little. * You wanna talk about it? Or no... * I can tell this isn't really her thing."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14582
msgid "That's sweet. Thanks, Olivia. I don't think this is a talk-it-through kinda problem, though. Just old wounds, you know?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14583
msgid "Olivia: I do. * There's no need to elaborate. The silence is shorthand in a language we both speak. We share pain, if not experience, and right now, that's enough."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14584
msgid "* We rest on each other and try and replace those mental scars with this sweet moment, this little pocket of safety, at least for now. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14585
msgid "* We listen to city noises and I touch her soft skin. There's nothing I would change about this moment. Eventually...................."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14586
msgid "* ........I blink awake."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14587
msgid "Olivia: You dozed off. Pretty cute, IMO."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14588
msgid "* She's back to working on the visor, positioned to manipulate wires without moving her shoulder too much, but now Forcier is here as well. She didn't wanna wake me..."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14589
msgid "Aha... Damn. I guess that means I should be heading home."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14590
msgid "* Olivia smiles. * If you wanna."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14591
msgid "* Olivia deserves her evening with Forcier. I really should let them be. I'm sure I'll see her again soon, though. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14592
msgid "* It feels weird to say bye after our little moment, so we just share a knowing glance as I slip out and start towards home. "
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14593
msgid "* Olivia charges down the stairs of her apartment, fulcrums around the corner and launches herself towards Decima's nextdoor workshop. Must not have seen me approach."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14594
msgid "Hey! Olivia! * I jog up to her, touch her shoulder."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14595
msgid "Olivia: HC. Perfect timing. I have something to show you."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14596
msgid "* Tucked under her arm is a bundle of small grey plastic limbs that I assume she's preparing to intruduce me to, but she just keeps walking."
