#: result.py:14597
msgid "* The door jingles as we enter the workshop. Decima is hunched over her workbench, finessing a tool inside a robots chest cavity. Common model."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14598
msgid "* Something old and only vaguely humanoid. THORco badge tarnished on its chest."
