#: result.py:14600
msgid "* Decima turns away from the obsolete droid, lifts her goggles. * Hey you two! You're gonna have to give me a minute. Chill wherever you like!"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14601
msgid "Olivia: Take your time."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14602
msgid "* I lean on Decima's messy desk, and Olivia plants herself in the swivel chair. Finally, I get a good look at what she's been carrying."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14603
msgid "* It's a humanoid ball-jointed doll, about a foot in height, its surface banded in 3d-printer artifacts. Eyes, hair, and other details have been omitted to make room for an array of small sensors."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14604
msgid "Olivia: I'm not a hardware person, but I did what I could. There's a few kinks I need Decima's help to work out."
