#: result.py:14605
msgid "* I delicately lift the limp, unadorned figure. * What is it?"
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14606
msgid "Olivia: A prototype."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14607
msgid "For what? * The pair of lenses in its face shine dully back at me."
msgstr ""

#: result.py:14608
msgid "Olivia: For you. This is gonna be your new form, for whenever I want to make you my plaything. It'll be a better fit than that dancing toy from before. I assure you."
msgstr ""

